\id MAT - KAPIN Yandabing Sept 2015
\h Matai
\toc3 Mat
\toc2 Matai
\toc1 Xoulek Nimza wei Matai byex o
\mt2 Xoulek Nimza wei
\mt1 Matai
\mt2 byex o
\imt1 Qayeeng wei la tax o
\ip Xoulek Nimza wei Matai byex ne eno la tax en qapiya vey wei tul pavulek en lulul wei qandi wou Yesu gyeik ingwei lam dei lek tembuing o. Qapiya tine tul pavulek atax en lulul wei qandi myaxeeng gyeik Maria wou Yesu yo, me tul pavulek la tyip ingwei xel leis Yesu mey o, me qandi lek veil meyeing o, de la veil e xe xel me lek me la tyoung gheyapu nei.
\ip Lul ngandoung ti Matai embei talex, eno nambei nye, Yesu wong ela teyei lek lulul wei Anutu neil zonghek takwei me xel byex eivek qokatu wei takwei yo o (Olpela Testamen). Anutu neil zonghek bei tyek bong tambiy ti bei e nam a qou xel Israel noumenam, de qapiya tiyon embei talex bei Yesu e tambiy tiyon. Eivek qapiya danghei valu wei Matai, eno qayeeng talex bei lulul wei Yesu wong eno la teyei lek qayeeng wei Anutu xe xel poropet neil takwei yo. Wei 1:22-23 me 2:4-6 me 2:14-15 me 2:23 me 4:13-16 me 8:16-17 me 12:15-21 me 13:34-35 me 21:2-5 me 21.16 me 26.24 me 26.31 me 26.54 me 27:6-10.
\ip Lul ngandoung nge eno qapiya wei Matai yo neil, inyon tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo o tete lalei wei Anutu yo. En xuk wei Yesu eno Anutu embei bo king zonghek wei xomaxoneing dalusateiv o, de embei xomaxoneing na mi betiwou woueing nalei wei e yo.
\ip Eivek qapiya danghei lim wei Matai, eno qayeeng ding a ding wei Yesu neil o. Tiwei tax eno di yeip eivek sapta 5-7 eno inyon xel qayeeng wei Yesu neil lek lukendu ti yo. Qayeeng tiyon talex xel xomaxoneing wei mindei nambei Anutu xe xel zonghek o. Qayeeng ding a ding nge wei yuw eno di yeip eivek sapta 10. Qayeeng tiyon Yesu wong wou xel betiyeing en lulul wei xel bong gyeik ingwei xel na neil Yesu xe xoulek wou xomaxoneing bamba yo.
\ip Qayeeng ding a ding tiwei yal eno di yeip eivek sapta 13, Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing bei talex wou xel xomaxoneing en Anutu xe tete lalei. Qayeeng ding a ding tiwei vey eno di yeip eivek sapta 18, Yesu neil qayeeng wei xomaxoneing embei mendei nambei e xe betiyeing zonghek o. De qayeeng ding a ding tiwei lim eno di yeip eivek sapta 24-25, Yesu neil qayeeng wei lulul embei qandi lek gyeik bouk loxyus o.
\ip Qapiya tiyon venaxow eno se neil teyei bei tambiy eti byex qapiya tiyon. Ekom qapiya tiyon qou lei bei Xoulek Nimza wei Matai byex o. Inyon nambei nye, xel wou naleind en Matai tiwei mi qou takis wei di yeip eivek sapta 9:9-13.
\c 1
\s1 Yesu buyeiw leind
\p 
\v 1 Yesu Kilisi buyeiw leind wei yeip eivek qapiya eno inye eivek velei wei Dawit o, de Dawit on eivek velei wei Apraham o.
\p 
\v 2 Apraham on Isaka ma,
\q1 de Isaka yon Yakop ma,
\q1 de Yakop on Yuda ma me liyeiw is,
\q1 
\v 3 Yuda yon Peres aluw Sela mend, de luw tend lei Tamar,
\q1 de Peres on Hesron ma,
\q1 de Hesron on Ram ma,
\q1 
\v 4 Ram on Aminadap ma,
\q1 de Aminadap on Nason ma,
\q1 de Nason on Salmon ma,
\q1 
\v 5 Salmon on Boas ma de ta lei Rahap,
\q1 de Boas on Obet ma de ta lei Rut,
\q1 de Obet on Jesi ma,
\q1 
\v 6 de Jesi yon king Dawit ma.
\p De Dawit on Salomo ma, e tiwei ta Yuria venei yo,
\q1 
\v 7 Salomo yon Rehoboam ma,
\q1 de Rehoboam on Abiya ma,
\q1 de Abiya yon Asa ma,
\q1 
\v 8 Asa yon Jehosapat ma,
\q1 de Jehosapat on Jehoram ma,
\q1 de Jehoram on Usia ma,
\q1 
\v 9 Usia yon Jotam ma,
\q1 de Jotam on Ahas ma,
\q1 de Ahas on Hesekia ma.
\q1 
\v 10 Hesekia yon Manase ma,
\q1 de Manase yon Amon ma,
\q1 de Amon on Yosia ma.
\q1 
\v 11 De Yosia yon Jekonaia\f + \fr 1:11-12 \ft Jekonaia, lei nge bei Jehoiakin.\f* ma me moxo lis liyeiw mindei gyeik xel Babilon lam wo vevek me zeimaxoun xel Israel de qou xel me la Babilon.
\p 
\v 12 Ka xel la Babilon:
\q1 Woyom Jekonaia yon Seatiel ma,
\q1 de Seatiel on Serubabel ma.
\q1 
\v 13 De Serubabel on Abiut ma,
\q1 de Abiut on Eliakim ma,
\q1 de Eliakim on Aso ma.
\q1 
\v 14 De Aso yon Sadok ma,
\q1 de Sadok on Akim ma,
\q1 de Akim on Eliut ma,
\q1 
\v 15 de Eliut on Eliesa ma,
\q1 de Eliesa yon Matan ma,
\q1 de Matan on Yakop ma.
\q1 
\v 16 De Yakop on Yosep ma, de Yosep on Maria leya, Maria wei qou Yesu wei xel mi taxe bei Kilisi yo, moux on Anutu beyal bei e qou moux alis vex wei e yo noum.
\p 
\v 17 Inyon nambei 14 neumambu wei Apraham me ela Dawit o, de 14 neumambu nanghei Dawit me ela tyip ingwei xel la xeitueing anghei Babilon o, deka xel la xeitueing anghei Babilon eno 14 neumambu me ela tyip wou bouk wei Yesu Kilisi\f + \fr 1:17 \ft Qes wei lei Kilisi eno nambei nye: tambiy wei xel taw wel lek e lu. Ekom eivek kwa wei Yudayeiw takwei eno xel mi taw wel lek moux nambei dee wei Anutu beyal bei em bale me natax en e xe xomaxoneing. Natax en ingwei Yesu lam o xel ngenong di axe e en xel embei gyei lek mend nanghei inye me nanghei inyei en xel wou naleind bei tambiy vako ti tyek nam devind xel veil nimaying. Xel taxe tambiy tiyon Kilisi. Eivek qayeeng wei Hibru eno xel neil, Mesia. Qes, tambiy wei Anutu beyal bei e qou xomaxoneing noum o.\f* yo.
\s1 Yesu Kilisi umbek
\p 
\v 18 Tine inye pavulek en ingwei Yesu Kilisi umbek o: Moxo ta Maria eno xel beyal bei e mendei wou Yosep, luw se ghei dei lekti ekom vexo xei qou veil en Laweeng Vambuing nikanzek.
\v 19 Maria leya Yosep on tambiy wei bombek om embei se bong niyalenyeing wou vexo eivek xel moux alis vex dalus mend, om embei na veil e xupekeing.
\p 
\v 20 Ekom Yosep nanghei di wounalei en tine, Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela lam wou e eivek maviing me neil, “Yosep wa velei wei Dawit o, wa seng gwaleeng qe wa qou Maria nambei veneim, en yak tiwei tumi eivek e yon inye lam wou Laweeng Vambuing.
\v 21 Tyek vexo bou neu moux ti, yond wa taxe e lei bei Yesu, en tyek devind e xe xel veil xel xe sewokeing.”
\p 
\v 22 Lul dalus tine la teyei lek ambei ingwei Tambiy Ngandoung neil eivek poropet mya yo:
\q1 
\v 23 “Wei, vexawo wei paleveeng o ti tyek xei qou veil me bou neu moux ti, de tyek xel taxe e bei Imanuel.” \rq Yesaya 7:14\rq*
\m Qes ambei nye, “Anutu toundei is xey.”
\p 
\v 24 Ka Yosep qandi lek de moxo wong ambei kawei Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela neil wou e yo, me qou Maria nambei e venei.
\v 25 Ekom moxo se yeip is e qe ka Maria qou neu moux woy le. De moxo taxe neu lei Yesu.
\c 2
\s1 Xel lundpeyei wei mendalus eno lam yei Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Ka Yesu umbek eivek Betelem wei Yudia nei, eivek bouk wei king Herot eno xel lundpeyei wei mendalus wei mi yei dee lek betum eno lam anghei ninei me lam Yerusalem
\v 2 me teling, “Tambiy tiwei umbek ambei king wei Yudayeiw eno toundei inya? Xa xei e xe betum anghei ninei me na lam en xa bei bong lalo wou e.”
\p 
\v 3 King Herot ngo qayeeng tine eno moxo is xel Yerusalem dalus wounaleind ngenong.
\v 4 Woyom moxo taxe xel lumuki leitata me xel putoung wei petieing wei xomaxoneing dalus o, moxo teling wou xel bei Kilisi tyek dumbek anghei inya?
\v 5 Xel neil elox, “Eivek Betelem wei Yudia nei, en inye qayeeng vati wei poropet byex takwei yo:
\q1 
\v 6 “‘Ekom Betelem wang eivek tembuing danghei wei Yuda yo
\q2 wa leim se nayak en beyeeng leilaing wei Yuda yo,
\q1 en eivek wang eno tyek wa xe tambiy ti bong ambei wa xe leilaing
\q2 me tyek mendei bei gyovaxa wei a xe xomaxoneing wei Israel o.’” \rq Maika 5:2\rq*
\p 
\v 7 Woyom Herot taxe xel lundpeyei wei mendalus o xupekeing me ngo teyei wou xel bei lek bouk vati eno betum lam nale.
\v 8 Moxo wong xel la Betelem me neil, “Xam la me wimexe e wo nimza en yak on. Ka xam ghe gweiwou e, xam ghe bong qayeeng nam wou ay, en kandek ana bong lalo wou e is.”
\p 
\v 9 Ka xel ngo king xe qayeeng woy, xel la wou sakwaing no me la, me betum wei xel yei ghei ninei eno la tax en xel, dekalekom la nale ghey lek beyeeng kawei yak on toundei ghei yo.
\v 10 Gyeik xel yei betum eno xel wo xeindlala ngandoung.
\v 11 Xel la eivek xomek lalei me yei yak on is ta Maria, de xel ev vaxend qatu eivek dom wo lalo wou e. Woyom xel tax xel xe vaxak malew dom wong ghol, me xax myalouk, me xax myalouk nge wei mi wo xeimangou yo la wou e.
\v 12 De Anutu peti xel eivek maviing bei xel se nox wou Herot, qe xel na nox sakwaing ba me nox bend.
\s1 Yesu ma luw ta qou e me pek me la Izip
\p 
\v 13 Ka xel lundpeyei wei mendalus la veil, Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela lam wou Yosep eivek maviing. Me neil, “Qandi lek me qou yak on aluw ta me pek me la Izip. Xam a mi mendei inyon deka a neil wou wang bole, en Herot di yimexe yak on en embei nyeis e mey.”
\v 14 Om moxo qandi lek, me qou yak on aluw ta me la eivek boukeing me la Izip,
\v 15 de moxo mindei inyon deka Herot mey le. Me lul tine la teyei lek ambei Tambiy Ngandoung neil eivek poropet mya yo.
\q1 “A taxe neung moux bei e nam veil Izip.” \rq Hosea 11:1\rq*
\p 
\v 16 Gyeik Herot woulek bei xel wei lundpeyei wei ninei eno tyoxe e, moxo lalei wo vanei mouyo, om wong qayeeng nikanzek bei xel nyeis xel yak moux dalus eivek Betelem me xel yak wei beyeeng paviyeing wei xel xe vakovek qes yuw o me e teiloum axo, teyei lek bouk wei e ngo wou xel lundpeyei wei ninei yo.
\v 17 Woyom lul tine la teyei lek ambei Anutu neil eivek poropet Yelemia mya yo.
\q1 
\v 18 “Vya ti eno xel ngo eivek beyeeng Rama,
\q2 inyon engeing me talot ngandoung,
\q1 Resel di eng en neuyeiw dalus mey,
\q2 me vexo embei xel se bong e lalei bo nimza,
\q1 en nambei neuyeiw dalus mey de ti se toundei mapieing.” \rq Yeremia 31:15\rq*
\s1 Yosep loumelam Nasaret
\p 
\v 19 Ka Herot mey woy eno Tambiy Ngandoung xe angela ti lam wou Yosep eivek maviing nanghei Izip
\v 20 de neil, “Qandi lek, me qou yak on aluw ta me lox me la tembuing wei Israel nei, en xel wei embei nyeis yak on na mey eno mey.”
\p 
\v 21 Om moxo qandi lek me qou yak on aluw ta me lal lox me la tembuing wei Israel o.
\v 22 Ekom e ngo bei Arkelaus yeiteyei Yudia eivek ma Herot nimbeeng, om moxo yaleeng en embei se na inyon. Ekom Anutu neil wou Yosep eivek maviing ti, om moxo la distrik Galili,
\v 23 me la dei eivek beyeeng wei xel mi taxe bei Nasaret. Om tine la teyei lek ambei ingwei neil eivek poropet myend o. “Tyek xel taxe e bei tambiy wei Nasaret o.”
\c 3
\s1 Yoan Lipekeing menyex wou sakwaing
\p 
\v 1 Eivek bouk ti beimambei yon eno Yoan lipekeing lam, moxo neil qayeeng eivek tembuing bandaing wei Yudia nei
\v 2 me neil, “Xam pekwi xow, en tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno lam paviy.”
\v 3 Tambiy tine inye tiwei Anutu luk en e eivek poropet Yesaya mya yo:
\q1 “Tambiy ti vya taxe lam anghei tembuing bandaing nei,
\q1 ‘Menyex wou sakwaing en Tambiy Ngandoung,
\q2 wong sakwaing on wo bombek en e.’” \rq Yesaya 40:3\rq*
\p 
\v 4 Yoan xe teimb on xel duw angya leliy kamel nivlus, me mi vex let wei xel duw en leliy ninavi yo vivekwou xeikatu. E xeeng yaeing on zevak me beyexta nilouk wei qeis lalei yo.
\v 5 Xomaxoneing nanghei Yerusalem me nanghei Yudia tambak nei me danghei dalus wei memiing Yorodan vi eno xel lam wou e.
\v 6 Xel neil xel xe sewokeing teyei, de Yoan lipek xel eivek memiing Yorodan.
\p 
\v 7 Ekom moxo yei xel ngenong wei Parisi me Sadyusi lam en embei qou lipekeing, moxo neil wou xel: “Xam on myeiy nilul neu! Eti neil wou xam bei tyek xam a pek me ghe na veil Anutu lalei vanei wei di lam o?
\v 8 Wangwei xam pekwi xow neing nei yon kwa wei xam eno talex lek bei xam ghe pekwi xow.
\v 9 De xam seng boueivek naleimim me na neil wou venaxow bei, ‘Xa mami Apraham.’ A neil wou xam bei Anutu teyei bei bong qakous beimambei ne qandi lek me ghok ambei Apraham neuyeiw.
\v 10 Qov di yeip wou xax qes woy, om xax tambak wei se mi vuk neing nimza eno tyek xel buv veil me banex ena eivek nenyex.
\p 
\v 11 “A lipek xam en memiing bei xam pekwi xow. Ekom Tambiy tiwei tyek nam yus en ay eno e nikanzek ghanaw a veil, a se nimza teyei bei qalei e xe vaxalambes. Moxo tyek zipek xam en Laweeng Vambuing me nenyex is.
\v 12 Moxo zeim taliv eivek mema, en embei seyex wit en beyal myapapu veil wit neing, de qekuwou me na toung eivek xomek yaeing, ekom moxo tyek banyuw myapapu lek nenyex wei se mi mey yo.”
\s1 Yoan lipek Yesu
\p 
\v 13 Woyom Yesu lam anghei Galili me la Yorodan bei Yoan zipek e.
\v 14 Ekom Yoan embei paseisexe e me neil, “Teyei bei a qou lipekeing wou wang, nambei nya wang lam wou ay?”
\p 
\v 15 Yesu neil elox, “Embong ondek wang bong ambei a neil ne, eivek kwa nimza tine uw teyei bei bong sakwaing dalus embo bombek.” Om Yoan betiwou e xe qayeeng.
\p 
\v 16 Ka Yesu lipek woy, moxo lek lam veil memiing. Gyeik kayon bombek eno tyoung gheyapu tax, de moxo yei Anutu xe Laweeng Vambuing lam ambei menek beliy me dei lek e.
\v 17 Vya ti lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei me neil, “Tine inye a Neung Moux, wei a laleing vind o. A laleing wo xeilala en e.”
\c 4
\s1 Sandang wo axeing wou Yesu
\p 
\v 1 Woyom Laweeng Vambuing qou Yesu me la tembuing bandaing nei bei tambiy mapetok bo axeing wou e.
\v 2 Yesu vambu yaeing teyei lek bendiyeing mepyeiyuw me boukeing mepyeiyuw is om maxepya e.
\v 3 Tambiy mapetok wei mi wo axeing eno lam wou e me neil, “Wangwei wa Anutu Neu Moux, ond neil me qakous ti beimambei ne pekwi nambei belet.”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu neil elox, “Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye: ‘Xomaxoneing se mindei mapieing en belet venaxow, qe xel mi dei mapieing en qayeeng tambak wei mi lam eivek Anutu mya yo.’ ” \rq Petieing 8:3\rq*
\p 
\v 5 Woyom tambiy mapetok qou e me la beyeeng vambuing Yerusalem me wong e nale lek xomek vambuing on pundanghou.
\v 6 Moxo neil, “Wangwei wang on Anutu Neu Moux ond vyeip me la tembuing. En xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye,
\q1 “‘Moxo tyek bong qayeeng nikanzek wou e xe angela en xel gyeiteyei wang,
\q2 me tyek xel a zeim wang zekna eivek memend,
\q1 en kandek qakous ti se byex wa vaxam.’ ” \rq Qapiya Lalo 91:11-12\rq*
\p 
\v 7 Yesu neil elox wou e, “Inyon xel byex eivek xoulek is bei: ‘Wa se toung wa xe Tambiy Ngandoung Anutu eivek axeing.’” \rq Petieing 6:16\rq*
\p 
\v 8 Kalekom tambiy mapetok qou e me la lek lukendu vaxading. De talex tete lalei wei tembuing sapa me lulul nimzamza dalus eno wou e.
\v 9 E neil, “Wangwei wang dev vaxam qatu eivek me ghe bong lalo wou a nei on tyek am bong lul dalus tine wou wang.”
\p 
\v 10 Ekom Yesu neil wou e, “Sandang, la dingta veil ay! En xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye, ‘Wang bong lalo wou Tambiy Ngandoung wa xe Anutu me ghe bong xuk wou e venaxow.’ ” \rq Petieing 6:13\rq*
\p 
\v 11 Woyom tambiy mapetok la veil e, dom angela lam me vind e.
\s1 Yesu xe xuk teyoxeing tiwei tax o
\p 
\v 12 Ka Yesu ngo bei xel toung Yoan eivek xeitueing, moxo lox me la Galili.
\v 13 De la veil Nasaret, me la dei eivek Kapenaom, wei di yeip wou lounyeing Galili vi yo, eivek tembuing wei Sebulon me Naptali.
\v 14 Eivek kwa tine eno Yesu wong e la teyei lek ambei qayeeng wei Anutu neil eivek poropet Yesaya mya yo:
\q1 
\v 15 “Tembuing wei Sebulon me tembuing wei Naptali,
\q2 eno di yeip wou lounyeing vi, me la valu wei Yorodan nei,
\q2 me tembuing wei Galili wei xel amba lam dei lek o.
\q1 
\v 16 Om xomaxoneing wei mindei eivek mapetok ngandoung eno yei xeiyaing ngandoung ti.
\q1 Me xel wei mindei eivek mapetok eno
\q2 xeiyaing byex la lek xel.” \rq Yesaya 9:1-2\rq*
\p 
\v 17 Lek bouk tiyon eno Yesu neil qayeeng atax wou xel, “Xam pekwi xow, en tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno lam paviy.”
\s1 Yesu taxe xel betiyeing tiwei tax o
\p 
\v 18 Bouk ti eno Yesu la ghavineeng wou lounyeing Galili nenyawes, yei tambiy yayuw wei lindama yo, inyon Simon xel mi taxe bei Petele luw li Andrias. Luw di nex lewek eivek lounyeing, en nambei xel on ingwei mi qou woing o.
\v 19 Woyom Yesu neil, “Muw lam me betiwou ay, en tyek a bong muw a qou xomaxoneing nambei muw ghe mi qou woing o.”
\v 20 Lutika eno luw ghanaw luw xe lewek dom betiwou e.
\p 
\v 21 Yesu la no, me yei tambiy yayuw inyon Jems wei Sebedi neu moux me li Yoan. Luw toundei eivek bot is ma teiv Sebedi, me di menyex wou lal xe lewek. Woyom Yesu taxe la wou luw.
\v 22 Se wo lululek en luw ghanaw luw xe bot me ma teiv dom betiwou e.
\s1 Yesu wong xel wei vanei eno wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 23 Yesu la ghavineeng eivek Galili tambak, me di teyoxe xel eivek xomek qekueing ama wei Yudayeiw o, me moxo di neil Xoulek Nimza wei tete lalei, me wong xel wei vanei leimalei eno wo nimzalek eivek xel xomaxoneing on senghoing.
\v 24 Yesu xe pavulek la wo sapa eivek Siria, me xomaxoneing qou xel dalus wei vanei leimalei wong xel o me lam wou e, eti yeiw wei vanei nilul is vanei ngandoung, me laweeng nilul dei eivek xel me xel wei vanei wei nietekeing mi wong xel mi pewilexe lek tembuing me xel wei kanzek mey eno Yesu wong xel wo nimzalek.
\v 25 Xel qendu ngandoung wei betiy e eno lam anghei Galili me Dekapolis, me Yerusalem, me Yudia me Yorodan loxalu nei.
\c 5
\s1 Yesu neil qayeeng lek lukendu
\p 
\v 1 Yesu yei xel qendu ngandoung on lam, om moxo lek la lukendu nenyawes. Ka e la dei, e xe xel betiyeing lam wou e.
\v 2 Om moxo teyoxe wou xel me neil,
\v 3 “Anutu bo mata wou xel wei woulek bei xel kanyo eivek nund laweeng o, en tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno inyon xel xe.
\p 
\v 4 “Anutu wong mata la wou eti yeiw wei mi wo talot o, en tyek bo xel laleind vevop.
\p 
\v 5 “Anutu wong mata la wou eti yeiw wei mi beoux xow o, en tyek bong tembuing tambak wou xel.
\p 
\v 6 “Anutu wong mata la wou eti yeiw wei mindei maxep me kwend mi tip en sakwaing bombek o, en tyek bong e na teyei lek wou xel.
\v 7 Anutu wong mata la wou eti yeiw wei lalei pyaweing o en tyek talex lalei pyaweing wou xel.
\v 8 Anutu wong mata la wou eti yeiw wei laleind wo vako yo, en tyek xel gyei Anutu.
\p 
\v 9 “Anutu bo mata wou eti yeiw wei mi leis qayeeng mey me wo lalei vevopeing wou xomaxoneing o, en tyek xel taxe xel bei Anutu neuyeiw.
\p 
\v 10 “Anutu bo mata wou eti yeiw wei mi qou nimaying en sakwaing bombek o, en tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno inyon xel xe.
\p 
\v 11 “Anutu bo mata wou xam gyeik xel xomaxoneing embei bo nol wou xam o me na neil qayeeng nilul lek xam, me bo nimaying me tyonyeing lek xam me na neil qayeeng leimalei dalus wei nilul o lek xam en xam ghe mi betiwou ay.
\v 12 Xam laleimim embo nimza me ghe bong xeimimlala, en xam xe xouveing ngandoung toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu, en eivek sakwaing ambei nyon eno xel wo nimaying wou xel poropet eti yeiw wei la tax en xam o.
\s1 Xam on nambei mileeng me xeiyaing
\p 
\v 13 “Xam on nambei mileeng wei tembuing o. Ekom wangwei nenyeing wei mileeng on na ma, on tyek xam ghe bong vati wou me mileeng enox bong nenyeing no? Inyon tyek se nox bo nimza no, om xam banex ena myayaing me xel xomaxoneing bakei lek.
\p 
\v 14 “Xam on xeiyaing wei tembuing sapa yo. Beyeeng ngandoung wei toukale lek qetyei eno se teyei bei ghupek.
\v 15 Xomaxoneing se mi byex eivek lam me toung ela xeinghembi eivek dipek. Qe xel mi lax lek vaxa wei mi nale lek o, me mi wong xeiyaing wou xel dalus wei mindei eivek xomek lalei yo.
\v 16 Om nambei nyon eno xam ghe bong xam xe xeiyaing etel atax wou xomaxoneing mendghalus, en kandek xel gyei xam xe kwa nimza yon me sanghoxe xam Mamim lei eivek tyoung gheyapu.
\s1 Qayeeng petieing wo neing lek
\p 
\v 17 “Xam seng bou kwamim bei a lam bei semaleeng qayeeng petieing veil o qayeeng poropet. A se lam bei semaleeng qe a lam bei bong embo neing lek.
\v 18 A neil wou xam zonghek, ka tyoung gheyapu luw tembuing nati, tyek qayeeng nayaka ti tyek se nati, o dee nayak wei xel byex eno tyek se nati veil petieing qe ka lulul dalus na teyei lek bole.
\v 19 Om wangwei xelti embei gyei qayeeng petieing ne nayak ti nambei lul bandaing me na teyoxe xel valu me xel bong ambei nyon, eno tyek e lei bo nayaka eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei, ekom eti yeiw wei mi betiwou me teyoxe xel moux alis vex en petieing o, eno tyek xel a neil e lei bo ngandoung eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 20 Om a neil wou xam bei wangwei xam se betiwou kwa bombek wei Anutu xe yo, me xam xe kwa bombek se ghanaw kwa bombek wei xel Parisi me xel putoung wei petieing, ond xam seng teyei being na eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo.
\s1 Qayeeng wei leiseing xel a mey o
\p 
\v 21 “Xam ghe ngo bei inyon qayeeng wei xel neil wou bumyeiw on takwei nei yo, ‘Xam seng nyeis xel amey, me e tiwei leis nge mey eno tyek bale lek qayeeng.’ Qou e loum 20:13
\v 22 Ekom a neil wou xam eti yeiw wei laleind mi wo myavanei wou liyeiw ba eno tyek bale lek qayeeng. A neil no, eti yeiw wei neil qayeeng nol lek liyeiw ba eno tyek na gyei lei ngandoung wei kanzol o. Ekom wangwei tambiy ti e neil, ‘Wang on bandol!’ eno tyek na eivek nenyex wei beyeeng nilul o.
\p 
\v 23 “Nambei nyon om wangwei wa being na toung xound lek qeind, ekom wang wou naleim bei lim neil qayeeng ti lek wang,
\v 24 ond wa toung wa xe da e na mya wou qeind. De wang nox me na bole me menyex qayeeng is lim, woyom wang noum me ghe na toung wa xe da.
\p 
\v 25 “Wa menyex wou qayeeng daing is tambiy wei embei qou wang me na bong qayeeng en wang o. Wang bong inye gyeik ingwei muw anghei di la wou sakwaing o, enok na qou wang me na wou tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng o, me tambiy wei mi ngo qayeeng eno bong wang na wou beyeiv, me xel a toung wang na eivek xeitueing.
\v 26 A neil wou wang zonghek, tyek wa seng teyei bei na myayaing, qe ka wa dexouv xomek xeitueing en wa xe malew kayo dalus bole.
\s1 Qayeeng wei kwapesiv o
\p 
\v 27 “Xam ghe ngo qayeeng wei xel neil o, ‘Xam seng bo kwapesiv.’ Qou e Loum 20:14
\v 28 Ekom a neil wou xam bei eti yeiw wei mi yei vex me lalei mi zeim e lek en vex eno inyon wong kwapesiv is e woy eivek lalei.
\v 29 Wangwei wa mam payeiv bo wang bong sewokeing, ond wa qepei veil me banex ena. Inye nimza bei wa saing neing ti na veil de xel se banex wa neing dalus na eivek beyeeng wei nilul o.
\v 30 Me wangwei wa memam payeiv e bo wang bong sewokeing, ond qateiv veil me nex ela. Inye nimza bei wa saing neing ti de xel se banex wa neing dalus na eivek beyeeng wei nilul o.
\s1 Qayeeng wei qateiveing iingama yo
\p 
\v 31 “E neil is ambei nye, ‘Xelti embei qateiv luw venei xe iingama ond e bong qapiya wei qateiveing iingama yo ti wou e.’ \rq Petieing 24:1\rq*
\v 32 Ekom a neil wou xam, eti bei qateiv iingama wei luw venei, gyeik venei se wo kwa nol, ond wo venei wong ambei vex wei mi wo kwapesiv o, me eti bei dii vex wei qateiv iingama eno wo kwapesiv is e.”
\s1 Xam se neil zonghek is inyapunei
\p 
\v 33 Yesu neil no, “Xam ghe ngo bei inyon xel neil wou bumyeiw takwei nei, ‘Wa se pyalek qayeeng wei wang neil zonghek is inyapunei yo, qe xam ghe gweiteyei qayeeng zonghek is inyapunei wei xam ghe neil wou Tambiy Ngandoung o.’
\v 34 Ekom a neil wou xam, xam se neil qayeeng zonghek is inyapunei. Xam se neil tyoung gheyapu nei bei byexaxoun qayeeng ti, en inye Anutu xe siaking,
\v 35 o xam se neil lek tembuing, en inye e xe pom wei mi lax vaxa lek o, o xam se neil lek Yerusalem, en inyon beyeeng ngandoung wei King wei ghanaw veil o.
\v 36 Me wa se neil qayeeng zonghek is inyapunei lek lumkanzek, en wa seng teyei bei bong lum velus ti bo teleing o bo ngak.
\v 37 Qe wa mou neimbei ‘E’ o wa neimbei ‘Ma.’ Qayeeng wei xel mi tetulexe eno lam wou tambiy kawei nilul o.
\s1 Xam seng bong myaveweeng nox me na
\p 
\v 38 “Xam ghe ngo qayeeng wei xel neil o woy, ‘Wangwei xelti embo nol wou wa mamghalus, ond wang bo nol wou e manghalus is ambei nyon, me wangwei xelti qatuw wa newoum apek ond wa qatuw e newou pek is ambei nyon.’ \rq Qouloum 21:24\rq*
\v 39 Ekom a neil wou xam bei xam seng bong myaveweeng nox wou xel wei nilul o. Wangwei xelti petapexe wa ling nge payeiv, ond wa pekwi ling valu nox wou e is.
\v 40 Me wangwei xelti embei bo qayeeng en wang me na qou wa xe teimb, ond wang bong e qou wa xe teimb ding is.
\v 41 Wangwei tambiy ti tendu wang bei wa qalei e xe qoupek me ghe na teyei lek kilomita ti, ond wang na is e teyei lek kilomita yuw.
\v 42 Wangwei tambiy ti teling wang en lulti yon wang bong wou e, de tambiy ti embei qou lulti wou wang dekakom bong enoum on wa se pesek.
\s1 Wa laleim devind xel vevek amba
\p 
\v 43 “Wang ngo ingwei xel neil o woy, ‘Wa laleim devind nimpapu de ghe gwei xel wei vevek amba bo nol.’
\v 44 Ekom a neil wou wang, wa laleim devind xel wei vevek amba yo me na zeimemam en eti yeiw wei embei bo nol wou wang o,
\v 45 om nambei nyon xam on tyek mendei nambei Mang wei toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu yo neuyeiw, eno moxo mi wong sayeiv mi siing lek xel nilul me nimza, me wong luing mi tei lek xel wei bombek o me xel wei se bombek o is.
\v 46 Wangwei wa laleim devind eti yeiw wei laleind mi vind wang, on tyek wa qou xouveing vati? Beip xel wei mi qou takis eno se mi wong inyon?
\v 47 Me wangwei wa neil bendiyeing wou limyeiw venaxow, on tyek wa qou lul vati ghanaw xel valu? Xel wei mendalus eno se mi wong inyon is?
\v 48 Xam a mi mendei embo nimzayang, nambei xam Mamim wei tyoung gheyapu mindei nimzayang o.
\c 6
\s1 Vineing xel wei kanyo yo
\p 
\v 1 “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en xam seng bong xam xe kwa wei bombek o eivek xel xomaxoneing mend bei xel gyei. Wangwei xam ghe bong ambei nyon nei, ond tyek xam se qou xouveing ti wou xam Mamim eivek tyoung gheyapu nei.
\p 
\v 2 “Om wa being bong lul wou xel wei kanyo yo, ond wa se neil me xel davei vuk me natax en wang nambei xel wei myend yuw mi wong eivek xomek qekueing ama me sakwaing mema nayak, bei xel xomaxoneing bo lei ngandoung wou xel o. A neil wou xam zonghek bei, xel qou nind xouveing dalus woy.
\v 3 Ekom gyeik wa being bong wou xel wei kanyo yo, wa seng bong wa memam qeinz boulek vati wei wa memam payeiv embei bong o,
\v 4 en kandek wa xe wongeing e mi mendei xupekeing. Woyom Mam yei vati wei wang wong xupekeing o, eno tyek bong xouveing wou wang.
\s1 Kwa wei zeimeing mema yo
\p 
\v 5 “Me gyeik wa bei zeimemam, wa seng bong ambei xel wei myend yuw o, en xel laleind mi vind bei na mi bale me na zeim memend eivek xomek qekueing ama me na mi bale wou sakwaing nayak en kandek moux alis vex a mi gyei xel. A neil wou xam zonghek bei, xel qou nind xouveing dalus woy.
\v 6 Ekom gyeik wa bei zeimemam, ond wang na eivek bam lalei me na toung qapomb zeyi dom na zeimemam wou Mam, wei mi dei xupekeing o. Woyom Mam wei mi yei vati wei mindei xupekeing, eno tyek bong xouveing wou wang.
\v 7 Me gyeik xam a bei zeimemamim, xam se zeimemamim ding nambei xel wei mandalus mi wong o, en xel wou naleind bei tyek Anutu na ngo xel xe qayeeng ngenongakes on.
\v 8 Xam seng ghok xel, gyeik ingwei wa seng ghei teling wou e yo, eno xam Mamim woulek woy en vati wei wambei teling wou e yo.
\p 
\v 9 “Woyom tine inye xam a bei zeimemamim eno nambei nye:
\q1 “ ‘Xa Mami eivek tyoung gheyapu,
\q1 wa leim e mi mendei vambuing.
\q1 
\v 10 Wa xe tete lalei e nam.
\q1 Xa teyei bei betiwou wa laleim
\q2 lek tembuing, nambei xel mi betiwou nanghei tyoung gheyapu yon.
\q1 
\v 11 Gweimbeeng wang bong xami yaeing wei bouk titi eno wou xa.
\q2 
\v 12 Wa semaleeng sewokeing wei xa yo,
\q2 xa is ambei nyon xa semaleeng sewokeing wei xel ba mi wong wou xa yo.
\q1 
\v 13 Me wa se qou xa na eivek axeing,
\q1 qe wa qou xa veil tambiy nilul on.’
\m 
\v 14 En wangwei wa semaleeng sewokeing wei xomaxoneing wong wou wang o, on tyek Mam wei toundei tyoung gheyapu nei tyek semaleeng wa xe sewokeing is.
\v 15 Ekom wangwei wa se semaleeng xomaxoneing nge xe sewokeing veil, ond tyek Mam se semaleeng wa xe sewokeing is.
\s1 Kwa wei vambueing yaeing o
\p 
\v 16 “Gyeik wambei vambu yaeing, ond wa seng gweimam nol nambei xel wei myend yuw mi wong o, en xel mi wo mend nol me talex wou xel moux alis vex bei xel vambu yaeing. A neil wou xam zonghek, xel qou nind xouveing dalus woy.
\v 17 Ekom gyeik wambei vambu yaeing, on wa pelei wel lek lum me davu mam,
\v 18 om wa seng bong kwa wei vambuing yaing gyeip yaeing wou xomaxoneing mendghalus. Ma, wang bong wou Mam manghalus wei mindei xupekeing o. Mam wei toundei xupekeing eno venaxow mi woulek, vati wei xel mi wong xupekeing o, eno tyek bong xouveing wou wang.
\s1 Lul nimzamza eivek tyoung gheyapu
\p 
\v 19 “Xam se qekuwou xam xe lulul nimzamza lek tembuing ne, wei xevek me niyeis mi wo nol wou yo, me xel wei panaxeing o mi dembu xomek me panax.
\v 20 Ekom xam a mi qekuwou xam xe lulul nimzamza e na eivek tyoung gheyapu nei, wei xevek me niyeis se teyei bei bo nol wou, me panaxana se teyei bei dembu me na lalei me panax.
\v 21 En nanghei ingwei wa xe lul nimza toundei ghei yo, eno wa laleim tyek na mendei is ambei nyon.
\s1 Xe mendghalus ne lam wei xe neing o
\p 
\v 22 “Xe mendghalus ne lam wei xe neing o. Wangwei wa mam on nimza, on wa neing dalus on tyek na pup en xeiyaing.
\v 23 Ekom wangwei wa mam aluw on nilul, yon wa neing dalus on tyek bo mapetok. Om wangwei xeiyaing wei toundei eivek wang on bo mapetok, yon mapetok on tyek bong ngandoung eivek wang mouyo!
\p 
\v 24 “Tambiy ti se teyei bei bo xuk wou teiv yayuw. Moxo tyek lalei bo nol wou nge, de lalei devind nge, me tyek na mi ngo e xe qayeeng, de na toung demi wou nge. Wa seng teyeimbei bong xuk wou Anutu me malew is.
\s1 Xam se bou naleimim ngenong
\p 
\v 25 “Nambei nyon a neil wou xam bei, xam seng bounaleim ngenong en mapieing wei xam o me na neimbei, ‘Tyek xey a gha vati? O na num va? De xe neing eno tyek xey a byex vati?’ Mapieing ne ngandoung ghanaw yaeing, me neing ne ngandoung ghanaw teimb.
\v 26 Xam ghe gwei menek menek wei senghoing bandaing nei, xel se mi xen o se mi qekuwou o toung lulul eivek xomek yaeing. Ekom xam Mamim wei toundei tyoung gheyapu nei eno mi vet xel. Beip xam seng ghanaw menek menek on veil, ei?
\v 27 Eti yeiw wei mi wou naleind ngenong eno teyei bei tetulexe seivma nayaka lek e xe mapieing?
\p 
\v 28 “Me xam ghe di wou naleimim ngenong en teimb en va? Xam ghe gwei qapaing mavya wei toungale yon. Xel se mi wong pok o duw teimb.
\v 29 Ekom a neil wou xam bei Salomo mi vunek en lul nimzamza, ekom e xe vunekeing nimza yon se nambei qapaing mavya ti beimambei ne.
\v 30 Wangwei inye Anutu mi vunekwou qeis qeis wei xuk o nambei nyon, ond inyon gweimbeeng me yanyeing eno xel mi nex ela eivek nenyex. Beip moxo se mi vunekwou xam? Xam on xe wongeingis on nayaka.
\v 31 Om xam seng bounaleim ngenong, me na neimbei, ‘Tyek xey a gha vati?’ o ‘Tyek xey a num vati?’ o ‘Tyek xey a bunek en vati?’
\v 32 En xel wei mendalus eno mi yimexe lul dalus ti beimambei ne, de xam Mamim wei tyoung gheyapu eno woulek woy en vati wei xam a bei qou yo.
\v 33 Ekom xam ghe gwimexe e xe tete lalei me e xe sakwaing bombek bole, de lulul dalus ti beimambei ne eno tyek bong wou xam is ambei nyon.
\v 34 Nambei nyon xam seng bou naleimim en yanyeing, en yanyeing tyek bounalei en venaxow. Nimaying wei bouk titi eno teyei lek bouk tiyon venaxow.
\c 7
\s1 Xam seng gwei xel nge xe kwa me baluk en
\p 
\v 1 “Xam seng gwei xel nge xe kwa me baluk en, enok Anutu bong kwa nambei nyon wou xam is.
\v 2 En eivek sakwaing kawei xam ghe wei xel nge me ghe luk en e, eno tyek Anutu bong kwa nambei nyon wou xam, me vati wei xam ghe mi wong wou xel nge yo, tyek Anutu bong ambei nyon wou xam is.
\p 
\v 3 “Wang wei myasa wei dei eivek lim nge ma yon en va, de wa seng wei pelang wei di yeip eivek wamaxow mam on?
\v 4 Inye nambei nya wang neil wou lim, ‘Wong a laluwexe myasa yon lam myayaing veil wa mamghalus,’ de pelang wei toundei eivek wamaxow mamghalus on?
\v 5 Wa tambiy wei wa myam yuw o, myaxeeng eno wa laluwexe pelang veil venaxow mamghalus bole, woyom tyek wang gwei embo nimza me laluwexe myasa veil lim manghalus.
\p 
\v 6 “Xam se qou lul wei vambuing wei xel wong wou Anutu yo me ghe bong wou xel naw on, me wa se banex wa xe viyaviy na wou xel bok on. Wangwei wang bong nei, tyek xel bakei lek angya vaxend, de woyom tyek xel pekwi me noum wou xam me zanga xam ghe bo tiptip.
\s1 Xam teling, de xam ghe gwimexe, de ghe nyeis memam lek qapomb
\p 
\v 7 “Xam teling on tyek bong wou xam. Xam ghe gwimexe on tyek xam ghe gweiwou. Xam ghe nyeis memamim lek qapomb on tyek natax veil xam.
\v 8 En xel dalus wei mi teling eno mi qou, me eti mi yimexe eno mi yeiwou, me eti yeiw wei mi leis memend lek qapomb eno tyek natax.
\p 
\v 9 “Xam eti yeiw, wangwei e neu moux teling wou en belet, tyek wang bong qakous ti wou e?
\v 10 O wangwei e teling wou wang en woing, tyek wang bong myeiy ti wou e?
\v 11 Xam mayeiw on nilul, ekom xam ghe mi wong lul nimza wou neumyeiw, om xam Mamim wei toundei tyoung gheyapu nei tyek bong lul nimza wou eti yeiw wei mi teling wou e yo!
\v 12 Om kwa tambak wei wambei xel bamba bong wou wang eno wang bong ambei nyon wou xel, eno tine inye qayeeng qes wei petieing o me qayeeng qes wei xel poropet o.
\s1 Tete mya nayak me ngandoung
\p 
\v 13 “Xam a mi na nox tete mya nayak. En tete mya wei ngandoung me sakwaing ngandoung eno inyon la wou beyeeng wei qoueing nilul o, me xel ngenong eno mi la lox.
\v 14 Ekom tete mya nayak me sakwaing nayak on la wou beyeeng wei mapieing o, me moux alis vex nuyuw ka mi yei me betiwou.
\s1 Xax ti is neing
\p 
\v 15 “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en poropet wei tyonyeing. Xel mi lam wou xam eivek teimb wei sipsip nivlus o, ekom xel laleind ond xok ambei naw bemeeng.
\v 16 Nangya xel xe kwa yon tyek xam ghe boulek e neing. Beip xel xomaxoneing mi qou xax wain neing lek qeis wei niying o, o xel mi qou xax basunghek lek qeis wei nileli yo?
\v 17 Nambei nyon xax sapa wei nimza eno mi vuk neing nimza, dom xax nilul mi vuk neing nilul.
\v 18 Xax nimza ti se teyei bei buk neing nilul, o xax nilul ti se teyei bei buk neing nimza.
\v 19 Xax sapa wei se mi vuk neing nimza eno xel mi vuv veil me nex ela eivek nenyex.
\v 20 Om tyek xam ghe gwei lek xel xe neing me ghe boulek xel.
\p 
\v 21 “Se xel dalus wei mi taxe a bei, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, Tambiy Ngandoung,’ eno tyek na eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo, qe eti yeiw wei mi wong e betiwou Mang wei tyoung gheyapu yo lalei.
\v 22 Xel ngenong tyek na neil wou ay lek bouk kayon, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, Tambiy Ngandoung, beip xa se mi neil qayeeng poropet eivek wa leim, me eivek wa leim eno xa mi tiy memo la myayaing me na wong lulvako ngenong?’
\v 23 Woyom tyek a neil wou xel bombek, ‘A se woulek xam nayaka. Xam wei ghe mi wo kwa nilul, xam la veil ay!’
\s1 Kamunda wei lupeyei me lupeyei maeing o
\p 
\v 24 “Nambei nyon xel sapa wei mi ngo a xe qayeeng tine me mi betiwou eno inye nambei tambiy lupeyei wei ev beeng lek qakous o.
\v 25 Luing tei, me memiing butek, me laweeng vei xomek wo pimapi, ekom xomek se qepei me teila, en nambei mundeeng on nale nikanzek eivek qakous.
\v 26 Ekom eti yeiw wei se mi ngo a xe qayeeng ti beimambei ne me betiwou, eno nambei tambiy wei ev xomek lek luzeeng bandaing o.
\v 27 Luing tei, me memiing butek, me laweeng vei xomek wo pimapi, om xomek qepei me teila niseikeing.”
\p 
\v 28 Yesu neil qayeeng ti beimambei ne ma woy, xel qendu ngandoung on etek en e xe qayeeng wei di teyoxe yo,
\v 29 en moxo teyoxe xel teyei lek tambiy wei lei ngandoung o, de se nambei xel xe putoung wei petieing o.
\c 8
\s1 Tambiy wei vanei lepa yo
\p 
\v 1 Moxo di loum axone veil lukendu, eno xel qendu ngandoung ti betiwou e.
\v 2 De tambiy ti is vanei lepa eno lam ev vaxakatu eivek wou e me neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei wa laleim devind nei, yon wang bong am bo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 3 Yesu tatei mema la me axlek e, de neil, “A laleing vind! Wang bo vako.” Lutika eno moxo xe vanei lepa yon ma veil e.
\v 4 Woyom Yesu neil wou e, “Wang wei inyon dom wa se neil wou xelti. Qe la, me talex xow wou lumuki me toung xound teyei lek Mose neil o, en xel boulek pavulek ne bei wa xe myavanei yon ma.”
\s1 Lei ngandoung wei vevek o xe wongeingis
\p 
\v 5 Ka Yesu la eivek beyeeng Kapenaom, beyeiv wei mi yeiteyei 100 vevekyeiw eno ti lam wou e me teling wou en vineing.
\v 6 Moxo neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, a xe xukxe eno vanei wong om di yeip lek zek eivek xomek lalei. Moxo kanzek mey me di axe vanei ngandoung.”
\p 
\v 7 Yesu neil wou e, “Tyek a nak me na bong embo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 8 Ekom beyeiv neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, a se nimza bei wang nam eivek a bang lalei. Qe wa mou neil qayeeng dom a xe xukxe e bo nimzalek.
\v 9 En a maxow ne a mindei kwanghembi eivek xel wei wo leind ngandoung o, me xel vevek mindei kwanghembi eivek ay. Wangwei a neil wou tine, ‘La,’ ond moxo la. De na neil wou nge yon, ‘Lam,’ ond moxo lam. Me a neil wou a xe xukxe, ‘Wong tine,’ ond moxo mi wong.”
\p 
\v 10 Yesu ngo qayeeng tine, moxo etek mouyo me neil wou eti yeiw wei di betiwou e yon, “A neil wou xam zonghek, a se mi xei tambiy ti eivek Israel eno xe wongeingis ambei nye.
\v 11 A neil wou xam bei inyon xel ngenong tyek nam anghei ninei me xeinei, me nam mendei me gya mata ngandoung on is Apraham aluw Isaka lal Yakop eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 12 Ekom xomaxoneing wei Israel wei tete lalei eno tyek Anutu banex xel na myayaing eivek mapetok ngandoung, nanghei inyon eno tyek xel bong talot ngandoung me dexound newound bo nyiknyik.”
\p 
\v 13 Woyom Yesu neil wou beyeiv, “La! En tyek na tyip ambei ingwei wang wongis bei etyip o.” De e xe xukxe wo nimzalek seivma kayon.
\s1 Yesu wong xel ngenong wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 14 Woyom Yesu lam eivek Petele xe xomek, moxo yei Petele yeing avexta gying wong me e di yeip lek zek.
\v 15 Moxo axlek e mema de gying on ma veil e, me vexo qandi lek me di menyex lulul wou e.
\p 
\v 16 Soukeing tiyon, eno xel ngenong wei memo dei eivek xel eno liyeiw qou xel me lam wou Yesu. Me e neil de xel laweeng nilul on la myayaing me wong xel ngenong wei vanei eno wo nimzalek.
\v 17 De kwa tine la teyei lek vati wei Anutu neil eivek poropet Yesaya mya yo:
\q1 “E maxow qou xe xe myavanei leimalei
\q2 me semaleeng xe xe vanei leimalei veil.” \rq Yesaya 53:4\rq*
\s1 Yesu neil en nimaying wei betiyeing wou e yo
\p 
\v 18 Gyeik Yesu yei xel qendu ngandoung wei nale vivekwou e yon, moxo neil nikanzek wou xel betiyeing bei, “Xey a na nge loxalu wei lounyeing nei.”
\v 19 Woyom putoung wei petieing o ti eno lam wou e me neil, “Putoung, wambei mi na inya yo eno tyek a betiwou wang.”
\p 
\v 20 Yesu neil elox bei, “Xel naw bemeeng xe eeng me menek menek xe lewis, ekom Xomaxoneing Neu Moux xe beyeeng wei embei ni lu lek eno ma.”
\p 
\v 21 Betiyeing nge neil wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wong a la ev mang wole.”
\v 22 Ekom Yesu neil wou e, “Wa betiwou ay, dom wong xel meyeing di ev xel venaxow xe meyeing.”
\s1 Yesu neil dom laweeng valeivek on tip
\p 
\v 23 Woyom moxo la eivek bot de e xe xel betiyeing betiwou e.
\v 24 Se wo lululek, qe laweeng ngandoung ti tyip wou xel lek lounyeing masenghoing, omek laweeng vei lounyeing lam embei sevunexe bot is xel. Ekom Yesu vena di yeip.
\v 25 Xel betiyeing la me piyexe e, me neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, vind xa! Xey am bim a qou nilul ne!”
\p 
\v 26 Moxo neil elox, “Xam xe wongeingis on nayaka, nambei nya xam ghe waleeng?” Woyom moxo qandi lek me luk nikanzek wou laweeng me mamileeng wei di vuk me lam on yeip kanzek, me wo nimza no.
\p 
\v 27 Xel moux on etek me teling, “Tambiy tine e vati? Om memiing aluw laweeng ngo e vya!”
\s1 Yesu tiy memo veil tambiy yayuw
\p 
\v 28 Ka Yesu la tei lounyeing nge loxalu wei Gadarayeiw xe tembuing nei, eno moux yayuw wei memo dei eivek luw eno lam myayaing veil eeng wei xel qateiv eivek qakous o me lam wou e. Tambiy yuw on bemeeng om xelti se teyei bei na nox sakwaing tiyon.
\v 29 Woyom luw ghak, “Anutu Neu Moux, wa being bo vati wou uw? Beip wang lam inye bei bo nol wou uw de bouk anghei?”
\p 
\v 30 Bok qendu ngandoung ti di ya ghei dingta ka nanghei inyon en xel.
\v 31 Laweeng nol yon tay wou Yesu, “Wangwei wa tiy xa na myayaing nei, on wong xa la eivek bok qendu ngandoung nei.”
\p 
\v 32 Moxo neil wou xel, “Xam la!” Om xel lam myayaing me la eivek xel bok on, me bok qendu tiyon dalus veimyend me la oing mazanghei me heivek lounyeing de mey eivek memiing.
\v 33 Xel wei mi yeiteyei bok on yei tine, om xel veimyend me la eivek beyeeng on me neil qayeeng dalus en tine, me vati wei belup wou moux yuw wei memo mindei eivek luw o.
\v 34 Woyom xel tambak wei beyeeng on la wou Yesu. Me gyeik xel yei e, xel luk nikanzek wou e bei ena veil xel xe tembuing.
\c 9
\s1 Yesu wong tambiy wei bezomb eno wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 1 Yesu lek la eivek bot ti, me la nge loxalu nei me la tyip emaxow beeng qes.
\v 2 Xel valu qou tambiy bezombeing ti wei xel liw lek lelek o me lam. Yesu yei xel xe wongeingis, om neil wou tambiy wei bezomb on, “A neung, wa qou laleim vevopeing. A semaleeng wa xe sewokeing veil.”
\p 
\v 3 Xel putoung valu wei petieing eno xel neil wou ma en tine bei, “Tambiy tine embei qou Anutu nimbeeng!”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu woulek xel xe woueing nalei me neil, “Xam ghe di wou naleimim nilul eivek laleimim enva?
\v 5 Qayeeng tina inye xeiles bei a neil: ‘A semaleeng wa xe nilul,’ o a neimbei, ‘Qandi lek me la’?
\v 6 Ekom inyon xam ghe boulek bei, Xomaxoneing Neu Moux wo lei ngandoung lek tembuing en semalenyeing sewokeing.” Woyom moxo neil wou tambiy wei bezomb on bei, “Qandi lek, de qou wa xe lelek me la bam.”
\v 7 De moux moxo qandi lek me la beeng.
\v 8 Xel qendu ngandoung on yei tine, xel etek en ingwei xel yei Anutu xe nikanzek me sanghoxe Anutu, e tiwei wong nikanzek wou xomaxoneing ti yo.
\s1 Yesu taxe Matai
\p 
\v 9 Ka Yesu la nanghei inyon, moxo yei tambiy ti lei Matai toundei eivek xomek takis. Moxo neil wou e, “Betiwou ay,” om Matai qandi lek me betiwou e me la.
\p 
\v 10 Kale Yesu di ya eivek Matai xe xomek, xel ngenong wei mi qou takis me xel sewokeing eno lam me di ya is e me e xe xel betiyeing.
\v 11 Xel Parisi yei tine, om xel teling wou xel betiyeing, “Nambei nya xam xe putoung di ya is xel wei mi qou takis me xel wei mi wo sewokeing o?”
\p 
\v 12 Yesu ngo tine me neil, “Xel wei vanei ma eno se mi la wou dokta, qe xel wei vanei yo.
\v 13 Ekom xam ghe na me na qou kwa wou qayeeng tine qes:
\q1 ‘A laleing vind lalei pyaweing de a laleing se vind seing xound.’ \rq Hosea 6:6\rq*
\m En a se lam bei taxe xel wei bombek o, qe xel wei sewokeing o.”
\s1 Yesu luk en kwa wei vambueing yaeing o
\p 
\v 14 Woyom Yoan xe xel betiyeing lam me teling wou Yesu, “Nambei nya ekom xa is xel Parisi mi vambu yaeing, de wa xe xel betiyeing se mi vambu yaeing?”
\p 
\v 15 Yesu neil elox bei, “Nambei nya xel wei lam en iingama eno na qou laleind maying gyeik tambiy wei embei dii vex eno nanghei toundei is xel? Ka bouk wei xel embei qou tambiy wei iingama yo me na veil xel, woyom tyek xel vambu yaeing.
\p 
\v 16 “Tambiy ti se mi qou qaeing vako myasepu me duw eivek teimb takwei, en qaeing vako wei xel duw on tyek tetei me zex teimb on bo nilul.
\v 17 Xel ti se mi taw wain vako eivek wain takwei ninavi. Wangwei xel bong ambei nyon nei, wain ninavi yon tyek na tip, de wain on tyek na taw veil de ninavi yon tyek bo nol. Qe xel mi taw wain vako yon eivek ninavi vako, me luw xouing tyek mendei nimza.”
\s1 Yesu piyexe vexawo wei mey o de wo vex wei vanei yo wo nimzalek
\p 
\v 18 Ka moxo neil qayeeng tine, gyovaxa ti lam me ev vaxakatu eivek wou e tax me neil, “A neung vex mouk mey. Ekom wang nam a ni memam lek e, en vexo e mendei mapieing no.”
\v 19 Yesu qandi lek me la is e, me e xe betiyeing is ambei nyon.
\p 
\v 20 De woyom vex tiwei mi qou gyand teyei lek vakovek qes xoumeeng yuw eno lam me di la yus en e me axlek e xe teimb ding on myasepu.
\v 21 Vexo neil wou xow, “Wangwei a mou daxlek e xe teimb, on tyek a bo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 22 Yesu pekwi me yei vex on me neil, “A neung vex, wa laleim embo nimza, wa xe wongeingis wong wang wo nimzalek.” Om vexo wo nimzalek gyeik kayon.
\p 
\v 23 Yesu la eivek gyovaxa xe xomek me yei xel wei di vei sakwep me wo talot me yei xel qendu yon di wo nindenduing,
\v 24 moxo neil, “Xam la veil. Vexawo ne se mey qe di yeip.” Ekom xel napexe e.
\v 25 Ka Yesu tiy xel qendu ngandoung on la myayaing, moxo la lalei me zeim vex on mema, de vexo qandi lek.
\v 26 Qayeeng la wo ngandoung en tine eivek tembuing danghei danghei nei dalus.
\s1 Yesu wong matekeing yayuw me myatueing ti wo nimza lek
\p 
\v 27 Ka Yesu la nanghei inyon me la, tambiy matekeing yayuw betiwou e, me di taxe la wou e, “Dawit Neu Moux,\f + \fr 9:27 \ft Qayeeng tine, “Dawit Neu Moux”, qes nge nambei nye Mesia.\f* pyanaleim en uw!”
\p 
\v 28 Moxo la eivek xomek, eno tambiy yuw wei mend tekeing o lam wou e, me moxo teling luw, “Muw ghe wongis bei a teyei bei bong tine?”
\p Luw lewexe, “Ee, Tambiy Ngandoung.”
\p 
\v 29 Woyom moxo toung mema lek luw mendghalus me neil, “Muw ghe wongis om lul tine e na teyei lek wou muw.”
\v 30 De luw mendghalus yeila. Yesu peti luw, “Kandek muw seng bong xelti boulek lul tine.”
\v 31 Ekom luw la myayaing nei me teyoxe qayeeng on lala en Yesu eivek tembuing danghei danghei dalus tiyon.
\p 
\v 32 Ka luw la veil, xomaxoneing qou tambiy ti myatueing wei memo dei eivek me se teyei bei baluk o me lam wou Yesu.
\v 33 Me gyeik Yesu tiy memo yon la myayaing, tambiy wei myatu yon luk. Xel qendu ngandoung on etek me neil, “Lulti nambei tine eno xelti se mi yei eivek Israel ti.”
\p 
\v 34 Ekom xel Parisi neil, “Moxo mi tiy xel angya nikanzek wei gyovaxa lukanzek wei xel memo yo.”
\s1 Xel xukxe yon nuyuka
\p 
\v 35 Yesu mi la eivek beyeeng nayak dalus me beyeeng me teyoxe xel eivek xomek qekueing ama wei xel Yuda yo me neil Xoulek Nimza wei tete lalei yo me wong xel wei vanei leimalei eno mi wo nimzalek.
\v 36 Gyeik ingwei yei xel qendu ngandoung on, moxo pyanalei en xel, en nambei xel lundpeyei yon la bandabanda, me xel mindei e wo nol nambei sipsip wei gyovaxa ma veil o.
\v 37 Woyom moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing, “Neing zuw ngenong ekom xel xukxe yon nuyuw ka.
\v 38 Om xam teling wou xuk ma bei e bong xel xukxe na eivek e xe xuk me na qou neing eivek xuk.”
\c 10
\s1 Yesu wong xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw la
\p 
\v 1 Yesu taxe e xe xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw on lam wou e me wong nikanzek wou xel bei xel a mi tiy laweeng nilaxes me bong xel wei vanei leimalei eno bo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 2 Xel sinale xoumeeng yuw ne leind ambei nye. Tiwei tax eno Simon e lei nge xel mi taxe bei Petele me li Andrias, Jems wei Sebedi neu moux o me li Yoan,
\v 3 Pilip me Batolomiu, Tomas me Matai tambiy wei mi qou takis o, Jems Alpias neu moux, me Tadius,
\v 4 Simon wei Selot me Yudas Iskariot, tiwei tyek na neil Yesu teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend o.
\p 
\v 5 Yesu wong xel xoumeeng yuw ne eno la de peti xel bei, “Xam seng na eivek xel amba senghoing o ghe na eivek Samaria xe beyeeng on ti,
\v 6 qe xam ghe na wou xel sipsip wei Israel wei lati yo.
\v 7 Ka xam a being na eno xam ghe na neil qayeeng tine, ‘Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno lam paviy.’
\v 8 Xam ghe bong vanei e ma, me xam a piyexe xel meyeing, de ghe bong xel wei lepa yo bo nimzalek me xam a tiy memoyeiw na veil. Lul wei xam ghe qou bandaing, eno xam ghe bong wou xel bandaing.
\v 9 Xam se qou lulti nambei ghol o silva malew o kopa malew gyand eivek xam xe let.
\v 10 Gyeik xam ghe na wou sakwaing eno xam se qou vaxak ti, o teimb yuw, o vaxalambes o patongeeng is. En xel wei mi wo xuk eno tyek xel bong yaeing wou xel.
\p 
\v 11 “Wangwei xam a being na eivek beyeeng nayak o beyeeng, ond xam ghe gwimexe tambiy wei nimza yo ti me ghe na mendei is e eivek e xe xomek deka xam ghe na veil le.
\v 12 Ka xam a being na eivek xomek ti, eno xam a neil bendiyeing wou xel.
\v 13 Wangwei xel wei xomek on na qou xam is xeindlala, xam ghe bong xam xe lalei vevopeing wou xel, ek wangwei na ma, ond xam a qou xam xe lalei vevopeing noum wou xow.
\v 14 Wangwei xelti se qou xam o na ngo qayeeng wei xam o, ond xam pepa vegyuveeng veil vaxamim gyeik xam a being na veil xomek o beyeeng nayak o.
\v 15 A neil wou xam zonghek bei, gyeik bouk wei Anutu embei bo qayeeng en xomaxoneing eno nimaying ngandoung tyek qandi wou beyeeng nayak tiyon ghanaw Sodom aluw Gomora.
\v 16 Wei, ambei bong xam ghe na nambei sipsip eivek xel naw bemeeng senghoing. Nambei nyon xam a qou lupeyei nambei myeiy me mendei males nambei beliy.
\p 
\v 17 “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en xel xomaxoneing, tyek xel a qou xam me na wou xel kanzol me tyek xel bo nol wou xam me sesa xam eivek xomek qekueing ama.
\v 18 Tyek xel a qou xam me na bale wou xel lei ngandoung wei seyap o me xel king mend en ay, en nambei xam ghe mi betiwou ay me ghe neil xoulek teyei wou xel me xel amba.
\v 19 Ekom gyeik xel a zeimaxoun xam, xam seng bou kwamim ngenong en vati wei xam ambei neil o, bei tyek xam a neil ambei nya. Lek seivma kayon eno Anutu tyek bong vati wei xam ambei neil o,
\v 20 en inye tyek xam venaxow se neil, qe inye xam Mamim xe Laweeng eno tyek baluk eivek xam myamim.
\p 
\v 21 “Li venaxow tyek na neil li teyei me xel nyeis e mey, me ma ti tyek bong ambei nyon wou neu, de neuyeiw tyek bo vevek is mamata me xel ba nyeis xel amey.
\v 22 Xomaxoneing dalus tyek laleind bo nol wou xam en ay, ekom eti yeiw wei nale nikanzek me ena bouk loxyus eno tyek Anutu devind xel veil meyeing.
\v 23 Wangwei xel bo nilul wou xam eivek beyeeng ti, ond xam a pek me ghe na beyeeng nge. A neil wou xam zonghek bei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux noum eno tyek xam seng na eivek beyeeng tambak wei Israel o buplek.
\p 
\v 24 “Yak wei wevek xomek o se ghanaw e xe putoung, o xukxe ti se ghanaw e xe teiv.
\v 25 Ekom wangwei yakyak wei wevek xomek o teyei lek e xe putoung, ond inyon woy. Me wangwei xukxe teyei lek e xe teiv, ond inyon woy is ambei nyon. Wangwei xomek ma eno xel taxe bei e Belsebul, ond tyek xel bo lei wei nilul o wou e xe xel wei xomek on!
\p 
\v 26 “Om xam seng gwaleeng en xel. Lul dalus wei xel vun eno tyek nam yanyateiv. Me qayeeng tambak wei yeip xupekeing eno tyek xomaxoneing boulek.
\v 27 Vati wei a neil wou xam eivek boukeing, eno xam a neil eivek bendiyeing. Me qayeeng wei xam ghe di ngoung wouma eivek nenyamim, eno tyek xam bale lek xomek demi qetyei me na neilteyei.
\v 28 Xam seng gwaleeng en xel wei embei nyeis xam neing a mey yo, dom xel se teyei bei nyeis xam numim pieing. Qe xam ghe gwaleeng en Anutu wei teyei bei bo nol wou xam numim pieing me xam neing eivek nenyex wei luta yo.
\v 29 Beip xel se mi xouv menek nayak yuw en selewa gyand nayak ti? Ek wangwei xam Mamim lalei se devind nei on tyek menek menek nayak on ti se teyei bei deteina lek tembuing.
\v 30 De nge is xam lumim velus dalus on eno Anutu pyaw memawou woy.
\v 31 Om xam seng gwaleeng. Xam ghe ghanaw menek nayak ngenong on.
\p 
\v 32 “Eti yeiw wei mi neil a teyei natax wou xomaxoneing eno tyek a neil e teyei natax wou Mang anghei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 33 Ekom eti bei dax a vun atax wou xomaxoneing, eno tyek a dax e vun is ambei nyon atax wou Mang nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\p 
\v 34 “Xam seng bou kwamim bei a qou lalei vevopeing me na lam tembuing. A se qou lalei vevopeing me na lam qe ngeyeing vevek.
\v 35 En a lam bei pekwi
\q1 ‘moux ti lalei bo nol wou ma,
\q2 de neu vex ti lalei bo nol wou ta,
\q1 me neu vex lalei bo nol wou yeing avexta.
\q2 
\v 36 Moux ti eivek xel venaxow eno tyek bo nol wou emaxow xe xel wei xomek o.’ \rq Maika 7:6\rq*
\p 
\v 37 “Xelti embei lalei devind ma luw ta ghanaw ay, eno tyek se bong ambei a xe. Xelti embei lalei devind neu moux aluw neu vex ghanaw ay, ond tyek se bong ambei a xe.
\v 38 Me xelti embei se qalei e xe xax pepeeng me betiwou ay, ond se teyei bei bong ambei a xe.
\v 39 Tambiy ti embei bong e xe mapieing embo nimza, on tyek na saing e xe mapieing. Dom xelti embei saing e xe mapieing en ay, ond tyek gyeiwou mapieing zonghek.
\p 
\v 40 “Tambiy ti embei qou xam eno qou ay, me eti qou ay eno qou tiwei wong a lam o.
\v 41 Tambiy ti embei qou poropet ti me gyeiteyei en nambei e mi neil qayeeng poropet ond tyek na qou xouveing wei poropet o. Me tambiy ti embei qou xel wei bombek o ti me gyeiteyei en nambei e yon tambiy wei bombek o yon tyek na qou xouveing wei tambiy wei bombek o.
\v 42 Me wangwei xelti bong mayamya memiing tyuweing ti wou xel beimambei wei leind maeing on ti en nambei inyon e a xe betiyeing, ond a neil zonghek wou xam bei, moxo tyek se saing e xe xouveing.”
\c 11
\s1 Yesu me Yoan Lipekeing
\p 
\v 1 Ka Yesu neil qayeeng wei embei teyoxe e xe xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw eno ma, moxo la nanghei inyon me la en embei na teyoxe me na neil qayeeng eivek beyeeng wei Galili nei.
\p 
\v 2 Gyeik Yoan ngo eivek xeitueing en vati wei Kilisi di wong o, moxo wong e xe xel betiyeing la,
\v 3 bei teling e, “Beip inye wang on tiwei tyek nam o, o xa mendi daxe tambiy bange?”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu neil elox, “Xam lox neil wou Yoan en vati wei xam ghe ngo me ghe wei yo:
\v 5 Xel matekeing eno mend yeila, me xel wei vaxend nol eno di la, me xel wei wo vanei lepa eno wo nimzalek, me xel wei nenyend wo qatu eno ngo wou, me xel meyeing eno qandi lek, de Xoulek Nimza eno xel neil wou xel kanyoyeiw.
\v 6 Mata e na wou xel wei xel xe wongeingis se tei en qayeeng wei ay yo.”
\p 
\v 7 Ka Yoan xe xel betiyeing la veil, Yesu luk wou xel qendu yon en Yoan: “Xam ghe la tembuing bandaing nei bei na gwei vati? Ghet wei laweeng di vei elox me loum o?
\v 8 Wangwei na ma nei, yon xam ghe la being na gwei vati? Moux ti wei vunek en teimb nimza yo? Ma, xel eti yeiw wei mi vunek en teimb nimza eno mindei eivek king beeng.
\v 9 Woyom xam ghe la being na gwei vati? Poropet ti? Ee, a neil wou xam bei, Poropet tiyon ghanaw xel poropet ba veil.
\v 10 Tambiy tine tiwei xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye,
\q1 “ ‘Wei, tyek a bong a xe nenyalesana ti na mamunghexeing en wang,
\q2 tiwei tyek menyex wou sakwaing atax en wang o.’ \rq Malakai 3:1\rq*
\m 
\v 11 A neil wou xam zonghek: Yoan Lipekeing ghanaw xel wei tayeiw wou xel lek tembuing ne yo leind, ekom e tiwei lei maeing eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno ghanaw e.
\v 12 Eivek bouk wei Yoan Lipekeing neil xoulek me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne, eno xel wo vevek nikanzek en na qou tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo, de xel wo vevek nikanzek om inyon wo nimaying ngenong wou e.
\v 13 En xel poropet dalus me petieing neil qayeeng poropet me e lam tyip wou bouk wei Yoan o.
\v 14 Me wangwei wa laleim devind bei na qou vati wei a neil ne, ond e yon Eliya wei embei nam o.
\v 15 Tambiy wei nenya nale lek e yo, ond e ngo qayeeng tine.
\p 
\v 16 “Tyek a neil qayeeng lek vati bei talex moux alis vex wei gweimbeeng ne? Xel on ambei yakyak wei mindei eivek beyeeng vateivek me mi taxe la wou xel bamba:
\q1 
\v 17 “‘Xa vei sakwep en xam,
\q2 ekom xam seng aw,
\q1 me xa wong lalo wei lalei pyaweing o,
\q2 ekom xam seng wong talot.’
\m 
\v 18 En Yoan lam eno se mi ya yaeing me num numeing, me xel neil, ‘Moxo memo ti toundei eivek e.’
\v 19 Xomaxoneing Neu Moux lam ya yaeing me num numeing, me xel neil, ‘Wei, inye e wei mi zongaxei me num ngenong o. E yon gweleeng wei xel wei mi qou takis me sewokeing o.’ Ekom e xe lupeyei nimza yon talex bei e xe xuk on la bombek.”
\s1 Lalei pyaweing en xomaxoneing wei se pekwi xow o
\p 
\v 20 Woyom Yesu neil beyeeng tiyon en ingwei mi wong lulvako eivek o, ekom xel on se pekwi xow.
\v 21 “Xam Korasin me xam Betsaida ghe gwaleeng amim en tyek xam a tulek nimaying. Wangwei lulvako wei a wong eivek xam eno xel bong eivek Taia me Saidon, on beip xel pekwi xow takwei nei me byex teimb wei talot o de ev vewev me pelei lek xow.
\v 22 Ekom a neil wou xam bei, lek bouk wei Anutu embei bong qayeeng en xomaxoneing dalus eno tyek nimaying ngandoung qandi wou xam ghanaw veil nambei ingwei qandi wou Taia me Saidon o.
\v 23 De xam Kapenaom, tyek xel a zeim xam ghe zekna pu wei tyoung nei? Ma yo, tyek wa deteina beyeeng wei meyeing o. En wangwei lulvako wei a wong wou xam eno xel bong eivek Sodom, yond tyek Sodom na mi mendei me e nam atyip bouk tine is.
\v 24 Ekom a neil wou xam bei lek bouk wei ngoeing qayeeng eno tyek bo nimaying ngandoung wou xam ghanaw Sodom.”
\s1 Xam ghe nam wou ay me na qou laweeng
\p 
\v 25 Lek seivma tiyon Yesu neil, “Mang, a sanghoxe wang, Tambiy Ngandoung wei tyoung gheyapu me tembuing o, en nambei wang vun lulti beimambei ne veil xel wei lundpeyei me kwa nimza yo, dom ghe talex eyeip yaing wou xel yakyak.
\v 26 Ee Mang, en inye wang betiwou wamaxow xe woueing nalei nimza.
\p 
\v 27 “Lulul dalusateiv eno Mang toung eivek a memang. Xelti se yeimawou xomaxoneing Neu Moux qe Ma venaxow, me xelti se yeimawou Ma qe Neu Moux venaxow me eti yeiw wei Neu Moux beyal bei talex e wou xel o.
\p 
\v 28 “Xam dalus wei ghe mi wong pok ngandoung me ghe mi qalei nimaying eno xam lam wou ay me tyek a bong xam ghe na mendei veil xuk wei xam ghe wong o.
\v 29 Xam qalei a xe pelang maying lek xow me qou kwa wou ay, en a ne a laleing xeiles me laleing vevopeing, me tyek xam numim na mendei me na qou laweeng.
\v 30 En a xe pelang on levismaeing me a xe maying ne vevopeing.”
\c 12
\s1 Tambiy Ngandoung wei Sabat o
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk wei Sabat eno Yesu la eivek xuk wei wit. E xe xel betiyeing maxepya xel om xel embei qou wit lu valu me gya.
\v 2 Xel Parisi yei tine, eno xel neil wou e, “Wei! Wa xe xel betiyeing di wong vati wei se la teyei lek petieing o lek bouk wei Sabat o.”
\p 
\v 3 Moxo lewexe, “Beip xam seng pyaw vati wei Dawit wong gyeik ingwei e me e xe xel wei mi la is eno maxepya xel o?
\v 4 Om Dawit la eivek xomek wei Anutu xe yo, de e me e xe xel wei mi la is e yo ya belet wei vambuing wei xel peti yo, en inyon xel lumuki venaxow xe.
\v 5 O xam seng pyaw eivek qapiya wei petieing o, bei lek Sabat eno xel lumuki wei mi wo xuk eivek xomek vambuing eno pyalek petieing wei Sabat o, eno se wo sewokeing?
\v 6 A neil wou xam bei tiwei toundei inye eno ghanaw xomek vambuing.
\v 7 Wangwei xam ghe boulek qayeeng tine qes,
\q1 “‘A laleing vind lalei pyaweingxow, de se seing xound,’ \rq Hosea 6:6\rq*
\m xam seng teyei bei toung nimaying lek xel wei se wo sewokeing o.
\v 8 En Xomaxoneing Neu Moux on Tambiy Ngandoung wei Sabat o.”
\p 
\v 9 Yesu la veil beyeeng tiyon, me la eivek xel xe xomek qekueing ama,
\v 10 me tambiy wei mema bezomb eno ti toundei inyon. Xel di yimexe qayeeng qes wei xel embei bong qayeeng en Yesu yo, om xel teling wou e, “Beip inyei teyei lek bei xey a bong xel wei vanei eno bo nimzalek Sabat, o ma?”
\p 
\v 11 Moxo neil wou xel, “Wangwei xam ti xe sipsip ti deteina eivek leiveeng lek Sabat, tyek wa seng na zeim e me na puw e nam myayaing?
\v 12 Xel xomaxoneing on ghanaw sipsip veil! Omva petieing neil embei xey a bong kwa nimza lek Sabat.”
\p 
\v 13 Woyom moxo neil wou tambiy on, “Tatei memam.” Om moxo tatei mema de mema wo nimza no, nambei mema nge.
\v 14 Ekom xel Parisi la myayaing me luk wouma bei tyek xel nyeis Yesu nambei nya.
\s1 Anutu xe xukxe wei beyal o
\p 
\v 15 Om Yesu la veil beyeeng tiyon, en woulek vati wei xel Parisi embei bo wou e yo. Xel ngenong betiwou e, me moxo wong xel dalus xe vanei ma,
\v 16 de peti xel bei eti se neil e teyei bei e eti.
\v 17 Kwa tine la teyei lek vati wei Anutu neil eivek poropet Yesaya mya yo.
\q1 
\v 18 “Wei, inye a xe xukxe tiwei a beyal o,
\q2 a laleing vind e me na wo xeinglala en e.
\q1 Tyek a toung a xe Laweeng lek e,
\q2 me moxo tyek baluk en kwa bombek wei moux alis vex wei tembuing sapa yo.
\q1 
\v 19 Tyek moxo se neil qayeeng is lalei vanei me taxe niseikeing,
\q2 me xelti tyek se ngo e vya eivek sakwaing mema nayak on.
\q1 
\v 20 Wangwei ghet na pyaw nayaka eno tyek se pyaw veil,
\q2 me wangwei lam bo lu bandaing tyek moxo se nyeis lam amey,
\q1 qe ka e menyex wou sakwaing bombek me e bo neing lek.
\q2 
\v 21 Eivek e lei eno xomaxoneing eivek tembuing bamba tyek na toung mend en e.” \rq Yesaya 42:1-4\rq*
\s1 Yesu me Belsebul
\p 
\v 22 Woyom xel qou tambiy wei memo wong e ma tuzeyi me myatu yo me lam wou Yesu, me e wong moxo wo nimzalek, en kandek moxo teyei bei baluk me gyeina.
\v 23 Xomaxoneing dalus etek me neil, “Beip inye Dawit Neu Moux?”
\p 
\v 24 Ekom gyeik xel Parisi ngo tine, xel neil, “Tambiy tine mi tiy memo en nikanzek wei Belsebul o, lukanzek wei xel memo yo.”
\p 
\v 25 Yesu woulek xel xe woueing nalei om neil wou xel, “Tete lalei dalus wei dembuma yo tyek bo nol wouma, me beyeeng ngandoung o xomek ti dembuma on tyek se bale nikanzek.
\v 26 Wangwei Sandang na tiy Sandang na veil, on moxo dembu venaxow. Woyom nambei nya moxo xe tete lalei tyek bale nikanzek?
\v 27 Me wangwei a tiy memo na veil angya Belsebul nikanzek nei, ond eti mi vind xel wei xam o me xel mi tiy memo yon la myayaing? Om xel wei xam eno tyek talex wou xam bei qayeeng wei xam on se la wo bombek.
\v 28 Ekom wangwei a tiy memo yon na veil nangya Anutu xe Laweeng, woyom Anutu xe tete lalei eno lam wou xam woy.
\p 
\v 29 “Nambei nya tambiy ti teyei bei na eivek tambiy wei nikanzek o beeng me na qou e xe lulul, ka e tup tambiy nikanzek on bole? Woyom e teyei bei na panax lulul eivek e xe xomek.
\p 
\v 30 “Moux wei se mindei is ay, eno inye mi wo vevek wou ay, de tambiy wei se mi qekuwou moux alis vex is ay eno mi tiy xel lala.
\v 31 Om a neil wou xam bei, sewokeing tambak me qayeeng lukeingyak wei xomaxoneing mi wong eno Anutu teyei bei semaleeng veil, ekom tambiy ti embei baluk yak lek Laweeng Vambuing eno e xe nilul on tyek se semaleeng veil.
\v 32 Tambiy ti embei baluk qayeeng nilul lek Xomaxoneing Neu Moux on tyek semaleeng veil, ekom xelti embei baluk nilul lek Laweeng Vambuing on tyek nilul wei e yon se teyei bei semaleeng veil, eivek bouk tine me bouk loxyus wei di lam o is.
\p 
\v 33 “Wangwei xax on nimza, ond tyek neing on bo nimza is, o wangwei xax on bo nilul on tyek neing on bo nol is ambei nyon, en xel mi woulek xax lek e neing.
\v 34 Xam on myeiy nilul neuyeiw, nambei nya tyek xam baluk qayeeng nimza? En qayeeng mi lam veil xomaxoneing laleind me xel myend mi luk.
\v 35 Xomaxoneing wei nimza eno tyek bo lulul nimza wei mindei eivek e lalei yo, dom xomaxoneing wei nilul eno tyek bo lul wei nilul wei toundei eivek e yo nam myayaing.
\v 36 Ekom a neil wou xam bei gyeik Anutu embei daxe xomaxoneing, xel eti yeiw wei mi neil qayeeng bandabanda dalus eno xel a tul pavulek wei xel o teyei.
\v 37 En wamaxow xe qayeeng eno tyek Anutu na neimbei wa bombek, de wamaxow xe qayeeng eno tyek na neimbei wa tambiy nilul.”
\s1 Dee wei Yona yo
\p 
\v 38 Woyom xel Parisi valu me putoung wei petieing o neil wou Yesu, “Putoung, xa bei ghei dee wei lulvako valu wou wang.”
\p 
\v 39 Moxo lewexe, “Xel moux alis vex nilul wei bouk tine wei mi toung demind wou Anutu yo eno mi teling en dee wei lulvako! Ekom xel se teyei bei gyei dee ti, qe tyek xel gyei dee wei poropet Yona yo.
\v 40 En Yona toundei bendiyeing yal me boukeing yal eivek woing ngandoung on bambou, om Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek mendei bendiyeing yal me boukeing yal eivek tembuing lalei.
\v 41 Lek bouk wei ngoeing qayeeng eno xel wei Niniwe tyek qandi me bale me bo qayeeng en xomaxoneing wei gweimbeeng ne me na neil xel xe nilul teyei, en xel pekwi xow gyeik ingwei Yona la neil xoulek o. Wei, gweimbeeng tambiy ti ghanaw Yona veil, eno lam toundei inye.
\v 42 Kwin wei xonei eno tyek nam bale lek qayeeng is xel wei gweimbeeng ne me bo qayeeng en xel, en vexo lam anghei tembuing myasepu bei nam a ngo Salomo xe kwa nimza. De gweimbeeng ne tambiy ti ghanaw Salomo eno lam toundei inye.
\s1 Laweeng nilaxes loumelam no
\p 
\v 43 “Gyeik laweeng nilaxes lam myayaing veil xomaxoneing ti, eno la eivek beyeeng bandaing me yimexe beyeeng wei embei na qou laweeng o ekom se yeiwou ti.
\v 44 Woyom neil, ‘Tyek a nox mena beyeeng wei a ghanaw o.’ Gyeik e lam tyip me yei xomek wei xelti se qou yo. Eno xel pepa e wo vako me vunekwou e wo nimza.
\v 45 Woyom moxo la me qou laweeng lim yuw ba wei nilul ayang ghanaw e yo, me xel la lalei me dei inyon. Om tambiy tiyon xe deing wo nilul ghanaw ingwei mindei tax o. Inyon tyek bong ambei kayon wou xel nilul wei gweimbeeng ne yo.”
\s1 Yesu ta me liyeiw
\p 
\v 46 Gyeik Yesu di luk is xel qendu yon, moxo ta me liyeiw moux toukale myayaing, en xel embei baluk is e.
\v 47 Xel ti neil wou e, “Wa tam me limyeiw moux lam toukale myayaing, en xel embei baluk is wang.”
\p 
\v 48 Yesu neil elox wou e, “A tang eti, me a lingyeiw eti?”
\v 49 Om seloung mema la wou e xe betiyeingyeiw, me neil, “Inye a tang me a lingyeiw moux.
\v 50 En eti yeiw wei mi betiwou Mang wei toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu yo lalei yond inyon a ling moux me a ling vex me a tang.”
\c 13
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei vuweing lulul vei
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk kayon eno Yesu la myayaing veil xomek me la toundei wou lounyeing vi.
\v 2 De xel qendu ngandoung ti qekuma vivekwou e om moxo lek la eivek bot ti me la dei eivek lalei, de xomaxoneing dalus on toukale nenyawes.
\v 3 Woyom moxo neil lulul ngenong wou xel eivek qayeeng pakeing, me neil, “Xukana ti la vuw lul vei eivek xuk.
\v 4 Ka moxo di vuw lul vei lala, eno valu teila lek sakwaing, me menek menek lam ya e ma.
\v 5 De valu teila lek tembuing wei qakous o, en inyon tembuing nayaka toundei lek qakous mapu yon. Om belup daing me lam, en nambei tembuing on se la ghembi.
\v 6 Ekom gyeik ingwei seiv leklam nale ghey, eno seiv leis vei yuvek lek me mupek, en luselis ma veil.
\v 7 De vei valu teila senghoing eivek qeis wei yingying o om tyip me sevunexe lulul vei yon.
\v 8 De vei valu teila lek tembuing nimza, me vuk neing teyei lek 100, me valu vuk 60 de valu 30 inye vati wei ev o.
\v 9 Eti nenya nale lek e, ond wong e ngo.”
\p 
\v 10 Xel betiyeing lam wou e me teling, “Nambei nya wang mi luk is xomaxoneing eivek qayeeng pakeing?”
\p 
\v 11 Moxo neil elox bei, “Lupeyei nimza wei tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu wei mi yeip xupekeing eno Anutu wong wou xam dom se wong wou xel.
\v 12 Eti yeiw wei liw nenyend wou a xe qayeeng petieing on tyek lupeyei gyeip yaing wou xel, me xel a qou lupeyei ngenong is. Ekom xel wei se mi ngo, eno lupeyei nayak wei xel qou yon eno tyek Anutu bouveil xel.
\v 13 En qes tine om a mi luk wou xel eivek qayeeng pakeing.
\q1 “Xel mendghalus tyek gyei, ekom tyek xel se gyei lulti.
\q2 Me xel a ngo, ekom tyek xel se ngo wou me boulek qayeeng qes.
\m 
\v 14 Om xel wong qayeeng wei poropet Yesaya neil eno wo neing lek.
\q1 “ ‘Tyek xam a ngo qayeeng lumama ekom tyek xam seng boulek.
\q2 Tyek xam a mi gwei lumama ekom tyek xam seng gwei lulti.
\q1 
\v 15 En xel xomaxoneing tine laleind wo nikanzek,
\q2 me xel on nenyend wo qatu
\q2 me xel mendghalus on tuzeyi.
\q1 Enok xel gyei nangya mendghalus,
\q2 me na ngo gya nenyend,
\q2 me boulek eivek naleind me pekwi me noum,
\q1 de tyek a bong xel bo nimzalek.’ \rq Yesaya 6:9-10\rq*
\m 
\v 16 Ekom xam Anutu e bong mata wou xam, en nambei xam mamimghalus yei ay me nambei xam nenyamim ngo wou qayeeng.
\v 17 A neil wou xam zonghek bei xel poropet ngenong me xel moux wei bombek eno embei gyei vati wei xam ghe wei gweimbeeng ekom xel se yei, me xel embei ngo vati wei xam ghe ngo gweimbeeng ekom xel se ngo.
\p 
\v 18 “Woyom ngo wou vati wei qayeeng pakeing neil en xukana vuw vei eno qes.
\v 19 Gyeik xelti embei ngo qayeeng ne en tete lalei me se boulek nei, on tambiy ka nilul eno lam me tetei vati wei xend eivek e lalei yo veil. Vei tine inye vei wei vuw lek sakwaing o.
\v 20 De vei wei teila lek tembuing wei qakous qakous, eno inye tambiy wei ngo qayeeng me lutika eno qou is lalei nimza me wo xeilala yo.
\v 21 Ekom luselis wei e yo ma om nale nayaka. Gyeik nimaying wei xel mi pesek qayeeng o nimaying wei xomaxoneing wo nol wouma en Anutu xe xoulek eno lam, lutika eno moxo saing e xe wongeingis.
\v 22 De vei wei teila eivek qeis wei yingying o, eno inyon tambiy wei ngo qayeeng, ekom wounalei en mapieing tine me lul dalus wei tembuing eno sevunexe om se vuk neing.
\v 23 Ekom vei wei teila lek tembuing nimza yon, inyon tambiy wei ngo qayeeng me woulek. Moxo vuk neing teyei lek 100 o 60 o 30 inyon vati wei xend o.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing en vyaing
\p 
\v 24 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing nge wou xel no. “Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yon nambei tambiy ti vuw vei nimza eivek e xe xuk o.
\v 25 Ekom ka xel dalusateiv yeip, e xe xel vevek amba lam me vuw vyaing eivek wit masenghoing dom la veil.
\v 26 Ka wit tyip me lu belup, woyom vyaing tyip is ambei nyon.
\p 
\v 27 “Xukma xe xukxe lam wou e me neil, ‘Teiv, beip wa seng vuw vei nimza eivek wa xe xuk? De woyom vyaing beimambei ne lam anghei inya?’
\p 
\v 28 “Moxo neil elox bei, ‘Vevek amba ti lam wong tine.’
\p “Xel xukxe teling wou e, ‘Wambei xa na me na puw veil?’
\p 
\v 29 “Moxo lewexe bei, ‘Ma, en nambei wa bei puw vyaing eno tyek wa puw wit luselis is.
\v 30 Wong luw xouing ling deka bouk wei qoueing neing o le. Lek bouk kayon eno tyek a neil wou xel wei mi qou neing o, “Xam a puw vyaing atax me na tup buing en nyuweing, woyom xam qeku wit me na qou me nam eivek a xe xomek yaeing.” ’ ”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei mastet vei me yis o
\p 
\v 31 Moxo neil qayeeng pakeing nge wou xel no: “Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno nambei mastet vei, wei tambiy ti qou me xen eivek e xe xuk o.
\v 32 Inyon nayakameng ka veil vei dalus, ekom gyeik ingwei tyip ngandoung, inyon ling ngandoungateiv ghanaw lul dalus wei ev eivek xuk me wong ngandoung nambei xax, omek menek menek wei senghoing bandaing nei mi lam me qo lewis lek mema mema.”
\p 
\v 33 Yesu lox neil qayeeng pakeing nge no, “Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yon nambei yis wei xel vex mi qou me maleeng eivek palawa me wong palawa vuklek me wo ngandoung.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu mi luk ti beimambei ne dalus wou xel qendu ngandoung on eivek qayeeng pakeing. Moxo se mi neil qayeeng ti yeipyaing wou xel qe mi neil eivek qayeeng pakeing.
\p 
\v 35 Om nambei nyon kwa tine la teyei lek lulti Anutu neil eivek poropet mya.
\q1 “Tyek a tax myang en neileing qayeeng pakeing.
\q2 Tyek a neil pavulek en lul leimalei wei mindei xupekeing takwei wei tembuing lam nale yanyateiv o me elam gweimbeeng ne.” \rq Qapiya Lalo 78:2\rq*
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing qes wei vyaing o
\p 
\v 36 Woyom moxo ghanaw xel qendu yon me la eivek xomek. E xe xel betiyeing lam wou e me neil, “Neil e yeip yaing wou xa en qayeeng pakeing qes wei vyaing tyip eivek xuk o.”
\p 
\v 37 Moxo lewexe bei, “Tambiy tiwei vuw vei nimza yon, inyon Xomaxoneing Neu Moux.
\v 38 Xuk on tembuing sapa, de vei nimza yon teyei lek neuyeiw wei tete lalei yo. De vyaing on Sandang neuyeiw,
\v 39 me vevek amba wei vuw xel on inye tambiy kawei mapetok o. De bouk wei qoueing neing on inyon bouk wei embei na tip lek o, de xel wei embei qou neing eno inye xel angela.
\p 
\v 40 “Ka xel a puw vyaing me banyuw lek nenyex, yon tyek xel bong ambei nyon lek bouk loxyus.
\v 41 Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek bong e xe xel angela na myayaing nei, me tyek xel a puw lul dalus wei mi wong sewokeing mi tyip o me xel dalus wei mi wong nilul ayang eno veil e xe tete lalei.
\v 42 Tyek xel banex xel na eivek nenyex ngandoung de nanghei inyon eno tyek xel deeng me zanga newound bo nyiknyik.
\v 43 Woyom xel wei bombek o tyek na siing ambei sayeiv eivek tete lalei wei xel Mend xe yo. Tambiy ti nenya nale lek e, ond wong e ngo.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing en vuneing qoupek malew me viyaviy
\p 
\v 44 “Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei nambei xel vun qoupek wei malew eivek xuk ti. Gyeik tambiy ti yeiwou, eno la vun no, de woyom moxo wo xeilala me la wong vateivek lek lul dalus wei e yo dom la xouv xuk tiyon.
\p 
\v 45 “Nge no, tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno nambei tambiy wei mi wo vateivek lek lulul o ti eno di yimexe viyaviy nimzamza.
\v 46 Gyeik moxo yeiwou ingwei nimza maseim o ti, moxo la me wong vateivek lek e xe lul dalus de la xouv.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei lewek o
\p 
\v 47 “Nge no, tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yon nambei lewek wei xel nex e teila eivek lounyeing me qou woing leimalei dalus o.
\v 48 Lewek on pup, xel wei mi qou woing eno puw e leklam yasewis. Woyom xel dei tembuing me beyal woing wei nimza me toung eivek pasik ngenong, dom xel nex nilul o la.
\v 49 Tine inye vati wei tyek qandi lek bouk loxyus o. Angelayeiw tyek nam me beyal xel wei nilul o veil xel wei bombek o
\v 50 me banex xel na eivek nenyex ngandoung wei tyek xel na mi deeng me zanga newound bo nyiknyik o.”
\p 
\v 51 Yesu teling, “Xam ghe woulek lul dalus ti beimambei ne?”
\p Xel lewexe, “Ee.”
\p 
\v 52 Moxo neil wou xel bei, “Nambei nyon xel putoung tambak wei petieing wei woulek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno nambei xomek ti ma wei qou e xe lul wei xomek vateivek o me lul wei takwei me vako eno is me qou de lam myayaing.”
\s1 Poropet wei lei maeing o
\p 
\v 53 Yesu neil qayeeng pakeing ti beimambei ne ma, moxo la veil inyon.
\v 54 Moxo la beeng qes, me teyoxe xomaxoneing eivek xel xe xomek qekueing ama, om xel etek. Xel neil, “Xomaxoneing ne qou kwa ti beimambei ne nanghei inya me di wong lulvako ne?
\v 55 Beip inye se kamunda neu? De ta se lei Maria, me Jems, me Yosep me Simon me Yudas eno se e liyeiw?
\v 56 Beip inye e liyeiw vex se toundei is xey? Woyom moux tine qou lulti beimambei ne dalus nanghei inya?”
\v 57 De xel laleind wo maying en e.
\p Ekom Yesu neil wou xel, “Eivek e maxow beeng qes me eivek e maxow xe xomek inyon poropet wei lei maeing o.”
\p 
\v 58 Om moxo se wong lulvako ngenong ti nanghei inyon, en nambei xel xe wongeingis eno ma.
\c 14
\s1 Yoan lipekeing lukanzek
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk kayon eno Herot seyap tiwei tax o ngo qayeeng en Yesu,
\v 2 om neil wou e xe xel xukxe bei, “Tambiy tine inye Yoan lipekeing. Moxo qandi veil meyeing! Qes tiyon om qou nikanzek me di wong lulvako tine.”
\p 
\v 3 Takwei eno Herot zeimaxoun Yoan me tup e dom toung e eivek xeitueing en Herodias, li Pilip venei,
\v 4 en nambei Yoan neil wou moxo, “Inye se nimza bei wa qou lim Pilip venei.”
\v 5 Herot embei nyeis Yoan, ekom moxo yaleeng en xel xomaxoneing on, en inye xel wou kwend bei tambiy on poropet ti.
\p 
\v 6 Lek Herot xe bouk wei umbek lek eno lam om Herodias neu vexawo yon lam aw om Herot wo xeilala me lalei vind vexo,
\v 7 om wong qayeeng neing is nikanzek wou vexo bei tyek bong vati wei embei teling eno wou e.
\v 8 Lek ta xe woueing nalei, vexo neil, “Wang bong Yoan lipekeing lukanzek wou ay lek dipekta ne.”
\v 9 King moxo lalei wo nimaying, ekom e xe qayeeng wei neil zonghek is vexo me e xe xel wei lam en yaeing o, om moxo neil wou e xe xel bei vexo xe telinyeing embo neing lek
\v 10 om wong xel la qateiv Yoan kwa tip eivek xomek xeitueing.
\v 11 Moxo lukanzek eno xel toung lek dipekta me qou me la wong wou vexawo yon, de vexo qou me la wong wou ta.
\v 12 Yoan xe xel betiyeing lam me qou e neing me la ev. Woyom xel la neil wou Yesu.
\s1 Yesu vet moux 5,000
\p 
\v 13 Yesu ngo vati wei belup on, moxo la veil beyeeng me la lek bot me la ingwei xel ma veil o. Xel qendu ngandoung on ngo tine me betiy e me la vaxend nanghei beyeeng nayak ngenong on.
\v 14 Yesu teila me yei xel qendu ngandoung on, moxo lalei pyaxow en xel om wong xel xe vanei wo nimzalek.
\p 
\v 15 Ka ingwei di souk o, xel betiyeing lam me neil wou e, “Beyeeng bandaing tine xel ma veil, de moxo di bouk tiyo inye mouyo. Wong xel qendu ngandoung on la, en kandek xel na beyeeng nei me na bou xend yaeing valu yo.”
\p 
\v 16 Yesu neil elox, “Xel na enva? Xam ghe bong lul yaeing valu wou xel en xel gya.”
\p 
\v 17 Xel neil wou e, “Yaing ngenong ma veil xa yo, inye belet lim de woing yuw xemou.”
\p 
\v 18 Moxo neil, “Xam qou dalus me lam inye wou ay.”
\v 19 De moxo neil wou xomaxoneing on bei xel mendei tembuing lek lesilek on. Moxo qou belet lim on me qou woing yuw on is dom yeila tyoung gheyapu nei, me wo dange wou dom dembu. Woyom wong wou e xe xel betiyeing, me xel betiyeing wong wou xel xomaxoneing on.
\v 20 Xel dalus on ya me enden xel, de xel betiyeing qekuwou myapapu wei xel se ya yo eivek pasik xoumeeng yuw.
\v 21 Xel moux wei ya yaeing on teyei lek 5,000. Xel se pyaw memend wou xel vex alis neundyeiw.
\s1 Yesu di la lek lounyeing
\p 
\v 22 Lutika eno Yesu wong xel betiyeing la eivek bot me la tax en e me la nge loxalu, dekakom wong xel qendu ngandoung on la.
\v 23 Ka ingwei wong xel on la woy, moxo venaxow lek la lukendu bei na zeimema. Gyeik ingwei boukeing di lam eno e maxow toundei inyon,
\v 24 ekom bot vena la dingta takwei nei veil tembuing, me laweeng vei mamileeng vuk me lam leislek bot is xel.
\p 
\v 25 Ka embim boyaing eno Yesu di la wou xel, me la lek lounyeing mapu.
\v 26 Xel betiyeing yei moxo di la lek lounyeing mapu, om xel yaleeng me neil, “Inye memo ti nu.” Om xel yaleeng me nyayek.
\p 
\v 27 Ekom Yesu wo daing me neil wou xel, “Xam nale nimkanzek! Inye ay yo. Om xam seng gwaleeng.”
\p 
\v 28 Petele neil elox bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wangwei inye wang nei, ond neil me a lak wou wang lek memiing on.”
\p 
\v 29 Moxo neil, “Lam.”
\p Woyom Petele teila veil bot, dom la lek memiing mapu me la wou Yesu.
\v 30 Ekom moxo yei laweeng, moxo yaleeng mouyo, me di teila eivek manghembi, om taxe niseikeing, “Tambiy Ngandoung, vind ay!”
\p 
\v 31 Lutika eno Yesu tatei mema la me vyex e. Moxo neil, “Wa xe wongeingis on nayaka. Wa laleim on wo yuw enva?”
\p 
\v 32 Woyom luw lek la eivek bot, de laweeng on mey.
\v 33 Woyom xel wei toundei eivek bot on wong lalo wou e, me neil, “Neing ayang wang on Anutu Neu Moux.”
\p 
\v 34 Ka xel la nge loxalu, xel teila Genesaret.
\v 35 Xel xomaxoneing wei beyeeng on woulek Yesu, xel wong qayeeng la wou xel xomaxoneing wei mindei paviy beyeeng dalus on. Xomaxoneing dalus on qou xel xe xel wei vanei yo me lam wou e
\v 36 me tay wou e bei xel mou daxlek e xe teimb myasepu, me eti yeiw wei axlek e eno wo nimzalek.
\c 15
\s1 Belin me nilaxes
\p 
\v 1 Woyom xel Parisi valu me xel putoung wei petieing eno lam anghei Yerusalem me lam wou Yesu me teling,
\v 2 “Nambei nya wa xe xel betiyeing mi pyalek petieing wei buyeiw xe kwa wei takwei yo? Xel se mi sekweyexe memend atax ekom mi ya xend yaeing!”
\p 
\v 3 Yesu neil elox bei, “De nambei nya xam ghe pyalek qayeeng petieing wei Anutu xe yo en xam bumim venaxow xe kwa yon?
\v 4 En Anutu neil, ‘Wa mi gwevek mam aluw tam xe qayeeng’\f + \ft Qouloum 20:12\f* me ‘Xel tiwei embei neil vyalek ma luw ta eno xel nyeis e mey.’\f + \ft Qouloum 21:17\f*
\v 5 Ekom xam ghe mi neimbei wangwei tambiy ti e neil wou ma luw ta, ‘Vati wei ambei devind muw eno a beyal wou Anutu takwei nei,’
\v 6 tambiy moxo tyek se gwevek ma no. Lek kwa tiyon xam ghe mi toung demimim wou Anutu dom ghe mi sanghoxe lul wei xam bumimyeiw o.
\v 7 Xam wei myamim yuw o! Poropet Yesaya neil zonghek gyeik moxo neil en xam xe kwa yo.
\q1 
\v 8 “‘Xomaxoneing ti beimambei ne mi pamilexe ay en myend,
\q2 ekom xel laleind on toundei dingta en ay.
\q1 
\v 9 Xel mi wong lalo wou ay bandaing,
\q2 en xel xe teyoxeing ekom xel xe petieing yon lam wou xomaxoneing.’” \rq Yesaya 29:13\rq*
\p 
\v 10 Yesu taxe xel qendu yon lam wou e me neil, “Xam a ngo me ghe boulek.
\v 11 Vati wei mi la eivek eti yeiw myend eno se mi wong e wo nilaxes, qe vati wei lam myayaing veil e mya, eno mi wong e wo nilaxes.”
\p 
\v 12 Woyom xel betiyeing lam wou e me teling, “Beip wa seng woulek bei xel Parisiyeiw laleind wo myavanei gyeik xel ngo qayeeng tine yo?”
\p 
\v 13 Moxo neil elox bei, “Lul dalus wei Mang wei toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu nei se ev eno tyek xel a puw is luselis.
\v 14 Wong xel toukale. Xel on mend tuzeyi. Wangwei tambiy wei matekeing o natax en moux wei matekeing, luw xouing tyek deteina eivek leiveeng.”
\p 
\v 15 Petele neil, “Neil qayeeng pakeing tine qes wou xa.”
\p 
\v 16 Yesu teling wou xel, “Beip xam se ghei woulek no?
\v 17 Xam seng wei bei vati wei mi la eivek xomaxoneing myend me la eivek e xeita de woyom lam myayaing veil e me la eivek leiveeng?
\v 18 Ekom vati wei lam myayaing veil wa myam inyon lam anghei wa laleim nei, me ti beimambei ne mi wong xomaxoneing mi wo nilaxes.
\v 19 Inyon woueing nalei nilul, leiseing xel, kwa nilul wei iingama, kwa nilul wei kwapesiv o, panaxeing, qayeeng tyonyeing me lukyak lek xel nge eno lam myayaing veil xe laleind.
\v 20 Lulti beimambei ne ingwei mi wong xomaxoneing mi wo nilaxes, ekom yaeing is memend laxes eno se mi wong e wo nilaxes.”
\s1 Vex wei Kenan o xe wongeingis
\p 
\v 21 Yesu la veil beyeeng tiyon me la tembuing danghei wei Taia me Saidon nei.
\v 22 Kenan vex ti lam wou e, me di eng niseikeing, “Tambiy Ngandoung, Dawit Neu Moux, pyanaleim en ay! A neung vex toundei eivek nimaying ngandoung en memo wo nilul wou e.”
\p 
\v 23 Yesu se neil qayeeng ti lox. Om e xe xel betiyeing lam wou e me neil, “Wong vex on la, en vexo di eng xounaxoun me lam yus en xey.”
\p 
\v 24 Moxo lewexe, “Anutu wong a lam en xel sipsip wei Israel o venaxow wei lati yo.”
\p 
\v 25 Vex on lam me ev vaxakatu eivek atax wou e de neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, vind ay!”
\p 
\v 26 Yesu neil elox bei, “Inye se nimza bei qoueing yakyak xe belet me banex e na wou xel naw.”
\p 
\v 27 Vexo neil, “Ee, Tambiy Ngandoung, ekom xel naw mi ya myapapu wei mi teila eivek xel xe teiv xe lelek xeinghembi yo.”
\p 
\v 28 Woyom Yesu lewexe, “Vex, wa xe wongeingis on ngandoung! Wa xe telinyeing on embo neing lek nambei wa laleim vind o.” Om neu vex on wo nimzalek seivma kayon bombek.
\s1 Yesu vet xel 4,000
\p 
\v 29 Yesu la veil beyeeng tiyon dom la lounyeing Galili. Woyom moxo lek la lukendu nenya me dei tembuing.
\v 30 Xel qendu ngandoung on lam wou e, xel qou xel bezombeing, me matekeing, vaxa nol, me myatueing me xel valu beti is me toung xel wou Yesu vaxa, de e wong xel wo nimzalek.
\v 31 Xel xomaxoneing on etek en ingwei xel yei tambiy wei myatu eno luk no, me xel bezombeing wo nimzalek, me vaxa nol la me ingwei matekeing eno yeila. Me xel sanghoxe Anutu wei Israel o.
\p 
\v 32 Yesu taxe e xe xel betiyeing la wou e me neil, “A laleing pyaxow en xel xomaxoneing ti beimambei ne, en xel lam toundei inye is ay teyei lek bouk yayal de xel se ya lulti. Ambei se bong xel na maxep, enok xel mend bivek me pewilexe wou sakwaing.”
\p 
\v 33 E xe xel betiyeing lewexe, “Tyek xa qou belet anghei inya me na bong wou xel ngenong ne eivek beyeeng bandaing ne?”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu teling, “Xam ghe di qou belet vamva?”
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Lim yuw, de woing nayak matika is.”
\p 
\v 35 Moxo neil wou xel qendu yon bei xel mendei lek tembuing.
\v 36 Woyom qou belet lim yuw on is woing, de wong dange wou woy, om dembu me wong wou xel betiyeing, me xel la wong wou xel xomaxoneing on.
\v 37 Xel on dalus ya me enden xel. Dekalekom xel betiyeing qekuwou myapapu wei wo pupuv o me sei ela eivek pasik lim yuw me e pup.
\v 38 Xel wei ya yaeing on teyei lek 4,000. De xel se pyaw memend wou vex alis neuyeiw.
\v 39 Ka Yesu wong xel on la, moxo la eivek bot me la beyeeng wei Magadan nei.
\c 16
\s1 Xel neil wou Yesu en dee
\p 
\v 1 Xel Parisi me xel Sadyusi lam wou Yesu me wo axeing wou e me teling wou bei e talex dee wei tyoung gheyapu nei ti wou xel.
\p 
\v 2 Moxo neil elox bei, “Gyeik soukeing lam, eno laxap wo gyand om xam ghe neimbei ‘Inye tyek bo nimza,’
\v 3 de satiboukeing lul eno xam ghe neimbei, ‘De wangwei sayeiv nam a tyip, me na siing lek tyoung me wo gyand ekom laxap wo xeingak me sevun tyoung, woyom xel woulek bei laweeng tyek na tyip me luing detei.’ Xam ghe mi wei dee wei tyoung me ghe woulek ewo nimza, ekom nambei nya xam seng woulek dee wei bouk ti gweimbeeng ne yo.
\v 4 Xel moux alis vex nilul wei bouk tine wei mi toung demind wou Anutu yo eno xel embei gyei dee wei lulvako yo, ekom xel se teyei bei gyei dee ti qe dee wei poropet Yona yo.” Woyom Yesu la veil xel me la.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei Yis wei xel Parisi me Sadyusiyeiw o
\p 
\v 5 Gyeik xel betiyeing la is Yesu me la lounyeing nge loxalu, xel naleind ma me se qou belet ti.
\v 6 Yesu neil wou xel, “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en yis wei xel Parisi me Sadyusiyeiw o.”
\p 
\v 7 Xel neil tine eivek ama senghoing me neil, “En inye nambei xey se qou belet ti.”
\p 
\v 8 Yesu woulek xel xe qayeeng wei xel di luklek on om neil wou xel, “Xam xe wongeingis on nayaka. Nambei nya xam ghe di pyalek ama en ingwei belet ma yo?
\v 9 Beip xam seng ghei woulek? Beip xam seng wou naleimim en belet lim wei xel xomaxoneing 5,000 ya yo, me pasik vamva wei xam ghe qekuwou yo?
\v 10 O belet lim yuw wou xel 4,000, me pasik vamva wei xam ghe qekuwou yo?
\v 11 Nambei nya xam seng woulek bei a se di luk wou xam en belet om a neil qayeeng tine wou xam? Ekom xam ghe gweiteyei xow en yis wei xel Parisi me Sadyusiyeiw o.”
\v 12 Woyom xel woulek bei moxo se di teling xel bei xel gyei xow teyei en yis wei xel mi toung eivek belet o, qe en teyoxeing wei xel Parisi me Sadyusiyeiw o.
\s1 Petele neil Kilisi teyei
\p 
\v 13 Yesu la eivek tembuing danghei wei Sisalia Pilipai eno moxo teling wou e xe xel betiyeing, “Xel xomaxoneing mi neil embei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux on eti?”
\p 
\v 14 Xel neil elox bei, “Xel valu mi neil embei wa Yoan lipekeing. De valu mi neil embei wa Eliya, me valu mi neil embei wa Yelemia o tambiy wei poropet o ti.”
\v 15 Om moxo teling xel, “ekom xam ghe neimbei ay eti?”
\p 
\v 16 Simon Petele lewexe, “Wang on Kilisi, Anutu mapieing neu moux.”
\p 
\v 17 Yesu neil elox, “Simon Yona neu, mata e nak wou wang, en xomaxoneing ti se neil inye teyei wou wang, qe inye lam wou Mang wei toundei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 18 De a neil wou wang bei wang on Petele qes bei qakous, me lek qakous tine tyek a bong a xe xel wongeingis bo ngenong, me bale nikanzek lek e de nikanzek wei meyeing eno tyek se nam lelolexe inyon.
\v 19 Tyek am bong ki wei tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei eno wou wang, om vati wei wambei tup lek tembuing eno tyek Anutu na tup anghei tyoung gheyapu nei, de vati wei wa tul lek tembuing ne eno tyek Anutu na tul veil anghei tyoung gheyapu nei.”
\v 20 Woyom moxo peti e xe xel betiyeing bei xel se neilteyei bei e Kilisi.
\s1 Yesu neil e xe meyeing teyei ti myaxeeng
\p 
\v 21 Qandi eivek bouk kayon eno Yesu neilteyei wou e xe xel betiyeing bei tyek na Yerusalem me na qou myavanei ngenong lek xel teivateiv me xel lumuki leitata me xel putoung wei petieing o memend, me xel nyeis e mey de lek bouk yal eno moxo tyek qandi lek veil meyeing.
\p 
\v 22 Om Petele qou moxo me la nenyawes me luk niseikeing atax wou e, “Tambiy Ngandoung, se teyei ti! Lul tine tyek se belup wou wang!”
\p 
\v 23 Yesu pekwi ma me neil wou Petele, “Sandang, la a deming! Wambei bale zeyi ay. Wa lum on se betiwou lulul wei Anutu yo, qe lulul wei xomaxoneing o.”
\p 
\v 24 Woyom Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing, “Wangwei tambiy ti embei betiwou ay, ond e dax xow vun dom qalei e xe xax pepeeng me betiwou ay.
\v 25 En wangwei xelti embei zeimaxoun e xe mapieing yond tyek na saing veil, ekom xelti embei saing e xe mapieing en ay eno tyek na qou e xe mapieing.
\v 26 Wangwei tambiy ti e qou lul dalus wei tembuing sapa ne yo, dom na saing ning mapieing, on tyek na qou lul nimza vati? Moux on tyek bo xouveing vati zeyi ning nu pieing?
\v 27 En Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek nam is Ma xe xeiyaing ngandoung is e xe xel angela, de woyom moxo tyek bong xouveing wou xel titi teyei lek vati wei xel mi wong o.
\v 28 A neil wou xam zonghek, xel valu wei toukale inye eno tyek se daxe meyeing atax, qe ka xel gyei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux nam eivek e xe tete lalei le.”
\c 17
\s1 Yesu neing pekwi bange
\p 
\v 1 Ka bouk limti la veil eno Yesu qou Petele me Jems me Yoan inyon Jems li, me qou xel venaxow me la lek lukendu vaxading ti.
\v 2 Nanghei inyon eno moxo neing pekwi me wo bange wou xel mend. Me ma siing nambei sayeiv me e xe teimb wo pus ambei xeiyaing.
\v 3 Dekakom Mose luw Eliya lam tyip wou xel mendghalus me di luk is Yesu.
\p 
\v 4 Om Petele neil wou Yesu, “Tambiy Ngandoung, inye nimza bei xey a toumendei inye. Wangwei wa laleim devind nei, on tyek a sakev xomek nayak yayal, ti wou wang, de ti wou Mose de ti wou Eliya.”
\p 
\v 5 Ka moxo di luk, laxap teltyip me lam wo tenu zeyi xel, me vya ti lam anghei laxap nei me neil, “Tine inye a neung, e tiwei a laleing vind o, a wo xeinglala en e. Om xam a mi ngo e!”
\p 
\v 6 Xel betiyeing ngo tine me xel ev vaxend qatu eivek de mend la lek tembuing, is yalenyeing mouyo.
\v 7 Ekom Yesu lam axlek lal. Moxo neil, “Qandi lek. Mal seng gwaleeng.”
\v 8 Om lal veil mendlek, eno lal se yei xelti, qe Yesu venaxow.
\p 
\v 9 Ka xel di lam axo veil lukendu, Yesu luk nikanzek wou xel bei, “Xam se neil wou xelti en vati wei xam ghe wei ne, qe ka Xomaxoneing Neu Moux qandi lek veil meyeing le.”
\p 
\v 10 Xel betiyeing teling wou e, “Inye xel putoung wei petieing eno neil embei Eliya tyek nam a tax enva?”
\p 
\v 11 Yesu neil elox bei, “Xam ghe boulek neing bei Eliya e nam me menyex wou lulul dalus.
\v 12 Ekom a neil wou xam bei, Eliya lam takwei nei, ekom xel se woulek e, qe xel wong kwa leimalei wou e teyei lek woueing nalei wei xel o. Eivek sakwaing kayon eno Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek na qou nimaying ngandoung lek xel memend.”
\v 13 Woyom xel betiyeing woulek bei moxo di luk en Yoan Lipekeing.
\s1 Yesu wong yak ghavis wei laweeng nol dei eivek e yo wo nimza
\p 
\v 14 Yesu is betiyeing yal on la wou xel qendu yon. Moux ti lam wou Yesu me ev vaxa qatu eivek wou e manghalus.
\v 15 Moxo neil, “Tambiy Ngandoung, wa pyanaleim en a neung moux en mi puw vaxa mema me mindei eivek nimaying. Moxo mi pewilexe eivek nenyex, o mi teila eivek memiing.
\v 16 A qou e me na lam wou wa xe xel betiyeing, ekom xel se teyei bei bong embo nimzalek.”
\p 
\v 17 Yesu neil elox bei, “O xam moux alis vex wei se mi wongis eno xam xe woueing nalei me kwa eno se la teyei lek. Tyek a mendei is xam bouk vamva? Me teyei lek bouk vamva eno tyek a mi qalei nimaying wei xam o? Qou ghavis on me lam wou ay.”
\v 18 Yesu neil laweeng nol on, dom e lam myayaing veil ghavis on, om ghavis on wo nimza lek seivma kayon bombek.
\p 
\v 19 Woyom xel betiyeing venaxow lam wou Yesu me teling, “Nambei nya ekom xa se teyei bei tiy inyon na myayaing?”
\p 
\v 20 Moxo neil elox bei, “Xam xe wongeingis on nayaka. A neil wou xam zonghek, wangwei xam xe wongeingis nayaka nambei mastet neughalus, wa teyei bei neil wou lukendu tine, ‘La veil inye me la inyei,’ on tyek na ngo me na. Lulti tyek se bo pok wou wang. [
\v 21 Ekom lul ambei nye tyek se nam myayaing, qe nangya zeimeing me vambueing yaeing.”]
\p 
\v 22 Yesu is e xe xel betiyeing la me qekuma nanghei Galili, woyom moxo neil wou xel, “Tyek xel a toung Xomaxoneing Neu Moux na eivek xomaxoneing memend.
\v 23 Me tyek xel nyeis e mey, de lek bouk yal eno moxo tyek qandi lek mapieing.” Xel betiyeing ngo qayeeng tine om moxoyeiw laleind wo maying.
\s1 Da wei xomek vambuing o
\p 
\v 24 Ka Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing la tyip Kapenaom, xel wei mi qou takis wei xomek vambuing eno lam me teling wou Petele, “Beip xam xe putoung se mi toung takis wei xomek vambuing o?”
\p 
\v 25 Moxo neil elox wou xel bei, “E, mi toung o.” Ka Petele lam eivek xomek eno Yesu luk ti myaxeeng me teling, “Simon, wang wou naleimim ambei nya? Xel king wei tembuing ne yo mi qou takis leimalei wou eti, wou xel venaxow neundyeiw, o wou xel amba?”
\p 
\v 26 Petele neil, “Wou xel amba.”
\p Yesu neil wou e, “Om xel venaxow neundyeiw se teyei bei toung takis.
\v 27 Ekom xey se bong anghei xel laleind bo nol wou xe nei, om la lounyeing nei me nex wa xe ying la eivek. Woing tiwei wang qou tax o, wa tax e mya de tyek wangwei malew selewa ngandoung ti. Wa qou me ghe na bong wou xel en aning takis de wa nim is ambei nyon.”
\c 18
\s1 Eti wo lei ngandoung eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei
\p 
\v 1 Lek bouk kayon eno xel betiyeing lam wou Yesu me teling, “Eti wo lei ngandoung eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei?”
\p 
\v 2 Moxo taxe yak tika me wong e nale eivek xel senghoing.
\v 3 De neil, “A neil wou xam zonghek, wangwei xam se pekwi me ghe ghok ambei yak kane, on tyek xam seng teyei bei na eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo.
\v 4 Nambei nyon, eti yeiw wei mi beoux xow nambei yak kane eno wo lei ngandoung eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\p 
\v 5 “Me eti yeiw wei qou yak ambei nye eivek a leing, eno qou ay.
\v 6 Enok tambiy ti bong yak ti beimambei wei wongis a ne detei en sewokeing, ond inye teyei bei xel banoux qakous ngandoung lek e kwa dom banex e deteina heivek mamileeng me e mey.
\p 
\v 7 “Inye lalei pyaweing en xomaxoneing wei tembuing ne eno mi wong xel amba mi tei en sewokeing. Zonghek, lul nilul ambei nyon eno tyek nam, ekom tambiy wei wong inyon tyip eno e gyaleeng!
\v 8 Om wangwei wa memam o wa vaxam na toung wang eivek sewokeing, ond qateiv veil me nex e la. Inye nimza bei wang na eivek mapieing luta luta is memam tixemou o vaxam tixemou, enok wa memam yuw o vaxam yuw ekom xel banex wang na eivek nenyex wei luta luta yo.
\v 9 Me wangwei wa mamghalus na toung wang eivek sewokeing, ond qepei e lam myayaing me nex e la. Inye nimza bei wang na mendei mapieing is mamghalus tixemou enok wa mamghalus yuw ekom xel banex wang na eivek nenyex wei luta luta yo.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei sipsip lati yo
\p 
\v 10 “Xam ghe gweiteyei en kandek xam se neimbei yakyak ambei inye lul bandaing. En a neil wou xam bei xel xe angela eivek tyoung gheyapu nei eno mi yei Mang wei tyoung gheyapu nei manghalus.
\v 11 [En Xomaxoneing Neu Moux lam bei qou eti yeiw wei lati yo noum.]
\p 
\v 12 “Wang wou naleim ambei nya? Wangwei tambiy ti xe sipsip teyei lek 100, ekom ti nati, yond tyek moxo se teyei bei ghanaw 99 on lek qetyei dom na gyimexe tiwei lati yo?
\v 13 De wangwei e gyeiwou nei, a neil wou xam zonghek, moxo tyek bo xeilala en tiwei lati yo de se 99 wei se lati yo.
\v 14 Eivek sakwaing ambei nyon eno Mam wei toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu embei yakyak on ti se nati.
\s1 Wa lim wei wo sewokeing wou wang o
\p 
\v 15 “Wangwei lim bo sewokeing wou wang, ond eivek muw venaxow senghoing eno la me neil e xe nilul teyei wou e. Wangwei e ngowou wa xe qayeeng, yon nambei wang qou lim loum.
\v 16 Ekom wangwei e se ngowou nei, yon wa qou tambiy ti o yuw is xow, en kandek ‘pavulek tambak wei moux yuw o yal eno na byexaxoun qayeeng.’\f + \fr 18:16 \ft Petieing 19:15 qayeeng veweeng eno neil ambei nye, “Pavulek tambak wei moux yuw o yal eno na byexaxoun qayeeng.”\f*
\v 17 Wangwei e bei se ngowou xel xe qayeeng, yon wa neil wou kongrikesin dalus. Ek wangwei e pyalek kongrikesin xe qayeeng, ond xam ghe gwei e bei inyon tambiy wei mandalus o tambiy wei mi qou takis o ti.
\p 
\v 18 “A neil wou xam zonghek, vatiyeiw wei xam ghe tup lek tembuing eno tyek Anutu na tup eivek tyoung gheyapu, de vatiyeiw wei xam ghe tul lek tembuing eno tyek Anutu na tul veil eivek tyoung gheyapu.
\p 
\v 19 “A neil wou xam no bei, wangwei xam on yuw na toung laleimim lekti en vati wei muw ambei teling en eno tyek Mang wei tyoung gheyapu nei bong wou muw.
\v 20 En wangwei muw yuw o mal yal a being nam qeku lekti eivek a leing, inyon a toundei is mal.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing en xukxe wei lalei pyaweing ma veil e yo
\p 
\v 21 Woyom Petele lam wou Yesu me teling, “Tambiy Ngandoung, teyei lek lu vamva eno a teyei bei semaleeng ling xe nilul gyeik ingwei embo sewokeing wou ay yo? Ena teyei lek lim yuw?”
\p 
\v 22 Yesu neil elox, “A neil wou wang, se lu lim yuw, qe teyei lek lu lim yuw me e mi na lumama teyei lek 70.
\p 
\v 23 “Nambei nyon, tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno inye nambei king ti embei menyex wou malew vateivek is e xe xel xukxe wei xel qou wou e yo.
\v 24 Ka moxo qandi en menyex wou malew vateivek, moxo taxe tambiy wei qou malew 10,000 eno lam wou e.
\v 25 Ekom moxo se teyei bei bong malew zeyi, om teiv wo qayeeng nikanzek bei xel bong vateivek lek lis venei neu me lulul dalus wei e beeng o de bong ena zeyi malew vateivek wei qou yo.
\p 
\v 26 “Xukxe ev vaxa qatu eivek atax wou e me tay, ‘Wam di daxe ay, en tyek a bong lulul dalus nouk wou wang.’
\v 27 Teiv wei xukxe yon pyanalei en e, om semaleeng malew vateivek wei qou yo dom wong e la.
\p 
\v 28 “Ekom xukxe tiyon la myayaing, moxo yeiwou e xe laxous tiwei luw mi wo xuk lekti yo wei qou malew 100 wou e yo. Moxo sex e kwa de luk nikanzek wou e, ‘Wang bong vati wei wang qou wou ay eno noum!’
\p 
\v 29 “Moxo xe laxous wei luw mi wong xuk lekti eno ev vaxa qatu eivek me tay wou e, ‘Wam di daxe ay, en tyek a bong malew vateivek wei a qou eno nouk zeyi wou wang.’
\p 
\v 30 “Ekom moxo se lewexe lek. Qe la veil de toung laxous la eivek xeitueing deka embong malew vateivek wei qou yo noum zeyi le.
\v 31 Woyom laxousyeiw valu yei vati wei belup on eno xel laleind wo myavanei ngandoung. Om xel la neil wou xel xe teiv en lul sapa wei belup on.
\p 
\v 32 “Woyom teiv taxe xukxe la lalei me neil, ‘Wa xukxe nilul ayang. A semaleeng wa xe malew vateivek dalus wei wang o, en nambei wang tay wou ay.
\v 33 Se teyei bei wa pyanaleim en laxous nge wei muw ghe mi wo xuk o nambei ingwei a wong wou wang o?’
\v 34 Teiv moxo lalei wo vanei wou e om toung e la wou xel belimbo wei xeitueing o bei xel bong vanei wou e, deka e bong lulul dalus wei e qou yo noum bole.
\p 
\v 35 “Tine inye Mang wei tyoung gheyapu nei tyek bong wou xam titi yo, wangwei wa se semaleeng nilul wei limyeiw nge wong wou wang eivek laleim o.”
\c 19
\s1 Qateiv iingama veil
\p 
\v 1 Gyeik Yesu neil qayeeng ti beimambei ne ma, woyom moxo la veil Galili me la eivek tembuing wei Yudia me la loxalu wei memiing Yorodan nei.
\v 2 Xel qendu ngandoung betiwou e, om moxo wong xel wo nimzalek nanghei inyon.
\p 
\v 3 Xel Parisi valu lam wou e bei bong axeing wou e. Xel teling, “Beip inyei petieing neil embei moux ti qateiv iingama wei venei yo veil en woueing nalei wei emaxow o?”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu neil elox, “Beip xam seng pyaw qayeeng wei di yeip eivek qapiya wei Anutu yo bei, eivek myaxeeng eno ‘Anutu toung xomaxoneing, moux aluw vex,’ Myaxeeng selis 1:27
\v 5 de neil, ‘En qes tine moux tyek na veil ma luw ta me luw venei na toung lekti me luw bo neing tixemou?’ Myaxeeng selis 2:24
\v 6 Om luw se wo yuw no, qe luw wo neing tixemou. Nambei nyon vati wei Anutu tup lekti, eno xomaxoneing ti se qateiv e tip.”
\p 
\v 7 Xel teling, “Woyom nambei nya Mose wong qayeeng nikanzek bei moux e bong qapiya wou venei en qateiv iingama de bong vex on na?”
\p 
\v 8 Yesu neil elox, “Mose lenghek lek bei xam qateiv iingama en nambei xam laleimim on wo nikanzekta. Ekom myaxeeng eno kwa nambei inyon eno ma.
\v 9 Om a neil wou xam bei wangwei tambiy ti venei se bo kwapesiv is tambiy nge ekom leya qateiv iingama wei luw o, dom dii vex nge yond moux on venaxow wo kwapesiv.”
\p 
\v 10 Xel betiyeing neil wou e, “Wangwei kwa nambei nyon gyeip senghoing eivek moux ti luw venei, ond inye nimza bei moux tiyon se dii vex.”
\p 
\v 11 Yesu neil elox wou xel bei, “Xel ngenong tyek se qou qayeeng tine, qe wou xel valu wei Anutu wong nikanzek wou xel eno tyek bong ambei nyon de tyek xel se diima.
\v 12 En moux valu nikanzek wei embei bo yak eno ma gyeik ingwei umbek o, me xel valu eno xomaxoneing veil e nikanzek, de xel valu eno se ii vex en xel wou kwend en xuk tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu yo. Tambiy ti embei qou kwa nambei nye ond wong e qou.”
\s1 Xel yakyak me Yesu
\p 
\v 13 Woyom xel qou yakyak me lam wou Yesu bei e ni mema lek xel me na zeim wou xel. Ekom xel betiyeing luk nikanzek wou eti yeiw wei qou xel me lam o.
\p 
\v 14 Yesu neil, “Wong xel yakyak on lam wou ay, de xam se bale zeyi xel, en tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei eno inye wou xel ambei nyon.”
\v 15 Gyeik e li mema lek xel woy, woyom moxo la veil inyon me la.
\s1 Tambiy ghavis wei lulul ana yo
\p 
\v 16 Tambiy ti lam wou Yesu me teling, “Putoung, lul nimza vati a teyei bei bong dom na qou mapieing luta?”
\p 
\v 17 Yesu neil elox, “Wang teling ay en vati wei nimza yo en va? Inyon Anutu venaxow nimza. Wangwei wa bei qou mapieing luta nei, ond wa betiwou qayeeng petieing dalus.”
\p 
\v 18 Moux moxo teling, “Tina?”
\p Om Yesu neil elox, “ ‘Wa seng nyeis xel amey. Wa seng bo kwapesiv is vex wei dei leya yo. Wa se panax. Wa seng bong qayeeng tyonyeing wou xel.
\v 19 Wa mi gwevek mam aluw tam. Wa laleim e mi devind nimpapu nambei wa laleim mi vind wamaxow o.’ ” \rq Qouloum 20:12-16; Lumuki 19:18\rq*
\p 
\v 20 Tambiy ghavis on neil wou e, “Petieing dalus eno a mi betiwou. De vati tyek am bong no?”
\p 
\v 21 Yesu lewexe, “Wangwei wambei mendei bo nimza nei, ond la wo vateivek lek lulul dalus wei wang o me wong wou xel kanyoyeiw, de tyek wa qou lul nimza ngenong nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei. Woyom wang nam betiwou ay.”
\p 
\v 22 Ekom tambiy ghavis on ngo qayeeng tine, om moxo lalei wo maying ngandoung me la, en nambei e xe lulul ngenongakes.
\p 
\v 23 Woyom Yesu neil wou e xe xel betiyeing, “A neil wou xam zonghek, inye pok ngandoung en lulul ana embei na eivek tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei yo.
\v 24 A neil wou xam no bei, inye pok neing en ingwei kamel embei na eivek ying manghalus wei duweing o, de pok wei malew ana ti embei na eivek tete lalei wei Anutu xe yo eno ghanaw xel amba ne.”
\p 
\v 25 Yesu xe xel betiyeing ngo tine, moxoyeiw etek niseikeing me teling, “Wangwei nambei nyon nei ond tyek eti mendei mapieing luta?”
\p 
\v 26 Yesu yeila xel de neil, “Wou xel xomaxoneing eno inye se teyei, ekom is Anutu eno lulul dalus on teyei.”
\p 
\v 27 Petele lewexe lek e, “Xa ghanaw lul dalus bei betiwou wou wang! Woyom tyek xa qou vati?”
\p 
\v 28 Yesu neil wou xel, “A neil wou xam zonghek, gyeik kawei lul dalus embei bong vako, eno Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei mendei lek e xe sia vambuing wei lei ngandoung o, xam eti yeiw wei ghe mi betiwou ay eno tyek xam mendei lek a xe sia xoumeeng yuw wei vambuing, me ghe gwei veleivlei xoumeeng yuw wei Israel o teyei.
\v 29 Me xel sapa wei ghanaw xel xe xomek, o liyeiw moux, o liyeiw vex, o ma, o ta, o neuyeiw, o xuk en a leing yon tyek na qou 100 ngenong is me tyek xam a qou mapieing luta luta.
\v 30 Ekom xel ngenong wei lam atax eno tyek nox yus, de xel ngenong wei lam yus eno tyek na tax.”
\c 20
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing lek xel xukxe wei mi wong xuk eivek xuk wain o
\p 
\v 1 “En tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno nambei tembuing ma ti la satiboukeing lulayang bei na qou xel moux en xel na bong xuk eivek e xe xuk wain.
\v 2 Moxo lewexe lek xel bei dexouv xel en malew selewa ti lek bouk titi dom wong xel la eivek e xe xuk wain.
\p 
\v 3 “Lek seivma nambei limvey eno tambiy moxo la me yei xel valu toungale eivek beyeeng vateivek dom xel se di wong lulti.
\v 4 Moxo neil wou xel, ‘Xam is ambei nyon xam ghe na bong xuk eivek a xe xuk wain, de tyek a dexouv xam en xouveing wei bombek o.’
\v 5 Om moxoyeiw la.
\p “Moxo lox me la lek ingwei seivma evlek me seivma yal soukeing eno wong kwa kawei yo no.
\v 6 Lek seivma lim soukeing kayon eno moxo la no me yei xel valu nanghei toungale bandabanda. Moxo teling xel, ‘Nambei nya xam ghe mi nale inye bouk tine dalus dom xuk maeing?’
\p 
\v 7 “ Xel lewexe, ‘En nambei xelti se qou xa en xuk.’
\p “Moxo neil wou xel, ‘Xam is ambei nyon xam ghe na bong xuk eivek a xe xuk wain.’
\p 
\v 8 “Lek soukeing kayon, eno xuk wain ma neil wou e xe tambiy wei lam xeinghembi en e yo bei, ‘Taxe xel wei wo xuk o lam me xouv xel. Myaxeeng eno wa dexouv xel wei lam yusayang o me mendi na dekakom ghe na wou xel wei lam atax o.’
\p 
\v 9 “Xel wei wo xuk lek seivma lim eno lam me xel titi qou malew selewa titi.
\v 10 Om gyeik xel wei lam wo xuk atax eno xel embeik nge tyek xel a qou malew zekna ghanaw xel valu wei lam yus o. Ekom xel titi eno qou malew selewa titi.
\v 11 Xel qou xouveing woy, eno moxoyeiw luk ngenong is tembuing ma.
\v 12 Moxoyeiw neil, ‘Xel moux tiwei lam wo xuk yus eno xel wo xuk teyei lek seivma ti, ekom wang wong xel qou malew teyei lek ambei xa wei wo xuk ngandoung wou seiv myavanei lek bouk tine dalus o.’
\p 
\v 13 “Ekom moxo lewexe lek xel on ti, ‘Gweleeng, a se wo nol wou wang. Beip wa seng lewexe lek bei bong xuk en malew selewa ti?
\v 14 Qou wa xe xouveing me la. Ambei bong malew wou tambiy wei lam wong xuk yus o nambei ingwei a wong wou wang ne yo.
\v 15 Beip inye se di yeip wou a bei a bong vati en a maxow xe malew? O inye a memang les om wang qouwou ay?’
\p 
\v 16 “Om nambei nyon xel wei la yus eno tyek na tax, de xel wei lam atax eno tyek na yusayang.”
\s1 Yesu neil e xe meyeing teyei luyal en ingwei embei mey yo
\p 
\v 17 Ka Yesu di la pu Yerusalem nei, moxo qou e xe xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw me xel venaxow la nenyawes me neil wou xel,
\v 18 “Wei, xey am bei na pu Yerusalem nei, en Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek xel a toung e na eivek xel lumuki leitata me xel putoung wei petieing o memend. Me tyek xel bo qayeeng en e me na neimbei e mey,
\v 19 me tyek xel a toung e na eivek xel amba memend en xel a neil seloukeing lek e me sesa e me na tuw e lek xax pepeeng. De lek bouk yal eno moxo tyek qandi lek mapieing!”
\s1 Vex ti tay wou Yesu en neu luw
\p 
\v 20 Woyom Sebedi neu luw lam is tend wou Yesu, me ev vaxa qatu eivek me teling Yesu en e xe lalei vineing.
\p 
\v 21 Moxo teling, “Inye wa laleim vind vati?”
\p Vexo neil, “A laleind vind bei a neung yuw ne eno nge mendei wou wa memam payeiv de nge wou wa memam qeinz eivek wa xe tete lalei.”
\p 
\v 22 Yesu neil wou luw, “Muw seng woulek vati wei muw ghe teling en o. Muw ghe teyei bei num eivek mayamya wei ambei num eivek ne?”
\p Luw neil, “Uw a teyei.”
\p 
\v 23 Yesu neil wou luw, “Tyek muw a num eivek a xe mayamya, ekom deing wou a memang payeiv o qeinz eno inye se wou ay bei a zenghek lek. Beyeeng tine inye wou eti yeiw wei Mang venaxow menyex woy wou xel o.”
\p 
\v 24 Ka xel xoumeeng ngo qayeeng tine, eno xel wo veweeng wou Yoan aluw li.
\v 25 Yesu taxe xel xouing lam me neil, “Xam ghe woulek bei king wei xel amba eno mi wo ninkanzek bei gyeiteyei xel, me xel xe lei ngandoung mi wo ninkanzek bei moux alis vex na mi betiwou qayeeng tambak wei xel o.
\v 26 Om se is xam. Qe eti bei bo lei ngandoung eivek xam senghoing ond e bong ambei xam xe xukxe,
\v 27 me eti embei na tax ond e bong ambei xam xe xukxe bandaing,
\v 28 teyei lek ambei nyon eno Xomaxoneing Neu Moux se lam bei tyek moux alis vex devind e, qe lam bei bong e xe mapieing nambei xouveing en xomaxoneing ngenong.”
\p 
\v 29 Ka Yesu lis e xe xel betiyeing la veil Jeriko, xel qendu ngandoung on betiwou e.
\v 30 Moux matekeing yayuw toundei wou sakwaing vi, om gyeik luw ngo bei Yesu di lamela, luw taxe, “Tambiy Ngandoung, Dawit Neu Moux, pyanaleim en uw!”
\p 
\v 31 Xel qendu yon luk nikanzek wou luw bei denduing ma, ekom luw taxe niseikeing, “Tambiy Ngandoung, Dawit Neu Moux, pyanaleim en uw!”
\p 
\v 32 Yesu nale dom taxe luw. Moxo teling, “Muw ambei a bong vati wou muw?”
\p 
\v 33 Luw lewexe, “Tambiy Ngandoung, uw ambei gheina yo.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu lalei pyaxow en luw om axlek luw xouing mendghalus. De se denlek en luw mend yeila de luw betiwou e.
\c 21
\s1 Yesu la eivek Yerusalem nambei king
\p 
\v 1 Ka xel la tyip paviy Yerusalem me la Betpage lek lukendu Oliv nei, Yesu wong betiyeing yuw la,
\v 2 me neil wou luw, “Muw ghe na beyeeng tiwei muw mamim di yeila nei, lutika eno tyek muw ghe gwei dongi ti xel tup anghei inyon, is neu lingheing toukale lip ta. Muw wa tul luw xouing me na qou me ghe nam wou ay.
\v 3 Wangwei xelti neil lulti wou muw, ond muw a neil wou bei Tambiy Ngandoung embei bong xuk en, dom tyek bong luw noum daing.”
\p 
\v 4 Lul tine la teyei lek lul tiwei Anutu neil eivek poropet mya yo:
\q1 
\v 5 “Neil wou Sayon neu vex,
\q2 ‘Wei, xam xe king lam wou xam.
\q1 Moxo lam ambei tambiy wei lei maeing o me dei lek dongi ti.
\q2 Moxo dei lek dongi lingheing ti me lam.’” \rq Sakarias 9:9\rq*
\p 
\v 6 Betiyeing aluw la me wong e la teyei lek kawei Yesu neil wou luw o.
\v 7 Luw qou dongi ta me neu lingheing, me vax luw xe teimb ding lek luw, de Yesu deilek lek.
\v 8 Xel qendu ngandoung on vax xel xe teimb ding lek sakwaing, de xel valu qateiv xax memama me liw lek sakwaing.
\v 9 Xel qendu ngandoung wei la mamunghexeing en e me xel wei di betiwou eno di taxe bei,
\q1 “Hosana ena wou Dawit Neu Moux!
\q1 Mata ena wou tiwei lam eivek Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo! \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:26\rq*
\q1 Hosana ena eivek tyoung gheyapu nei!”
\b
\p 
\v 10 Gyeik Yesu la eivek Yerusalem eno moux alis vex dalus wei beyeeng ngandoung on etek om xel teling, “Tambiy on eti?”
\p 
\v 11 Xel qendu yon lewexe, “Tine inye Yesu, poropet wei lam anghei Nasaret eivek Galili yo.”
\s1 Yesu tiy xel wei wo vateivek veil xomek vambuing
\p 
\v 12 Yesu la eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing o me tiy xel wei di xouv lulul me wo vateivek anghei inyon o. Moxo qapyex lelek wei xel di pelipek malew me eti yeiw wei di wo vateivek lek menek beliy o.
\v 13 Moxo neil wou xel, “Xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye, ‘A xe xomek tyek xel taxe bei xomek wei zeimeing mema yo,’\f + \fr 21:13 \ft Yesaya 56:7\f* ekom xam ghe pelipek e xok ambei ‘eeng wei xel panaxana yo.’\f + \fr 21:13 \ft Yelemia 7:11\f*”
\p 
\v 14 Xel wei mend tekeing me vaxend nol eno lam wou e eivek xomek vambuing, me moxo wong xel wo nimzalek.
\v 15 Ekom xel lumuki leitata me putoung wei petieing lam yei lul nimza wei e wong o me yakyak wo vyend eivek xomek vambuing lalei, “Hosana ena wou Dawit Neu Moux,” om xel laleind wo nilul.
\p 
\v 16 Xel teling e, “Beip wang ngo vati wei xel yakyak ti beimambei ne di neil ne?”
\p Yesu neil elox. “E. Beip xam seng mi pyaw qayeeng,
\q1 “‘Eivek yakyak me yakyeis myend wang menyex wou bei
\q2 xel a mi sanghoxe wa leim’?” \rq Qapiya Lalo 8:2\rq*
\p 
\v 17 Om moxo la veil xel me la Yerusalem me la Betani, de moxo dei inyon boukeing tiyon.
\s1 Xax basunghek mupek
\p 
\v 18 Satiboukeing lul, eno Yesu di la wou sakwaing bei nox Yerusalem, ekom maxepya e.
\v 19 Moxo yei xax basunghek ti toukale wou sakwaing nenyawes, om la ingwei xax toukale ghei yo ekom se yei neing ti qe lis bandaing. Woyom moxo neil wou xax on, “Tyek wa seng nox buk neing no!” Se wo lululek en xax basunghek on mupek.
\p 
\v 20 Gyeik xel betiyeing yei tine, moxoyeiw etek mouyo. Xel teling, “Xax basunghek tine mupek daing ambei nya?”
\p 
\v 21 Yesu neil elox bei, “A neil wou xam zonghek, wangwei wa laleim se bo yuw en wa xe wongeingis nei, ond se nambei vati wei a wong wou xax basunghek ne venaxow, qe wa neil wou lukendu tine is ambei nyon, ‘La nex xow la eivek mamileeng,’ ond tyek bong ambei kawei wang neil o.
\v 22 Wangwei wang bongis nei, tyek wa qou vatiyeiw wei wang teling en o eivek zeimeing mema.”
\s1 Xel teling Yesu en e lei wei ngandoung o
\p 
\v 23 Yesu la eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing, ka moxo di teyoxe eno xel lumuki leitata me teivateiv wei xomaxoneing o lam wou e. Xel teling, “Wang di wong lulti beimambei ne nangya lei ngandoung wei eti yo? Me eti wong lei ngandoung tine wou wang?”
\p 
\v 24 Yesu neil elox bei, “Tyek a bong telinyeing ti wou xam is ambei nyon. Wangwei xam a neil enoum wou a bombek nei, on tyek a neil wou xam en lei ngandoung wei eti ingwei a di wong lulti beimambei ne nangya ne.
\v 25 Yoan xe lipekeing on lam anghei inya? Beip inyon lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei, o inyon lam wou xomaxoneing?”
\p Xel di luk en inye wouma me neil ambei nye, “Wangwei xey a neimbei, ‘Nanghei tyoung gheyapu nei,’ ond moxo tyek teling, ‘Woyom nambei nya xam seng wongis e?’
\v 26 Ek wangwei xey a neimbei, ‘Inyon lam wou xomaxoneing,’ ond xey a ghaleeng en xomaxoneing, en xel dalus woulek bei Yoan ne poropet ti.”
\p 
\v 27 Om xel neil e lox wou Yesu, “Xa loungen o.”
\p Woyom moxo neil, “Ay is ambei nyon tyek a se neil wou xam en lei ngandoung vati wei andi wong lulti beimambei ne en o.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei tambiy ti neu yuw o
\p 
\v 28 “Xam ghe wou naleimim ambei nya? Inyon tambiy ti neu moux yayuw. Moxo la wou neu nge wei tax o me neil, ‘Neung, la me wo xuk eivek xuk wain gweimbeeng.’
\p 
\v 29 “Moxo neil, ‘Tyek a se na.’ Dekalekom moxo lalei pekwi dom la.
\p 
\v 30 “Woyom ma la wou nge wei moun me neil ambei kawei yo no. Moxo lewexe, ‘Mang, tyek a na yo.’ Ekom moxo se la.
\p 
\v 31 “Eivek neu yuw on eno luw nge na wong ambei ingwei ma neil o?”
\p Xel lewexe, “Nge wei tax o.”
\p Yesu neil wou xel, “A neil wou xam zonghek, xel wei mi qou takis me vex wei kwapesiv o tyek na eivek tete lalei wei Anutu yo natax en xam.
\v 32 En Yoan lam wou xam bei talex sakwaing wei bombek ayang o wou xam, ekom xam seng wongis e, qe xel wei mi qou takis me xel vex wei kwapesiv o eno wongis. Me xam ghe wei inye, ekom xam seng pekwi xow me ghe wongis e.
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei yeingteyei xuk wain o
\p 
\v 33 “Xam a ni nenyamim wou qayeeng pakeing nge no, inyon tembuing ma ti ev e xe xuk wain. Moxo qo tete zeyi e vivekwou, me ev leiveeng wei qeing wain eivek o me ev xomek vaxading wei yeingteyei yo ti. Woyom moxo wong e xe xuk wain wou xel xukana valu dom la sakwaing anding.
\v 34 Bouk wei uleing wain neing o lam paviy, om moxo wong e xe xukxe la wou xel wei yeiteyei xuk wain bei na dul e xe neing valu.
\p 
\v 35 “Xel wei mi yeiteyei xuk wain eno zeimaxoun e xe xukxeyeiw, xel sesa ti, de leis nge mey, dom nex tiwei yal o en qakous.
\v 36 Woyom moxo wong xukxe valu lox me la wou xel no, xel la ngenong ka ghanaw nge tax veil, me xel wei mi yeiteyei xuk wain eno wong ambei kawei xel wong nge tax o wou xel.
\v 37 Ti yusayang eno moxo wong e maxow neu moux la wou xel. Moxo neil, ‘Tyek xel a ni nenyend wou a neung moux xe qayeeng.’
\p 
\v 38 “Ekom xel wei mi yeiteyei xuk wain eno yei e neu moux om xel neil wouma, ‘Tine inye xukma neu moux wei tyek na qou lulul dalus o. Xam lam, en xey a nyeis e mey de na qou e xe lulul dalus.’
\v 39 Om xel zeimaxoun e me nex e la myayaing veil xuk wain de leis e mey.
\p 
\v 40 “Nambei nyon om gyeik xuk wain ma nam, ond tyek moxo bong vati wou xel wei mi yeiteyei xuk wain on?”
\p 
\v 41 Xel neil elox bei, “Moxo tyek bo nol wou xel on bo nilul ayang me nyeis xel amey, de tyek moxo bong xuk wain on nox wou xel ba, eti yeiw wei teyei bei tyek bong xuk neing valu wou e gyeik bouk wei uleing neing o.”
\p 
\v 42 Yesu neil wou xel, “Xam seng mi pyaw vati wei yeip eivek qapiya vambuing yo:
\q1 “‘Qakous wei xel kamunda pesek,
\q2 eno wong ambei qakous ti myaxeeng me mi byexaxoun xomek o.
\q1 Inye Tambiy Ngandoung venaxow wong tine belup,
\q2 me wo nimza eivek xa mami’? \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:22-23\rq*
\p 
\v 43 “Nambei nyon a neil wou xam bei Anutu tyek na qou e xe tete lalei veil xam me bong wou xomaxoneing qendu ti wei tyek bong neing atyip o.
\v 44 De eti detei lek qakous nei tyek dembu me bo myapapu, ekom qakous embei detei lek tambiy ti eno tyek bo myasa bandaing.”
\p 
\v 45 Gyeik xel lumuki leitata me Parisi ngo Yesu xe qayeeng pakeing tine, xel woulek bei Yesu di neil inye lek xel.
\v 46 Om xel yimexe sakwaing wei xel embei zeimaxoun e yo, ekom xel di yaleeng en xel qendu ngandoung on en nambei xomaxoneing ngenong yei bei e yon poropet.
\c 22
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei mata ngandoung wei iingama yo
\p 
\v 1 Yesu luk is xel lu nge no eivek qayeeng pakeing, me neil embei,
\v 2 “Tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno nambei king ti wei menyex wou mata ngandoung wei iingama yo en neu moux.
\v 3 Moxo wong e xe xel xukxe la wou eti yeiw wei wong qayeeng la me neil wou xel bei xel nam en mata ngandoung wei iingama yo, ekom xel pesek bei se nam.
\p 
\v 4 “Woyom moxo wong xel xukxe valu no la me neil, ‘Neil wou xel wei a wong qayeeng la wou xel bei a menyex wou a xe yaeing woy, “Wei, a xe manghaxo me leliy wei ling tata yo eno xel leis me ghuw, me lul sapa a menyex wou woy. Xam lam en mata ngandoung wei iingama ne.” ’
\p 
\v 5 “Ekom xel se di li nenyend wou qayeeng qe xel la. Ti la e xe xuk, de nge la emaxow xe xuk malew.
\v 6 De xel ba zeimaxoun e xe xel xukxe me wo nol wou xel de leis xel mey.
\v 7 King moxo lalei wo vanei mouyo. Om wong e xe xel vevekyeiw la me semaleeng xel tiwei leis xel xukxe mey yo me nyuw beyeeng ngandoung wei xel on is.
\p 
\v 8 “Woyom neil wou e xe xel xukxe bei, ‘A menyex wou mata ngandoung wei iingama eno woy, ekom xel wei a wong qayeeng la bei xel nam eno xel on se nimza teyei bei nam.
\v 9 Om xam ghe na sakwaingta dalus me eti yeiw wei xam ghe gweiwou eno xam a qou me ghe nam eivek mata ngandoung wei iingama ne.’
\v 10 Om xel xukxe la eivek sakwaingta dalus nei me qekuwou xomaxoneing dalus wei xel yeiwou yo, xel nimza me nilul is, om xomek lalei wei mata ngandoung wei iingama yon puplek en xel.
\p 
\v 11 “Ekom gyeik king lam lalei me yei xel on, moxo woulek bei tambiy ti toundei inyon eno se byex teimb wei iingama yo.
\v 12 Moxo teling, ‘Gweleeng, wang lam eivek xomek ne lalei nambei nya, ekom wang seng byex teimb wei iingama yo?’ Ekom tambiy on se wo lukluk.
\p 
\v 13 “Woyom king neil wou e xe xel xukxe, ‘Xam tup e mema vaxa, dom nex e la myayaing nei eivek mapetok ngandoung nanghei inyon eno xel mi eng me mi nga newound mi wo nyiknyik.’
\p 
\v 14 “En nambei Anutu taxe xel ngenong, ekom beyal xel nuyuw ka.”
\s1 Toungeing takis wou Sisa
\p 
\v 15 Woyom xel Parisi la myayaing me yimexe sakwaing wei xel embei pakei qayeeng lek e en e maxow xe lukeing o.
\v 16 Xel wong xel xe betiyeing la wou e is xel wei Herot o. Xel neil, “Putoung, xa woulek bei wang on moux wei wang mi neil zonghek o me inyon wang mi teyoxe sakwaing wei Anutu xe lalei nimza is zonghek o. Wa seng mi waleeng en xelti, en nambei wa seng mi li nenyam wou xelti xe qayeeng.
\v 17 Woyom neil wou xa, wang wou naleim ambei nya? Beip inye teyeimbei xey a toung takis wou Sisa o xe se toung?”
\p 
\v 18 Ekom Yesu woulek xel xe woueing nalei nilul on, om neil, “Xam wei myamim yuw o, nambei nya xam ghe di wong en xam ambei bong axeing wou ay?
\v 19 Xam talex malew selewa wei xel mi toung takis eno ti me a xei.” Xel qou malew selewa ti me talex wou e,
\v 20 om Yesu teling xel, “Eti xe tenu tine? Me eti lei tine?”
\p 
\v 21 Xel neil elox bei, “Sisa.”
\p Woyom moxo neil wou xel bei, “Xam ghe bong vati wei Sisa xe yo ena wou Sisa, de vati wei Anutu xe yo ena wou Anutu.”
\p 
\v 22 Xel ngo tine eno xel etek mouyo. Om xel la veil e me la.
\s1 Iingama lek bouk loxyus wei qandieing lek o
\p 
\v 23 Lek bouk kayon Sadyusiyeiw wei mi neil embei xel meyeing tyek se qandi lek, eno lam wou e is telinyeing ti.
\v 24 Xel neil, “Putoung, Mose neil wou xa bei wangwei moux ti e mey de neu ema, ond e li moux e dii vexeiv on me bo li neuyeiw en e lei e se ma.
\v 25 Woyom inyon xel lim yuw lindama toundei eivek xa senghoing. Xel lind ti tax o ii vex on me mey, de moxo se wong yak ti, om li nge wei nexlek eno ii li venei vexeiv on.
\v 26 Sakwaing kayon eno li nge wei yuw me nge yal, me ela tei lek tiwei lim yuw eno teyeima.
\v 27 De loxyus eno vex on mey.
\v 28 Woyom lek bouk wei qandieing lek eno eivek xel lim yuw on eti venei? En inyon nambei xel xouing ii vex tiyon.”
\p 
\v 29 Yesu neil elox, “Xam ghe neil esewok en inyon xam seng mi pyaw qayeeng wei di yeip eivek qapiya vambuing o me xam seng woulek Anutu xe nikanzek.
\v 30 Gyeik bouk wei qandieing lek veil meyeing eno xomaxoneing tyek se diima o diima nox me noum. Tyek xel ghok ambei angelayeiw wei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 31 Ekom qayeeng tiwei qandieing lek veil meyeing, eno beind xam seng pyaw vati wei Anutu neil wou xam bei,
\v 32 ‘A ne Anutu wei Apraham xe yo, Anutu wei Isaka xe yo me Anutu wei Yakop xe yo.’ \rq Qouloum 3:6\rq*
\m Moxo se Anutu wei meyeing o, qe Anutu wei mapieing o.”
\p 
\v 33 Xel xomaxoneing qendu tiyon ngo tine, xel etek en e xe teyoxeing.
\s1 Petieing ngandoung wei ghanaw veil o
\p 
\v 34 Xel Parisi ngo bei Yesu qateiv xel Sadyusi xe lukeing, om xel Parisiyeiw toung lekti.
\v 35 Eivek xel senghoing eno tambiy ti, wei wo lupeyei en petieing, eno wo axeing wou Yesu en telinyeing tine,
\p 
\v 36 “Putoung, qayeeng petieing tina inye ngandoung ghanaw veil eivek petieing?”
\v 37 Yesu neil elox, “‘Xam laleimim devind Tambiy Ngandoung xam xe Anutu is xam laleimim dalus me is xam numim dalus me is xam lumimpeyei dalus.’ Petieing 6:5
\v 38 Tine inye qayeeng petieing tiwei tax o me ngandoung ghanaw veil.
\v 39 De nge yuw wei teyei lek eno nambei nye, ‘Wa laleim devind nimpapu nge nambei wa laleim mi vind xow o.’ Lumuki 19:18
\v 40 Petieing dalus me qayeeng poropet dalus eno milek qayeeng petieing yuw ne.”
\s1 Eti neu ingwei Kilisi ne
\p 
\v 41 Ka xel Parisi di qekuma eno Yesu teling xel,
\v 42 “Xam ghe wou naleimim ambei nya en Kilisi? Eti neu e?”
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Dawit neu moux o.”
\p 
\v 43 Moxo neil wou xel, “Woyom nambei nya Laweeng Vambuing wong kwa wou Dawit me moxo taxe e ‘Tambiy Ngandoung’? En moxo neil ambei nye,
\q1 
\v 44 “‘Tambiy Ngandoung neil wou a xe Tambiy Ngandoung,
\q2 “Dei wou a memang payeiv deka
\q1 a toung wa xe xel vevek eivek
\q2 wa vaxam xeinghembi le.”’ \rq Qapiya Lalo 110:1\rq*
\m 
\v 45 Woyom wangwei Dawit a mi taxe e bei ‘Tambiy ngandoung,’ on nambei nya ekom e yon Dawit neu moux?”
\v 46 Xelti se teyei bei neil qayeeng nge nox wou e, de lek bouk kayon me ela eno xelti se mi teling e no en lulti.
\c 23
\s1 Yesu peti xel gyovaxa wei lalo yo
\p 
\v 1 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel qendu ngandoung on is e xe xel betiyeing,
\v 2 “Xel putoung wei petieing me xel Parisi eno mindei lek Mose xe sia.
\v 3 Om xam a mi betiwou xel me ghe bong lul dalus wei xel neil wou xam o. Ekom xam seng bong vati wei xel wong o, en nambei xel se mi wong e teyei lek vati wei xel mi teyoxe yo.
\v 4 Xel tup nimaying ngandoung me toung lek xel xomaxoneing on ghandiwek, ekom xel venaxow se teyei bei zeim lek angya memend deyis bei bong ena veil.
\p 
\v 5 “Lul sapa wei xel mi wong en embei xel xomaxoneing gyei, me lek xel dambend me memend eno xel mi tup deneing wei xoulek o lek me e wo myasapa, me mi tup yis ding lek xel xe teimb ding myasepu.
\v 6 Xel laleind mi vind bei na mi mendei mya eivek bouk wei mata ngandoung o me eivek xomek qekueing ama lalei.
\v 7 Xel laleind mi vind bei moux alis vex a mi neil bendiyeing wou xel eivek beyeeng vateivek me na mi taxe e bei ‘Putoung.’
\p 
\v 8 “Ekom xam eno xel se taxe xam ‘Putoung,’ en xam xe putoung tixemou tateis me xam dalus on limim ama.
\v 9 De xam se taxe xelti lek tembuing bei ‘mang,’ en xam Mamim tixemou, me e toundei eivek tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 10 O xel ti se taxe xam ‘putoung,’ en xam xe putoung tixemou, inyon Kilisi.
\v 11 Xam xe teiv eivek xam senghoing eno e mi mendei nambei xam xe xukxe.
\v 12 En wangwei eti yeiw embei sanghoxe xow on tyek e lei detei eivek, de eti embei beoux xow on tyek e lei zekna.
\p 
\v 13 “Xam putoung wei petieing me xam Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam on ghe mi toung xomek mya wei tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu nei yo zeyi moux alis vex mend. Xam venaxow seng la eivek, me xam ghe mi nale zeyi xel wei di wong me yei en embei na eivek o.
\v 14 [Xam putoung wei petieing me xam Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o, en xam ghe mi wo nol wou xel vexeiv bend, me xam ghe mi tyoing lek me ghe mi zeimemam ding, nambei nyon tyek xam a qou myaveweeng ngandoung.]
\p 
\v 15 “Xam putoung wei petieing me xam Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam ghe mi ghavineeng lek tembuing me mamileeng being bong tambiy tixemou bo betiyeing wei xam o, me gyeik e wong ambei betiyeing ti, eno xam ghe mi wong moux on la eivek nilul ngandoung eno ghanaw veil eivek nenyex wei luta yo nambei xam venaxow.
\p 
\v 16 “Xam wei matekeing ambei talex sakwaing wou xomaxoneing bamba eno xam ghe gwaleeng amim. Xam ghe mi neimbei, ‘Wangwei tambiy ti na neil zonghek is inyapunei lek xomek vambuing, ond inyon se byexaxoun qayeeng. Ekom wangwei e neil zonghek is inyapunei lek ghol wei xomek vambuing o, ond inyon byexaxoun qayeeng.’
\v 17 Xam on bandol me mamim tekeing! Tina inye ngandoung, ghol o xomek vambuing wei wong ghol wo vambuing o?
\v 18 Xam ghe mi neil is ambei nyon bei, ‘Wangwei xelti e neil zonghek lek qeind is inyapunei ond inyon se byexaxoun qayeeng, ekom wangwei xelti neil zonghek is inyapunei lei lek xound wei toundei lek qeind, ond inyon byexaxoun qayeeng.’
\v 19 Xam moux wei mamim tekeing o. Tina inye ngandoung, xound o qeind wei wong xound on wo vambuing o?
\v 20 Nambei inyon, tambiy tiwei neil zonghek is inyapunei lei lek qeind on neil zonghek is inyapunei lei lek lulul dalus wei toundei lek o.
\v 21 Me tiwei mi neil zonghek is inyapunei lei lek xomek vambuing eno neil lek tiwei mindei eivek o.
\v 22 Me eti neil zonghek is inyapunei lei lek tyoung gheyapu eno neil lek Anutu xe siaking me tiwei mindei lek o.
\p 
\v 23 “Xam putoung wei petieing me Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam ghe wong ti eivek xoumeeng wei lul senyeing wei xuk lalei. Ekom xam ghe saing qayeeng ngandoung dalus wei petieing o veil, nambei qayeeng bombek, lalei pyaweing me wongeingis. Xam betiwou qayeeng ngandoung wei petieing ne yo dom xam naleimim se ma petieing bamba.
\v 24 Xam wei mamim tekeing wei ghe mi talex sakwaing! Xam ghe mi tiy mamayek veil xam xe louk, ekom xam ghe lep kamel.
\p 
\v 25 “Xam putoung wei petieing me Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam ghe mi sekweyexe mayamya me dipek demi, ekom eivek lalei eno pup en kwa eivekeing me ghe mi wou kwamim ngenong en lulul leimalei.
\v 26 Xam Parisiyeiw wei mamim tekeing o! Myaxeeng eno xam sekweyexe mayamya me dipek lalei bole, dekakom demi embo vako is.
\p 
\v 27 “Xam putoung wei petieing me Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam on nambei leiveeng meyeing wei xel pelei pen teleing lek o, wei wo nimza maseim lek demi yo, ekom lalei yon pup en xel meyeing kanzek me lul dalus wei nilaxes o.
\v 28 Xam is ambei nyon eivek sakwaing kayon, eno xel mi yei xam lek demi om xel embeik nge xam on bombek, ekom xam laleimim on pup en kwa wei tyonyeing me kwa wei pyaweing lek qayeeng o.
\p 
\v 29 “Xam putoung wei petieing me Parisiyeiw, xam ghe gwaleeng amim, xam wei myamim yuw o! Xam ghe ev leiveeng meyeing en xel poropetyeiw me ghe vunekwou leiveeng wei xel bombek o.
\v 30 Me xam ghe neil, ‘Wangwei xa mendei eivek bouk wei xa bumiyeiw, tyek xa se teyei bei devind xel me na nyeis xel poropet a mey.’
\v 31 Om xam venaxow ghe talex lek xow bei xam on neumambu wei xel wei leis poropetyeiw mey o.
\v 32 Woyom xam la wong sewokeing teyei lek ingwei bumyeiw mi wong o.
\p 
\v 33 “Xam on myeiy me myeiy nilul neuyeiw xam! Tyek xam a pek veil myaveweeng wei nenyex luta yon nambei nya?
\v 34 Nambei nyon tyek a bong xel poropetyeiw me xel wei lundpeyei nimza me xel putoung wei petieing o nak wou xam. Xel valu tyek xam ghe nyeis xel a mey dom na tuw valu lek xax pepeeng, de xel valu tyek xam ghe bo nol wou xel eivek xomek qekueing ama me na tiy xel na beyeeng nge me na nge.
\v 35 Om nambei nyon, xel dalus bombek gyand wei xel leis xel mey lek tembuing eno tyek mendei lek xam, qandi eivek Abel wei bombek o tax me e na Belekia neu moux Sakalias, tiwei xam ghe leis e mey eivek xomek vambuing me qeind senghoing o.
\v 36 A neil wou xam zonghek, lul nimaying dalus tine tyek nam lek xam qendu ti gweimbeeng ne dalus.
\p 
\v 37 “O Yerusalem, Yerusalem, xam eti yeiw wei ghe mi leis xel poropetyeiw me ghe nex xel wei lak wou xam en qakous. Taxombouk eno ambei mi qeku xam neumimyeiw lekti, nambei qouklex mi qekuwou neuyeiw eivek banis xeinghembi yo, ekom xam laleimim se vind.
\v 38 Wei, xam xe xomek tyek lelolexe me mendei bandaing.
\v 39 En a neil wou xam bei, tyek xam seng nox gwei a no qe ka xam a neimbei, ‘Mata ena wou e tiwei lam eivek Tambiy Ngandoung lei yo.’ ” \rq Qapiya Lalo 118:26\rq*
\c 24
\s1 Dee wei bouk loxyus e na tip lek o
\p 
\v 1 Yesu la veil xomek vambuing on me la eno e xe xel betiyeing la wou e. En xel embei talex xomek nimzamza wei toungale is xomek vambuing o wou e.
\v 2 Moxo neil, “Xam ghe wei lulti beimambei ne? A neil wou xam zonghek bei, tyek xel se teyei bei bong qakous nge mendei lek nge, qe tyek xel banex dalus deteina.”
\p 
\v 3 Ka Yesu toundei lek lukendu Oliv, xel betiyeing venaxow lam wou e me teling. “Neil wou xa, gyeik inya tyek tine belup, me dee vati tyek nam a tax en ingwei wa being nam o me ingwei bouk na tip lek o?”
\p 
\v 4 Yesu lewexe, “Xam ghe gweiteyei xow en kandek xelti se nam a tyoxe xam.
\v 5 En tyek xel ngenong nam lek a leing, me na neimbei, ‘A Kilisi yo,’ me na tyoxe xomaxoneing ngenong.
\v 6 Tyek xam a ngo vevek me qayeeng laweeng wei vevek o, ekom xam seng gwaleeng. Lulti beimambei ne tyek neing atyip, ekom bouk loxyus eno se ghei lam.
\v 7 Tembuing nge tyek qandi me bo vevek is tembuing nge, me tete lalei nge tyek bo vevek is tete lalei nge. Inyon tyek maxep ngandoung me tyek tembuing api nanghei beyeeng danghei danghei nei.
\v 8 Lul dalus ne inye myavanei nambei myaxeeng wei yak mi umbek o.
\p 
\v 9 “Woyom tyek xel a zeimaxoun xam me bo nol wou xam de nyeis xam amey, me tembuing sapa tyek laleind bo nol wou xam en ay.
\v 10 Lek bouk kayon xel ngenong tyek na toung demind wou xel xe wongeingis de tyek xel a dax ama vun me laleind bo nol wou ma,
\v 11 me poropet tyonyeing ngenong tyek nam a tyip me na tyoxe xomaxoneing ngenong.
\v 12 En kwa nilul on tyek bo ngandoung, de xel ngenong tyek na saing kwa wei lalei vineing o,
\v 13 ekom eti yeiw wei nale nikanzek me ena bouk loxyus eno tyek Anutu devind xel veil meyeing.
\v 14 De Xoulek Nimza tine en tete lalei eno tyek xel a neil e na eivek tembuing dalus en tembuing sapa na ngo, de woyom bouk loxyus eno tyek nam.
\p 
\v 15 “Deka xam ghe gwei lul nilul ayang, wei mi wo nol wou lulul eno bale eivek beyeeng vambuing on nambei poropet Daniel neil en o.” Daniel 9:27 (Yon xam wei ghe mi pyaw qayeeng ne eno xam woulek e wo nimza.)
\v 16 “Woyom eti yeiw wei mindei eivek Yudia eno xel a pek me na lek lukendu.
\v 17 De wangwei tambiy ti toumendei lek xomek demi qetyei eno tyek se detei nox a qou lul valu eivek beeng lalei.
\v 18 De tambiy ti toumendei eivek xuk eno se teyei bei nox me na qou e xe teimb ding nge.
\v 19 Inyon tyek bo nilul ayang lek bouk tiyon en xel vex wei xeipouyek o me tayeiw wei di wo luul wou neu yo!
\v 20 Xam a zeimemamim enok bouk wei pekeing eno qandi lek bouk wei nityuweing o lek bouk wei Sabat o.
\v 21 En lek bouk tiyon nimaying ngandoung tyek nam. Myaxeeng wei tembuing qandi vako yo me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne, eno nimaying ambei nyon se lam tulek xomaxoneing, de loxyus eno nimaying ambei nye tyek se nox atyip no.
\v 22 Wangwei Anutu se qateiv bouk tiyon bo sepi, yond tyek qetya xomaxoneing on veil, ekom wounalei en moux alis vex wei beyal om qateiv bouk wo sepi.
\v 23 Lek bouk kayon eno wangwei xelti na neil wou wang bei, ‘Wei, Kilisi inye!’ o, ‘Moxo inyei!’ ond wang seng bongis qayeeng on.
\v 24 En xomaxoneing tyonyeing valu tyek na neimbei a Kilisi o a poropet ti. Me tyek xel nam a tyip me bong dee me lulvako, wangwei xel teyei nei on tyek xel a tyoxe xomaxoneing wei Anutu beyal o.
\v 25 Wei, a neil wou xam a tax en lul dalus tine wei tyek nam atyip o.
\p 
\v 26 “Om wangwei xelti e neil wou xam, ‘Wei, moxo toundei eivek tembuing bandaing nei,’ yon xam seng na inyei, o ‘Moxo inye, toundei eivek xomek lalei nei,’ ond xam seng bongis.
\v 27 En nambei kawei zivip mi nex mema lam anghei ninei is xeiyaing me byex la lek tembuing tambak nei me la xeinei, om tyek bong ambei nyon lek bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum o.
\v 28 Lek beyeeng wei meyeing mi yeip lek o, inyon xel tuw mi qeku lak inyon.
\p 
\v 29 “Ka nimaying sapa tine na ma veil le, woyom lutika eno
\q1 “‘sayeiv tyek bo mapetok,
\q2 de dentouk tyek se teyeimbei tel, me
\q1 betum tyek detei nanghei tyoung nei,
\q2 de tyoung dalus tyek bo pimapi.’ \rq Yesaya 13:10; 34:4\rq*
\p 
\v 30 “Lek bouk kayon dee wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek nam mendei yaingateiv eivek tyoung, me xel veleivlei dalus wei tembuing eno tyek deeng. De tyek xel gyei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux mendi nam lek laxap, is nikanzek me xeiyaing ngandoung.
\v 31 Me moxo tyek bong e xe angelayeiw na is vukxax wei wo vya xoulekeing, me tyek xel qekuwou e xe xomaxoneing wei beyal o eivek tembuing sapa me ena tembuing myasepu dalus.
\p 
\v 32 “Woyom xam a qou kwa wou xax basunghek. Gyeik xam ghe gwei bei xax mema wo nilouk me lis vako byex lek, xam ghe boulek bei bouk wei seiv embei siing eno lam paviy.
\v 33 Nambei nyon om gyeik xam ghe gwei lul dalus ti beimambei ne, xam ghe boulek bei Xomaxoneing Neu lam paviy me toungale wou qapomb.
\v 34 A neil wou xam zonghek bei, xel moux alis vex ti gweimbeeng ne tyek se mey qe ka lulti beimambei ne neing atyip le.
\v 35 Tyoung gheyapu me tembuing tyek nati, ekom a xe qayeeng tyek se teyei bei nati.
\s1 Bouk me seivma wei xelti se woulek
\p 
\v 36 “Xelti se woulek bouk o seivma wei Kilisi embei noum o, xel angela eivek tyoung gheyapu, o Neu moux se woulek, qe Ma venaxow.
\v 37 Nambei ingwei eivek bouk wei Noaka yo, om tyek xel bong ambei kayon eivek bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum o.
\v 38 Myaxeeng lek bouk wei memiing se ghei butek o, xomaxoneing mi ya me num, me iima, me iima lox me loum, me la tyip wou bouk wei Noaka la eivek sip o.
\v 39 Xel se woulek vati wei embei belup wou xel o dekakom memiing butek me qou xel dalus me la. Kwa kayon eno tyek bong ambei nyon lek bouk wei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux noum o.
\v 40 Moux yayuw toundei eivek xuk yaeing eno tyek Anutu na qou nge na veil de nge na toumendei.
\v 41 Vex yayuw tyek mendi zouk wit, de tyek Anutu na qou nge de nge na toumendei.
\p 
\v 42 “Nambei nyon xam ghe gweiteyei xow, en nambei xam seng woulek bouk vati wei xam xe Tambiy Ngandoung tyek nam o.
\v 43 Ekom xam ghe bou naleimim bei, wangwei xomek ma boulek seivma vati wei xel panaxeing embei nam o, moxo tyek mendei bin e xe xomek en kandek xelti se dembu me na eivek.
\v 44 Om xam is ambei nyon xam ghe gweiwou xow, en Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek nam lek seivma wei xam seng woulek bei tyek nam o.
\p 
\v 45 “Woyom xukxe eti ingwei lupeyei nimza wei mi yeiteyei e xe xuk wo nimza nei? Wei e xe teiv toung e yeiteyei xel xukxe eivek e beeng bei e mi bong yaeing wou xel lek bouk wei teiv beyal o bombek?
\v 46 Inyon nimza wou xukxe tiyon wei e xe teiv yei bei moxo mi wong xuk on gyeik e loum o.
\v 47 A neil wou xam zonghek bei, teiv tyek na toung embo lei ngandoung en lul dalus eivek e beeng.
\v 48 Ekom wangwei xukxe tiyon tambiy nilul ti om mi neil wou xow, ‘A xe teiv la toundei dingta takwei nei,’
\v 49 woyom moxo la me leis e xe xel wei xel xouing mi wo xuk lekti yo, de mi ya me num is xel wei mi num me wo nol o.
\v 50 Teiv wei xukxe tiyon tyek noum lek bouk wei xukxe se woulek me seivma wei se woulek o.
\v 51 Teiv tyek bo myaveweeng ngandoung wou e me na toung e na is xel wei myend yuw o, nanghei inyon eno tyek xel deeng me xel newound bo nyiknyik.
\c 25
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei vexawo xoumeeng wei paleveeng o
\p 
\v 1 “Lek bouk kayon eno tete lalei wei tyoung gheyapu eno tyek ghok ambei vexawo xoumeeng wei paleveeng eno qou xel xe lam me la bei na daxe moux wei embei dii vex o.
\v 2 Xel lim eno loungeing de xel lim eno lundpeyei nimza.
\v 3 Xel lim wei loungeing eno qou xel xe lam ekom xel se qou wel ti is.
\v 4 De xel wei lundpeyei nimza eno xel qou wel eivek qakous botol is xel xe lam.
\v 5 Tambiy wei embei dii vex eno se lam daing, om xel xouing mend yeip om xel yeip.
\p 
\v 6 “Lek boukeing masenghoing eno xel ngo taxeing ti lam, ‘Wei, inye tambiy wei embei dii vex eno lam! Xam lam myayaing me la pelong e!’
\p 
\v 7 “Woyom xel vexawo paleveeng tiyon dalus qandi lek me yeiwou xel xe lam.
\v 8 Xel wei loungeing eno neil wou xel wei lundpeyei nimza yo, ‘Xam wong xam xe wel valu wou xa, en xa xe lam embei mey.’
\p 
\v 9 “Xel neil elox bei, ‘Ma, wel ne se teyei xam me xa is. Embong ondek xam ghe na wou eti yeiw wei mi wo vateivek lek wel o, me ghe na bou valu wou venaxow.’
\p 
\v 10 “Om ka vex lim on tupwou sakwaing bei na bou wel, tambiy wei embei dii vex eno lam tyip. Vexawo paleveeng wei yeiwou xow eno la lalei is e me la mata ngandoung wei iingama yo. Dom qepei qapomb lox zeyi.
\p 
\v 11 “Kalekom vexawo lim wei loungeing on lam is ambei nyon me neil, ‘Teiv! Teiv! Tax qapomb veil xa!’
\p 
\v 12 “Ekom moxo neil elox bei, ‘A neil zonghek wou xam bei a loung en xam.’
\p 
\v 13 “Nambei nyon om xam ghe gweiteyei xow, en xam seng woulek bouk o seivma vati wei embei noum o.”
\s1 Qayeeng pakeing wei xel xukxe qou malew o
\p 
\v 14 Yesu neil no, “Anutu xe tete lalei inye nambei tambiy ti embei na sakwaing anding, om moxo taxe e xe xel xukxe me toung lul dalus eivek xel memend bei xel a mi gyeiteyei.
\v 15 Moxo wong malew 5,000 wou ti, de malew 2,000 wou nge de malew 1,000 wou nge teyei lek nikanzek wei xel titi yo. De woyom moxo la sakwaing anding.
\v 16 Tambiy tiwei qou 5,000 eno la me wong xuk daing me qou malew valu is no teyei lek malew 5,000.
\v 17 Om nambei nyon is, nge wei qou malew 2,000 eno wo xuk me qou 2,000 lek mapu.
\v 18 Ekom tambiy tiwei qou malew 1,000 eno qou inyon dom la, de ev leiveeng eivek tembuing me vun e xe teiv xe malew eivek.
\p 
\v 19 “Ka xel xe teiv la dei enden woy, om moxo loum wou xel xukxe om embei menyex wou malew wei toung is xel o.
\v 20 Moux tiwei qou malew 5,000 eno qou 5,000 nge is me lam. Moxo neil, ‘Teiv, wang wong 5,000 wou ay. Wei, a qou malew 5,000 lek mapu is.’
\p 
\v 21 “E xe teiv neil elox bei, ‘Nimzayang, wa xukxe nimza me wang mi wo xuk wo nimza! Wang mi weiteyei xuk wo nimza is lul nayaka. Om tyek a toung wang gweiteyei lul ngenong. Lam me wo xeimlala is wa xe teiv!’
\p 
\v 22 “Moux wei qou malew 2,000 eno lam is ambei nyon. Moxo neil, ‘Teiv, wang wong malew 2,000 wou ay. Wei, a wo xuk me na qou 2,000 is no.’
\p 
\v 23 “E xe teiv neil elox, ‘Nimzayang, wa xukxe nimza me wang wo xuk wo nimza! Wang mi weiteyei xuk wo nimza is lul nayaka. Om tyek a toung wang gweiteyei lul ngenong. Lam me wo xeimlala is wa xe teiv!’
\p 
\v 24 “Woyom tambiy wei qou malew 1,000 eno lam. Moxo neil, ‘Teiv, a woulek woy bei wang on tambiy wei nimseikeing o, wang mi qou neing eivek xuk wei se wa memam xuk o, me ghe mi qekuwou vei wei wa seng vuw o.
\v 25 Om a xaleeng me na la vun wa xe malew eivek tembuing. Wei, Inye vati wei wa xe yo.’
\p 
\v 26 “E xe teiv neil elox bei, ‘Wa xukxe nilul wei qabonghapus o! Om wang woulek inyon bei a mi qou neing wei se a memang xuk o me na qekuwou vei wei a se vuw o?
\v 27 Inyon nimza, wang teyei bei toung a xe malew eivek xomek wei malew o, en kandek gyeik ingwei ambei noum ond a na qou is ingwei xel toung valu lek mapu is o.
\p 
\v 28 “‘Xam qou malew on veil e me wong e la wou tambiy wei qou malew 10,000 o.
\v 29 En xel dalus wei qou lul valu woy eno tyek na qou valu lek mapu, en e qou lulul ngenong. Ek wangwei xelti xe lul nayaka ond tyek na zeim lul nayak kayon veil e.
\v 30 Dom banex xukxe nilul on na myayaing eivek mapetok ngandoung. Nanghei inyon eno tyek na deeng de zanga newou bo nyiknyik.’
\s1 Sipsip de meme
\p 
\v 31 “Gyeik ingwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux embei noum eivek e xe xeiyaing ngandoung, me xel angela dalus is e, eno tyek moxo mendei lek e xe siaking eivek xeiyaing ngandoung wei tyoung gheyapu nei.
\v 32 Xel xomaxoneing dalus lek tembuing sapa tyek qeku nam wou e manghalus, de moxo tyek na pum xomaxoneing na yuw nambei gyovaxa mi pum sipsip veil xel meme yo.
\v 33 Moxo tyek na toung sipsip na wou mema payeiv de xel meme na wou mema qeinz.
\p 
\v 34 “Woyom king tyek na neil wou xel wei dei wou e mema payeiv o, ‘Xam tiwei Mang wong mata wou xam eno xam lam, xam a qou xam xe lul dalus eivek tete lalei wei menyex wou woy wou xam gyeik ingwei toung tembuing o.
\v 35 En maxepya ay eno xam ghe wong yaeing valu me a xa. A kwang tip en memiing eno xam ghe wong me a num. A ne nambei xel amba ekom xam ghe qou ay me la eivek xomek lalei.
\v 36 Teimb ma veil ay ekom xam ghe byex teimb lek ay. Vanei wong ay ekom xam ghe weiteyei ay. A la eivek xeitueing ekom xam ghe lam wei ay.’
\p 
\v 37 “Woyom xel wei bombek eno tyek na neil e nox wou e, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, gyeik inya xa xei maxepya wang me na vet wang, o wa kwam tip me xa wong numeing wou wang me wang num?
\v 38 Gyeik inya xa xei wang on nambei xel amba om xa qou wang lam, o teimb ma veil wang om xa vunekwou wang?
\v 39 Gyeik inya xa xei wang wo vanei o wang la eivek xeitueing me xa lak a xei wang?’
\p 
\v 40 “King tyek na neil enoum, ‘A neil wou xam zonghek, vati wei xam ghe wong wou a lingyeiw ti beimambei ne ti wei lei maeing o, ond inyon xam ghe wong wou ay.’
\p 
\v 41 “Woyom moxo tyek na neil wou xel wei dei wou e mema qeinz o, ‘Xam la veil ay, xam eti yeiw wei ghe dei eivek myaveweeng o, xam la eivek nenyex wei se mi mey yo wei xel menyexwou tambiy mapetok me e xe angelayeiw o.
\v 42 En maxepya ay ekom xam seng wo lulti wou ay bei angha. A kwang tip, ekom xam seng wong lulti me a num.
\v 43 A lam ambei xel amba, ekom xam seng qou a la eivek xomek. A teimb ma ekom xam seng byex teimb ti lek ay. Vanei wong ay me a la eivek xomek xeitueing ekom xam seng weiteyei ay.’
\p 
\v 44 “Tyek xel a neil enox bei, ‘Tambiy Ngandoung, gyeik inya xa xei maxepya wang o wa kwam tip o wang lam ambei xel amba o teimb ma o vanei wong wang o wang toundei eivek xeitueing ekom xa se vind wang?’
\p 
\v 45 “Moxo tyek na neil enox bei, ‘A neil wou xam zonghek, vati wei xam seng wong wou tiwei lei maeing en lulti beimambei ne, ond xam seng wong wou ay.’
\p 
\v 46 “Woyom tyek xel na qou myaveweeng wei luta yo, dom xel wei bombek eno tyek na qou mapieing luta luta.”
\c 26
\s1 Xel yimexe sakwaing wei embei nyeis Yesu yo
\p 
\v 1 Ka Yesu neil qayeeng ti beimambei yon ma woy, moxo neil wou e xe xel betiyeing bei,
\v 2 “Xam ghe woulek woy bei, bouk yayuw xemou nanghei di yeip zeyi Pasova, ingwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek xel bong ena wou xel en xel a tuw e lek xax pepeeng o.”
\p 
\v 3 Woyom xel lumuki leitata me xel teivateiv wei xel xomaxoneing qekuma eivek xomek wei lumuki lukanzek, wei lei Kaiapas o,
\v 4 me xel di luk me yimexe sakwaing wei xel embei tyoxe me na zeimaxoun Yesu me nyeis e mey o.
\v 5 Xel neil ambei nye, “Ekom se lek bouk wei mata ngandoung o, enok xel xomaxoneing on baluk ngenong de nyeis ama.”
\s1 Vex ti taw wel lek Yesu lu nanghei Betani
\p 
\v 6 Ka Yesu la Betani me la toundei eivek xomek wei tambiy ti lei Simon, wei takwei eno qou vanei lepa,
\v 7 de vex ti lam wou e is botol qakous wei wel xeimangou wei malew ngandoung o, de vex on taw wel lek e lu gyeik moxo di yeip pepenyeing lek zek o.
\p 
\v 8 Ekom xel betiyeing yei tine, eno xel laleind wou nilul, me neil, “Nambei nya vex ne wo nol wou wel ne?
\v 9 Wel tine teyei bei xey a bo vateivek lek me na qou malew ngandoung me na bong wou xel kanyoyeiw o.”
\p 
\v 10 Yesu woulek inye woy, om neil wou xel, “Nambei nya xam ghe wong nimaying wou vex ne? Vexo wong lul nimza tine wou ay.
\v 11 Xel kanyoyeiw eno tyek na mi mendei is xam taxombouk, dom ay tyek a se mendei is xam taxombouk.
\v 12 Vex ne taw wel lek aneing, om vexo wong inye bei menyex wou a neing en eveing eivek leiveeng meyeing.
\v 13 A neil wou xam zonghek, eivek tembuing sapa wei xel embei na neil Xoulek Nimza nei eno tyek xel a mi neil vati wei vex ne wong ne, me tyek xel a mi bou naleind en e.”
\s1 Yudas tup qayeeng is xel lumuki lei tata bei na neil Yesu teyei
\p 
\v 14 Woyom xel xoumeeng yuw on ti lei Yudas Iskariot la wou xel lumuki leitata
\v 15 me teling, “Xam ambei tyek ghe bong vati wou ay wangwei am bong e nak wou xam nei?” Om xel pyaw memend wou malew teyei lek silva xoumeeng yal (30) wou e.
\v 16 Woyom nanghei inyon me ela eno Yudas di yimexe sakwaing wei embei bong Yesu na eivek xel memend o.
\s1 Yesu xe mata
\p 
\v 17 Lek bouk atax wei Bouk Wei Yaeing Belet Wei Yis Ma Veil o, xel betiyeing lam wou Yesu me teling, “Wambei xa na menyex wou yaeing anghei inya en kandek wang gwa Pasova?”
\p 
\v 18 Moxo neil elox, “La eivek beyeeng ngandoung on me ghe na wou tambiy tinei me na neil wou e, ‘Putoung neil embei: A xe bouk wei xel beyal eno paviy. Ay is a xe xel betiyeing bei nak angha Pasova eivek wa bam.’ ”
\v 19 Om xel betiyeing wong ambei kawei Yesu neil wou xel o me menyex wou Pasova.
\p 
\v 20 Gyeik ingwei di souk, eno Yesu la dei lek lelek is xel betiyeing xoumeeng yuw.
\v 21 Ka xel di ya, moxo neil, “A neil wou xam zonghek bei, xam on ti tyek na neil a teyei me na toung ay eivek xel vevek amba memend.”
\p 
\v 22 Xel laleind wo nimaying me xel titi di neil wou e bei, “Tambiy Ngandoung, Beip se ay?”
\p 
\v 23 Yesu neil elox bei, “Tiwei embei toung mema eivek dipek is ay eno tyek na neil a teyei me na toung a na eivek xel vevek amba memend.
\v 24 Xomaxoneing Neu Moux tyek na nambei kawei xel byex eivek xoulek en e yo. Ekom nimaying ena wou moux tiwei embei neil Xomaxoneing Neu Moux teyei, dom na toung e na eivek xel ba memend! Inye nimza, bei tambiy tiyon ta se bou e.”
\p 
\v 25 Woyom Yudas tambiy tiwei embei neil e teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend o neil, “Putoung, neing ayang beip se ay?”
\p Yesu lewexe, “Nambei wang neil on.”
\p 
\v 26 Ka xel di ya, Yesu qou belet, de wong dange wou me dembu, de wong wou e xe xel betiyeing, de neil, “Xam qou me wa. Tine inye a neing.”
\p 
\v 27 Woyom moxo qou mayamya, me wong dange wou dom wong wou xel de neil, “Xam dalus a num eivek.
\v 28 Tine inye a gyand wei qokatu yo, en a qapyex lek xel ngenong bei e mi semaleeng sewokeing sapa.
\v 29 A neil wou xam, tyek a se nox me na num wain tine no me e mi na deka bouk tiyon tyek a num wain vako is xam eivek Mang xe tete lalei.”
\p 
\v 30 Woyom xel wong lalo ti, de xel la myayaing me la lukendu Oliv.
\s1 Yesu neil embei Petele tyek dax e vun
\p 
\v 31 Woyom Yesu neil wou xel, “Boukeing kane tyek xam xe wongeingis detei, en xel byex eivek xoulek eno nambei nye,
\q1 “‘Tyek a nyeis tambiy wei mi yeiteyei sipsip o,
\q2 dom xel sipsip na pek me davuna.’ \rq Sakarias 13:7\rq*
\m 
\v 32 Ekom tyek a qandi lek me na tax en xam me nana eivek Galili.”
\p 
\v 33 Petele neil elox bei, “Wangwei xel betiyeing dalus a saing xel xe wongeingis en wang, ond tyek a se teyei bei saing wang.”
\p 
\v 34 Yesu neil elox wou e bei, “A neil wou wang zonghek, boukeing kane, wei qouklex seng ghe sesa vya, tyek wang dax a vun luyal.”
\p 
\v 35 Ekom Petele neil embei, “Wangwei a mey is wang, ond a se teyei bei dax wang vund.” Me xel betiyeing dalus neil qayeeng kayon teyeima.
\s1 Yesu la Getsemani me la zeimema
\p 
\v 36 Woyom Yesu la is e xe xel betiyeing me xel la beyeeng ti lei Getsemani, me moxo neil wou xel, “Xam a toumendei inye nayaka le, dom a na inyei me na zeimemang bole.”
\v 37 Moxo qou Petele me Sebedi neu moux luw xouing is e. Moxo lalei wo nimaying me axe nilul ayang.
\v 38 Moxo neil wou lal, “A nung axe nimaying ngandoung om am bim a mey. Xam a toumendei inye me ghe gweiteyei is ay.”
\p 
\v 39 Moxo dula nayaka, de yeip ma eivek tembuing me zeimema, “Mang, wangwei nambei nyon nei, ond teyei bei wa zeim mayamya tine veil ay. Ekom wa se betiwou a xe woueing nalei, qe wa betiwou wamaxow xe woueing nalei.”
\p 
\v 40 Woyom moxo loumelam wou betiyeing yal on me yei lal di yeip o. Moxo teling Petele, “Se teyei bei mal mendi gweiteyei is ay teyei lek seivma ti?
\v 41 Xam a mi gweiteyei me na zeimemamim en kandek xam se detei eivek axeing. Laweeng lalei vind bei bong xuk, ekom neing mi wong nimbayaing.”
\p 
\v 42 Moxo lox me la luyuw no me zeimema, “Mang, wangwei mayamya tine se teyei bei ghanaw ay me a num, ond wa betiwou wamaxow laleim.”
\p 
\v 43 Ka moxo loumelam, moxo yei lal di yeip no, en nambei lal mend yeip.
\v 44 Om moxo ghanaw xel me lox tiwei yal o no me zeimema, me neil ambei kawei yo no.
\p 
\v 45 Woyom moxo loum wou e xe betiyeing me neil wou lal, “Xam anghei dei weip me ghe qou laweeng? Wei, seivma lam paviy, me gweimbeeng xel neil Xomaxoneing Neu Moux teyei me toung e la eivek xel wei sewokeing o memend.
\v 46 Qandi lek, en xey a na! En inye tambiy wei embei neil a teyei me na toung a na eivek xel memend eno lam!”
\s1 Xel zeimaxoun Yesu
\p 
\v 47 Ka moxo nanghei di luk, Yudas, tambiy tiyon eivek xel xoumeeng yuw eno lam tyip. Xel qendu ngandoung lam is e eno xel qou ngeyeing vevek me pebumeeng. Xel lumuki leitata me xel teivateiv wei xomaxoneing eno wong xel lam.
\v 48 Tambiy wei embei neil Yesu teyei me na toung e na eivek xel ba memend eno wong dee ti bei xel boulek: “Tiwei tyek a toung myang lek e ling ond moux tiyo inyon, om xam a zeimaxoun e.”
\v 49 Lutika eno Yudas lam wou Yesu me neil, “Boukeing Putoung!” dom toung mya lek e ling.
\p 
\v 50 Yesu neil elox bei, “Gweleeng, wang bong vati wei wang lam en o.”
\p Woyom xel moux on dulam paviy me zeimaxoun e.
\v 51 Ekom Yesu xe xelti mema la en e xe ngeyeing vevek, de tetei elam dom qateiv xukxe wei lumuki lukanzek on nenyalis tip veil.
\p 
\v 52 Yesu neil wou e, “Toung wa xe ngeyeing vevek on lox eivek beeng, en xel eti yeiw wei puw ngeyeing vevek tyek na mey angya ngeyeing vevek.
\v 53 Xam ghe wou naleimim bei tyek a se teyei bei taxe Mang, me lutika eno moxo tyek bong xel angela ngenong ghanaw xel qendu xoumeeng yuw wei vevek o me nam devind ay?
\v 54 Ekom wangwei a bong ambei nyon on qayeeng wei di yeip eivek Anutu xe qapiya vambuing ne tyek se bo neing lek. En Anutu xe qapiya neil embei, lul dalus tine eno e nam belup wou ay.”
\p 
\v 55 Lek seivma kayon eno Yesu neil wou xel qendu yon, “Beip a ne tambiy panaxeing me leiseing xel o, om xam ghe lam is ngeyeing aluw pebumeeng bei bo nol wou ay me na zeimaxoun ay? Bouk tambak ne a mindei eivek tete lalei wei xomek vambuing me na mi teyoxe xel, ekom xam seng zeimaxoun ay.
\v 56 Ekom tine dalus lam tyip nambei ingwei xel poropet byex eivek qapiya yo embo neing lek.” Woyom xel betiyeing dalus pek veil e me la.
\s1 Yesu nale wou xel kanzol mend
\p 
\v 57 Woyom xel moux wei zeimaxoun Yesu eno qou moxo me la wou lumuki lukanzek Kaiapas. Inyon xel putoung wei petieing me xel teivateiv wei di qekuma yo.
\v 58 Ekom Petele di betiwou e me la kwanding ka veil e. Moxo la eivek tete lalei wei lumuki lukanzek beeng o. Ka la dei inyon is xel belimbo, bei gyei vati wei embei belup wou Yesu yo.
\p 
\v 59 Xel lumuki leitata me xel kanzol dalus di yimexe qayeeng tyonyeing wei xel embei neil lek Yesu en kandek xel na nyeis e mey en o.
\v 60 Ekom xel se yeiwou qayeeng ti, de xel ngenong lam neil qayeeng ekom ma.
\p Dekalekom moux yayuw lam
\v 61 me neil embei, “Tambiy tine neil ambei nye, ‘A teyei bei lelolexe Anutu xe xomek vambuing de na nox me na dev eivek bouk yal.’ ”
\p 
\v 62 Woyom lumuki lukanzek nale ghey me neil wou Yesu, “Se teyei bei wa neil qayeeng ti noum? Inye qayeeng vati ingwei xel di neil lek wang ne?”
\v 63 Ekom Yesu nanghei toungale kanzek. Om lumuki lukanzek neil wou e, “A teling wou wang eivek Anutu mapieing lei, Neil wou xa wangwei wa Kilisi, Anutu Neu Moux nei.”
\p 
\v 64 Yesu neil elox bei, “Ee, nambei kawei wang neil on. Ekom a neil wou xam dalus, kalekom tyek xam ghe gwei Xomaxoneing Neu Moux mendei wou mema payeiv wei Anutu tiwei Nikanzekta me di lam lek laxap wei tyoung gheyapu yo.”
\p 
\v 65 Woyom lumuki lukanzek lex e xe teimb de neil, “Moxo lukyak lek Anutu yo! Nambei nya xey a ngo qayeeng valu is no? Wei, xam venaxow ghe ngo qayeeng lukeingyak wei e neil o.
\v 66 Xam ghe wou naleimim ambei nya?”
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Moxo teyei bei mey o.”
\p 
\v 67 Woyom xel pesuv myend louk lek e manghalus me lund memend de venoux e, de xel valu petapexe e
\v 68 me neil, “Kilisi, wa neil qayeeng poropet wou xa. Eti leis wang?”
\s1 Petele ax Yesu vun
\p 
\v 69 Petele moxo toundei myayaing eivek tete lalei wei xomek o. Xukxe vexawo ti lam wou e me neil, “Wang is en wang mindei is Yesu wei Galili yo.”
\p 
\v 70 Ekom moxo axvun eivek xel dalus mend. E neil elox bei, “A loung en vati wei xam ghe di luk en o.”
\p 
\v 71 Woyom moxo la myayaing wei tete mya nei. Inyon vexawo nge yei e me neil wou xel xomaxoneing nanghei inyon, “Tambiy tine mi la is Yesu wei Nasaret o.”
\p 
\v 72 Petele lox me la axvun no me neil zonghek is inyapunei bei, “A loung en moux tiyon!”
\p 
\v 73 Kalekom xel wei toungale inyon eno la wou Petele me neil, “Neing ayang wang on xel xe ti, en xa woulek wa vyam wei wang di luk on.”
\p 
\v 74 Woyom moxo neil vya lek xow me luk ninkanzek, “A neil neing wou xam bei, a loung en tambiy tiyon!”
\p Se denlek en qouklex sesa vya.
\v 75 Woyom Petele wou kwa en qayeeng wei Yesu neil o, “Qouklex se ghei sesa vya, eno tyek wang dax a vun luyal.” De moxo la myayaing me la eng ngandoungateiv mouyo.
\c 27
\s1 Yudas qo kwa
\p 
\v 1 Satiboukeing lulayang, eno xel lumuki leitata dalus me xel teivateiv wei xel xomaxoneing eno lam me di luklek qayeeng bei nyeis Yesu e mey.
\v 2 Xel tup e, de qou e me la wou eivek Pailat mema, lei ngandoung wei seyap o.
\p 
\v 3 Yudas tiwei neil Yesu teyei me toung e la eivek xel vevek memend o, yei bei xel byex qayeeng lek Yesu woy bei nyeis e mey, om moxo kwa pakou no me qou malew selewa xoumeeng yal (30) wei xel lumuki leitata me xel teivateiv wong wou e yo me lox wong elox wou xel.
\v 4 Moxo neil, “A wo sewokeing, en a neil tambiy wei nilul ma veil e yo teyei me na toung e lak eivek xam memamim.”
\p Xel neil elox bei, “Inyon se dei yeip wou xa ti. Qe inyon di yeip wou wamaxow o.”
\p 
\v 5 Om Yudas nex malew lox eivek xomek vambuing lalei dom la. Woyom Yudas venaxow la qo kwa me mey.
\p 
\v 6 Xel lumuki leitata zeim malew lek me neil, “Inye se la teyei lek qayeeng petieing bei xey a toung malew tine na eivek deng xeikatu wei xomek vambuing yo, en inye malew wei qapyex gyand o.”
\v 7 Om xel luk wouma me tup qayeeng bei dexouv tembuing wei xel wei mi betiy dengmuing o en malew tiyon en leiveeng meyeing wei xel amba yo.
\v 8 Om qes ambei nyon xel mi taxe Tembuing on Gyand me elam tyip gweimbeeng ne is.
\v 9 Woyom lul tine la teyei lek lulti Anutu neil eivek poropet Yelemia mya yo.
\q1 “Xel qou malew selewa xoumeeng yal (30) on teyei lek ambei xouveing wei xel xomaxoneing wei Israel beyal bei dexouv tambiy tiyon o,
\q2 
\v 10 me xel xouv tembuing wei xel wei mi betiy dengmuing en o ti, nambei Tambiy Ngandoung peti wou ay yo.” \rq Sakarias 11:12-13\rq*
\s1 Yesu nale wou Pailat manghalus
\p 
\v 11 Dekale Yesu nale wou lei ngandoung wei seyap o ma, me moxo teling e, “Beip wang on king wei Yudayeiw o?”
\p Yesu neil elox bei, “Nambei wang neil on.”
\p 
\v 12 De woyom xel lumuki leitata me teivateiv byex qayeeng lek Yesu, moxo se neil qayeeng ti lox wou xel.
\v 13 Woyom Pailat teling e, “Beip inye wa seng ngo pavulek wei xel di luk en wang ne?”
\v 14 Ekom Yesu se neil lulti lox, de se neil lulti lek qayeeng wei xel byex lek e yon, om tine wong lei ngandoung wei seyap o wounalei ngenong.
\p 
\v 15 Lei ngandoung wei seyap o xe kwa wei mi betiwou lek bouk wei Pasova eno mi tul xeitueing ti la teyei lek xel moux alis vex mi beyal o laleind.
\v 16 Lek bouk kayon eno tambiy nilul ayang ti lei Barabas eno toundei eivek xeitueing.
\v 17 Om xel qendu yon qekuma, Pailat teling xel, “Luw nge na xam ambei a bong e nak wou xam, Barabas o Yesu wei xel mi taxe bei Kilisi yo?”
\v 18 En moxo woulek bei xel venaxow xe laleind nilul, om xel qou Yesu me wong wou e.
\p 
\v 19 Ka Pailat toundei lek sia wei ngoeing qayeeng o, moxo venei wong qayeeng tine lam wou e: “Kandek wa seng bong lulti lek moux wei bombek o, en inye a axe nimaying ngandoung ti gweimbeeng eivek maviing en e.”
\p 
\v 20 Ekom xel lumuki leitata me xel teivateiv zeim xel qendu ngandoung on laleind lek bei e bong Barabas na wou xel dom nyeis Yesu e mey.
\p 
\v 21 Lei ngandoung wei seyap o teling, “Xam ambei a bong luw nge na, nak wou xam?”
\p Xel lewexe bei, “Barabas.”
\p 
\v 22 Pailat teling, “De tyek a bong vati wou Yesu tiwei xel taxe bei Kilisi ne?”
\p Xel dalus lewexe bei, “Tuw e lek xax pepeeng!”
\p 
\v 23 Pailat teling, “En va? E wong sewokeing vati?”
\p Ekom xel taxe lox wou e niseikeing bei, “Tuw e lek xax pepeeng!”
\p 
\v 24 Pailat woulek bei tyek xel se ngo e vya, de inyon vevek ngandoung embei qandi lek, om moxo qou memiing me sekweyexe mema eivek xel qendu ngandoung on dalus mend. Moxo neil, “Inye se sewokeing wei ay yo en moux tine gyand. Qe inye di yeip wou xam venaxow!”
\p 
\v 25 Xomaxoneing dalus lewexe, “Wong e xe gyand on lam lek xa me lek xa neumiyeiw!”
\p 
\v 26 Woyom moxo wong Barabas la wou xel. Dom neil wou xel vevekyeiw on bei xel sesa Yesu nangya yisviyeing, dekakom wong e la me xel tuw lek xax pepeeng.
\s1 Xel vevekyeiw luk seloukeing lek Yesu
\p 
\v 27 Woyom xel vevek wei lei ngandoung wei seyap o qou Yesu me la lalei eivek xomek seyap me qeku xel dalusateiv wei vevekyeiw o nale vivekwou e.
\v 28 Xel kwax e xe teimb veil dom byex teimb ding gyand nge lek e no,
\v 29 de xel bembinexe yis wei ying o lekti nambei qelumking de toung lek e lu. Xel toung xax nayak ti eivek e mema payeiv de dundek wou e ma me luk seloukeing lek e. Me neil, “Bendiyeing, king wei xel Yudayeiw o!”
\v 30 De xel pesuv myend louk lek e, de xel qou e xe patongeeng me sesa e lu gya lumama.
\v 31 Ka xel luk seloukeing lek e woy, xel kwax teimb wei xel byex lek e eno veil dom byex e maxow xe teimb lek no. Woyom xel qou e me la bei na tuw e lek xax pepeeng.
\s1 Xel tuw Yesu lek xax pepeeng
\p 
\v 32 Xel di tupwou sakwaing me la, eno xel la tyip wou tambiy wei Sairini yo ti, lei Simon, om xel tendu bei moxo e qalei xax pepeeng.
\v 33 Xel lam tyip wou beyeeng tiwei xel mi taxe bei Golgata (E qes ambei nye bei Beyeeng wei Lukanzek o).
\v 34 Nanghei inyon eno xel wong wain wei xel maleeng is lul senyeing o wou Yesu bei e num. Moxo num me axe le, ekom se num.
\v 35 Ka xel tuw e lek xax pepeeng woy, woyom xel nex qakous dee bei dembu e xe teimb wouma.
\v 36 Xel dei tembuing, me di yei e teyei nanghei inyon.
\v 37 Louk apu en e lu eno xel tuw qayeeng vati wei xel wong qayeeng en e yo bei: TINE INYE YESU, KING WEI YUDAYEIW O.
\v 38 Tambiy panaxeing yayuw eno xel tuw luw is e, nge wou e mema payeiv, de nge wou e mema qeinz.
\v 39 Eti yeiw wei di lam me la eno lukyak lek e, me bimexe lund
\v 40 me neil, “Wa kawei wang neimbei tyek lelolexe xomek vambuing dom ghe dev vako eivek bouk yal o inyon, om vind xow! Wangwei wa Anutu Neu Moux nei, tei lam veil xax pepeeng!”
\p 
\v 41 Eivek kwa kayon teyeima eno xel lumuki leitata me xel putoung wei petieing me xel teivateiv lukyak lek e.
\v 42 Xel neil, “Moxo vind xel bamba, ekom se teyei bei devind venaxow! Wangwei e king wei xel Israel o, yon e detei nam veil xax pepeeng en kandek xey a bongis e.
\v 43 Moxo mi wongis Anutu. Om wangwei Anutu lalei devind e nei yon e devind moxo, en mi neil embei, ‘A ne Anutu Neu Moux.’ ”
\v 44 Eivek sakwaing ambei nyon eno panaxeing yuw wei xel tuw is e eno lukyak lek e is.
\s1 Yesu mey
\p 
\v 45 Lek ingwei seivma evlek me e la seivma yal wei soukeing eno mapetok ngandoung sevunexe tembuing tambak on.
\v 46 Me embim seivma yal eno Yesu taxe niseikeing bei, “Eloi, Eloi, lama sabaktani?” Qes ambei nye bei, “A xe Anutu, a xe Anutu, nambei nya wang saing ay?” \rq Qapiya Lalo 22:1\rq*
\p 
\v 47 Woyom xel valu wei toungale inyon ngo tine, om xel neil embei, “Moxo taxe Eliya yo.”
\p 
\v 48 Lutika eno xel xe ti veimya me la qou balam. Moxo toung eivek wain senyeing me e pup, de tup lek xax mema nayak ti, dom zeim e la wou Yesu mya bei e num.
\v 49 Xel valu neil embei, “Wong xey a axe le bei, Eliya nam devind e.”
\p 
\v 50 Ekom Yesu nyayek niseikeing no, de wong e xe nulaweeng la dom mey.
\p 
\v 51 Lek kayon bombek eno qaeing ngandoung wei mii eivek xomek vambuing lalei eno lexla yayuw anghei pu me ela nge xo. De tembuing pi me wong qakous on dembu.
\v 52 Leiveeng meyeing ngenong mya tax de xel vambuing ngenong wei mey eno neing qandi lek mapieing.
\v 53 Xel lam myayaing veil leiveeng meyeing, deka Yesu qandi lek woy eno xel la eivek beyeeng vambuing Yerusalem me tyip wou xel xomaxoneing ngenong.
\p 
\v 54 Lei ngandoung wei vevek o is xel vevekyeiw toukale inyon is e me yei Yesu teyei eno yei tembuing pi me lul dalus tiwei qandi yon, om xel yaleeng, me neil, “Neing ayang tambiy tine inye Anutu Neu Moux!”
\p 
\v 55 Xel vex ngenong toukale kwanding, me di yei. Xel on ingwei mi betiwou Yesu nanghei Galili bei na devind e.
\v 56 Eivek vex vex on senghoing, inyon Maria wei Makdala me Maria wei Jems aluw Joses tend, me Sebedi neu luw tend.
\s1 Xel ev Yesu
\p 
\v 57 Ka moxo di souk, tambiy wei lulul ana eno lam anghei Arimatia, e lei Yosep. Moxo yon betiyeing wei Yesu yo ti.
\v 58 La wou Pailat, me teling wou en Yesu neing, om Pailat lewexe lek bei vevekyeiw bong Yesu neing na wou Yosep me e qou me na.
\v 59 Yosep qou neing on me beliv eivek qaeing teleing vako ti,
\v 60 me liw eivek e maxow xe leiveeng meyeing vako wei xel qateiv eivek qakous o. Dom moxo wilexe qakous ngandoung ti la zeyi leiveeng meyeing mya de la.
\v 61 Maria wei Makdala luw Maria nge eno toundei inyon paviy leiveeng meyeing.
\s1 Xel belimbo nale zeyi leiveeng meyeing
\p 
\v 62 Bouk wei Yudayeiw mi menyex wou lulul wei yaing eno lak veil, de bouk Sabat eno xel lumuki leitata me Parisiyeiw la wou Pailat.
\v 63 Xel neil wou e bei, “Teiv, xa wou naleimi en tambiy tiwei tyonyeing on wei nanghei toundei mapieing eno neil, ‘Ka bouk yal nak veil on tyek a qandi lek no.’
\v 64 Om wang bo qayeeng nikanzek en xel a toung leiveeng on mya zeyi embo nikanzek me ena tyip wou bouk yal. Enok e xe xel betiyeing nam me panax e neing dom na neil wou xel xomaxoneing bei moxo qandi lek veil meyeing. Tyonyeing tiwei yus ne tyek ghanaw tyonyeing wei wong a tax o.”
\p 
\v 65 Pailat neil embei, “Xam a qou xel belimbo wei mi yeiteyei leiveeng meyeing mya yo ti. La wong leiveeng mya yon wo nikanzek nambei xam ghe wou naleimim en o.”
\v 66 Om xel la lax leiveeng mya zeyi me toung newiy lek qakous dom wong xel belimbo la nale zeyi.
\c 28
\s1 Yesu qandi lek
\p 
\v 1 Ka bouk wei Sabat eno la veil, me di wong en embei boyaing lek bouk ti myaxeeng wei sounda qes tiyon o, Maria wei Makdala is Maria nge la en embei na gyei leiveeng meyeing.
\p 
\v 2 Woyom lutika eno tembuing pi ngandoung, en nambei Anutu xe angela lep me lam anghei tyoung gheyapu nei, me la ingwei leiveeng meyeing nei, me wilexe qakous la nale nenya dom dei lek.
\v 3 E ma yon siing ambei zivip, me e xe teimb on teltyip ambei laxap.
\v 4 Xel belimbo yon yaleeng en e, me etek niseikeing de pewilexe la yeip lek tembuing ambei xel meyeing.
\p 
\v 5 Ekom angela neil wou vex yuw on, “Muw seng gwaleeng, en a woulek bei muw ghe di wimexe Yesu, wei xel tuw lek xax pepeeng o.
\v 6 Moxo se toundei inye, en moxo qandi lek, nambei kawei neil o. Muw lam wei nimbeeng kawei yeip lek o.
\v 7 Muw ghe na daing me ghe na neil wou e xe xel betiyeing, ‘Tambiy moxo qandi lek veil meyeing me la tax en xam me la Galili. Tyek xam ghe na gwei e nanghei inyei.’ Wei, a lam en ambei nam a neil wou xam.”
\p 
\v 8 Om xel vex on tup me la nanghei ingwei leiveeng nei. Luw yaleeng ekom luw wo xeindlala mouyo, me veimyend bei na neil wou e xe xel betiyeing.
\v 9 Se denlek en Yesu la tyip wou luw. Moxo neil, “Satiboukeing.” Luw lam wou me axlek e vaxa dom wo lalo wou e.
\v 10 Woyom Yesu neil wou luw, “Muw seng gwaleeng. Muw la neil wou a lingyeiw bei xel na Galili, de tyek xel gyei ay anghei inyei.”
\s1 Qayeeng wei xel belimbo yo
\p 
\v 11 Ka vex yuw on di la wou sakwaing, xel belimbo yon valu la eivek beyeeng ngandoung me la neil qayeeng on wou xel lumuki leitata en lul dalus wei belup on.
\v 12 Xel lumuki leitata is xel teivateiv qekuma me neil qayeeng ti. Xel wong malew ngandoung wou xel vevekyeiw,
\v 13 me neil wou xel, “Xam a neil ambei nye bei, ‘Gyeik ingwei xa xeip eno moxo xe xel betiyeing lam eivek boukeing me panax e neing de qou me la.’
\v 14 Wangwei qayeeng tine na wou lei ngandoung wei seyap o, tyek xa menyex wou qayeeng is e, en kandek xam seng na eivek nimaying.”
\v 15 Om xel vevekyeiw qou malew on me wong ambei kawei neil wou xel o. De pavulek tine eno xel Yudayeiw mi neil e lala eivek ama senghoing me e lam tyip bouk ti gweimbeeng ne.
\s1 Yesu wong xuk ngandoung wou xel betiyeing
\p 
\v 16 Woyom xel betiyeing xoumeeng ti la Galili, me la lukendu tiwei Yesu neil wou xel bei xel na yo.
\v 17 Gyeik xel yei e, eno xel wong lalo wou e, ekom xel valu laleind wo yuw.
\v 18 Woyom Yesu lam wou xel me neil, “Lei wei ngandoung dalus eivek tyoung gheyapu me lek tembuing eno Anutu wong wou ay.
\v 19 Nambei nyon xam ghe na bong xomaxoneing wei tembuing sapa ne bong ambei a xe betiyeing, me ghe zipek xel eivek Mang lei me Neu lei me Laweeng Vambuing lei,
\v 20 me teyoxe xel bei xel bongis lul tambak tiwei a mi peti wou xam o. Wei, inye neing ayang, a mindei is xam teyei lek bouk sapa ne, me tyek a mi mendei is xam me ena tyip wou bouk wei la tip lek o.”
